\id MRK Ak…®gh…®m, 
\h Mak 
\mt1 MAK 
\mt2 Os…®risira Akamana AghuuŇč 
\c 1  
\ms1 Iesus zava Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthughun gun…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi 
\mr (Sapta 1.1--3.6) 
\s1 Gumasi uruer gumagh Jon, a ufhuaragha zava Iesus…®na akam…® ukuri 
\r (Metiu 3.1-12 ko Luk 3.1-9 ko Luk 3.15-17 koma Jon 1.19-28) 
\p  
\v 1 Kha mb…®ghar Iesus Krais Got…®n Otar r…®k…®nar…® kharaghava amuisiri iŇčaarir aghuuir gun…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi. 
\p  
\v 2 Aisaia Got…®na akam nigha zesi gumagh, Got fhom…®ra nona akaman aŇčga an…®…®Ňči. Anana os…®risima, an aŇčm mb…®Ňčgharani iti. Ma akamara khara. ‚ÄúN…®…® oragh! K…® nona ambuuŇčn gumagha amandaghtima, a ufhuaragh maŇč…®va n…®…®m…®usua utuaviri iŇčarami.  
\v 3 Gumaghani it…®…®Ňčn mav gumasi iti phat…®sira aŇčanan d…®…® mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄėGee Ikh…®vaghava utuavi azen…®va, anda r…®k…®r.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 4 Kamagha amuisima Jon zava gumasi iti phat…®sira aŇčaniri ikhava akam…® ukurava gumasi urua mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee navigh…® raghtima k…® gee urueghtima Got geno othevir maghat…®si g…®na amaaŇčga.‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 Ana akaar kharsi v…®Ňčgeema Judian distrigh…®ni itir…® uŇčuimba ko Jerusalem…®ni iti gumasi rako amisi mee bar zava nono othevir maghat…®sir gun…®m mb…®Ňčgeema a Jordan…® r…®m…®n mee urue. 
\p  
\v 6 Gumasi uruer gumagh Jon, a kamel…®n as…®ghana ar…®gh…®nana amuisi shaara sharagha ana as…®ghan ner…®n m…®ghas…®gha noni iva dii. A ner…®n khava sharagha ondaesi rako apharira aroroe apha iti. \f * \fr 1:6 \ft N…®…® kamel…®n as…®ghani iŇčeendagh ikhaaŇčm…®usua, n…®…® Mak 10.25v…®n gan n…®…® ikeeŇčgemi.\f* 
\v 7 AŇčna akam kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúNan g…®n zaami gumagh aŇčn gamgaaŇč guisimbaaŇčra nan gamgaaŇčga afhira. K…® aŇčn m…®na amuisi phat…®. K…® iv…®ra aviragh…®va aŇčna aŇčgarir shaarir…® umbuea afh…®rami thughat…®s phat…®.  
\v 8 K…® r…®m…®n gee urue, a g…®n z…®va Got…®n…® Utuman gamgaaŇčn gee uruami.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus…® uruegha g…®vasima Satan aŇčn khori ramuam…®usua aŇčga aghori 
\r (Metiu 3.13-17 ko Metiu 4.1-11 ko Luk 3.21-22 koma Luk 4.1-13) 
\p  
\v 9 Kha uthughun Iesus Galilin distrigh…®ni itir…® uŇčuu Nasareta thaeghava Jon…®m…®usua zesima, a Jordan…® r…®m…®n ana urue.  
\v 10 Iesus r…®m…®na aveni ikegha ak…®ran otuivi utughura a garima ovhee ukusima Got…®n…® Utum fhaman m…®n…®m mb…®ghegha aŇčm…®usua zeghiri.  
\v 11 Gumughun a zeghirima it…®…®Ňčn mav Got…®n…® uŇčuuni ikha d…®…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúN…®…® nano Otar. K…® bar n…®Ňčgi iphui. Nan nav bar n…®…®n vhusvhusi.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 12 Gumughun Got…®n…® Utum ana amandasima a gumasi iti phat…®sira aŇčanan gu.  
\v 13 A gugha, 40 p…®lan aroe rako r…®maŇčgarir kha aŇčanani itima, Satan aŇčn khori ramuam…®usua aŇčga aghori. A uruaŇčni itira as…®sir thooŇčni itima, Got…®n enseli mee aŇčn garava ana akuruvasi. 
\s1 Iesus gumaghan phunini ko phuninim mb…®kemisima mee aŇčn g…®n zui 
\r (Metiu 4.12-17 ko Luk 4.14-15 ko Metiu 4.18-22 koma Luk 5.1-11) 
\p  
\v 14 Gumughun gumasi uruer gumagh Jon, mee ana nigha r…®v…®nan kh…®rth…®gha ath…®sima, Iesus g…®n Galilin distrigh…®n gugha Got…®na akamana aghuuŇč ukuri.  
\v 15 A kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGot kha bisigha ativamir…® uthugho otuivousua bara aghangera zee. Gee navigh…® ragh…®va n…®ghn…®ghana aghavagharan Got…®na akamana aghuuŇčni ikh…®…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 16 Uthughun mav…®n Iesus Galilin r…®m…®m mb…®rogh…®n gua Saimon non…® undooghan Andru ko aniiŇčn garima, aniiŇč os…®riv…®usua noniiŇč noni ivhaeri ikii ukuri. AniiŇč os…®ri nia andagh…® uvhuesi gumaghaniiŇč.  
\v 17 Mauthughura Iesus kamagha aniiŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAŇčgo nan g…®n z…®tima k…® aŇčgon kh…®vaghtima, aŇčgo os…®ri nii mogh gumasi niaŇčga.‚ÄĚ  
\v 18 AniiŇč aŇčna akamam mbaraghav…®re ikha, noniiŇč noni ivhea thaegha aŇčn g…®n zui. 
\p  
\v 19 Gumughun a mange s…®vagha gua, Sebedin otar Jems non…® undooghan Jon ko aniiŇčn garima aniiŇč noniiŇč nona akemani ikhava noni ivhaeri ikia r…®k…®ri.  
\v 20 Ana aniiŇčn garav…®re ikha, aniiŇčn deema, aniiŇč phura noniiŇč noni inaghaves Sebedi ko aŇčni iŇčaarir gumasia thaesima, mee norira akemani itima, aniiŇč Iesus…®n g…®n zui. 
\s1 Utuman maghat…®ghan mav Iesus aŇčga avarasima a gumagha thaegha ak…®ran zee 
\r (Luk 4.31-37) 
\p  
\v 21 Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha Kaperneam…®n gusima avhughususan…® uthugho otosima a gua Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger r…®phenana aven gugha, r…®phenan khav…®na aveni iti gumasi rako amisi men surea amui.  
\v 22 A men surea amuima gumasi rako amisi bar aŇčna akamamba oraegha r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui. AŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®r kharsi, anda iz…®…® iti gumagham mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®r m…®n gu. AŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…® Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi mem mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®r m…®n zui phat…®. Kamagha amuisima gumasi rako amisi r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui. 
\p  
\v 23 A kamagh mem mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima utuman maghat…®gha aphasagha zii gumagh a zava Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger r…®phenana aven zegha deeghi.  
\v 24 A d…®…® kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® manmagh ee ramuam…®usua, Iesus NasaretiiŇčn gumagh? N…®…®ti eŇčga as…®ghas…®ghaousua zesire? K…® n…®…® ikaaŇči, n…®…® Got amandasi gumagh, n…®…® Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn bar inderasi gumaghara.‚ÄĚ  
\v 25 A deema, Iesusa akamana aghavagharan kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® in…®m…®re ikh…®…®. N…®…® kha gumagha thaegha ak…®ran z…®…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 26 Mauthughura utuman maghat…®gh Iesus…® oraegha gumaghan khavi ikuskusa d…®…®va arava ak…®ran zee.  
\v 27 Ana ak…®ran zesima, kha gumasi rako amisi bar bighan khav…®n ganigha guisimbaaŇčra r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuigha norira norir azaaghi, ‚ÄúKhara manmagha amuisi bighaaŇč? A sureno otheviri iŇčgaar iz…®…® iti gumaghan m…®na andar eŇčga amui. A iz…®…® itir gumaghan m…®n…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi. A iv…®ra akamana aghavaghar ikha unduur maghat…®si v…®Ňčgeema mee aŇčn m…®n zui.‚ÄĚ  
\v 28 Ana amuisi bisir niaghasi uzuam…®ra Galilin distrigh bar aŇčga arui. 
\s1 Iesus gumasi rako amisira av…®rara akuruvagha meŇčga amuima mee nomthegha indera 
\r (Metiu 8.14-17 koma Luk 4.38-41) 
\p  
\v 29 Iesus gumasir marsi ko Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger r…®phena thaeghava, Saimon ri Andru r…®phenan gue. Jems ri Jon iv…®ra men phorugha gu.  
\v 30 Mee gua garima Saimon…®na asamuiiŇč ar…®va mb…®kar…®gh siava akoghi ir…®ghavi itima, gumasir marsi aŇčn gun Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 31 Mee aŇčm mb…®kemisima, an aŇčm…®usua gua aŇčna afharimuun…® usuiragha ana ufhee. Ana ufheesima aŇčna ar…®mar…®m ana thaesima a r…®khavigha magh…®ra aghaer meŇčga an…®ndi. 
\p  
\v 32 Kha uŇčguar thughura, am…®n ph…®risima mee gumasi rako amisi, ar…®mar…®r maghat…®si iti tharsi rako unduur maghat…®si aphasasi tharsi bar mee nigha Iesus…®usua zii.  
\v 33 UŇčuun khav…®ni iti gumasi rako amisi bar zava r…®phenan khav…®ni it…®mana akamaniiŇčn nori akuvagha iti.  
\v 34 Mee itima, Iesusa ar…®mar…®r guara av…®rare iti gumasi rako amisi mena ar…®mar…®gha amuima mee indera. A unduur maghat…®sira av…®rara avarasima mee gumasi rako amisia thaegha ak…®ran zee. Unduur maghat…®si ana ikaaŇči, a Got…®n Otar. Kamagha amuisima a kamagh mem mb…®usue, ‚ÄúGee kamagh…®m mb…®k…®man thaghri, ‚ÄėK…® Got…®n Otar.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ A magh…®ra mee r…®ghorigharui. 
\s1 Iesus gumasi iti phat…®sira aŇčanan gugha Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčgeeghi 
\r (Luk 4.42-44) 
\p  
\v 35 Am…®r…®tusi r…®maaŇčra aro thighar anandima Iesus…® r…®khavigha r…®phena thaegha gua gumasi iti phat…®sira aŇčanan gugha Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 36 A gusima Saimon no r…®kurku nigha aŇčm…®usua garagharui.  
\v 37 Mee gua aŇčn ganighava kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumasi rako amisi bar n…®…®m…®usua garagharui.‚ÄĚ  
\v 38 Iesus mena akamani iŇčgar…®gha amua kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe aghani itir…® uŇčuimbari igharis thasir maŇčŇčaŇčga. K…® iv…®ra munagh Got…®na akam…® ukunaŇčga. K…® bighan khav…®usua Kaperneama thaegha zee.‚ÄĚ  
\v 39 A kamagh…®m mb…®kemigha Galilin distrigh…®na aŇčani bar andagha arui. Ana arua gua Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger r…®phenira aven guava akam…® ukuri. Ana akam…® ukura gumasi rako amisigha aphasasir…® unduur maghat…®si vathosi. 
\s1 Iesus mamburan ar…®mar…®m itir gumaghan mav aŇčga amuisima, a indera 
\r (Metiu 8.1-4 koma Luk 5.12-16) 
\p  
\v 40 Mamburan ar…®mar…®m itir gumaghan mav Iesus…®usua zava, aŇčm mb…®n…®man aviragha it…®v…®nia r…®ph…®righa phuv…®ra aŇčga aghori, ‚ÄúN…®…® vhusvhusigh…®v, n…®…® nara amuighti, k…® Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn inderagh…®v…®re ikaami.‚ÄĚ  
\v 41 Iesus kamagh oraegha, guisimbaaŇčra bar aŇčn…® ukuarukuvi. Kamagha amuigha a nona afharimuu nigha kha gumaghani iph…®a ath…®gha kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúNan vhusvhus. N…®…®m mb…®kar…®gh nomi inderaghami.‚ÄĚ  
\v 42 Iesus kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima, mamburan ar…®mar…®m…® uzuam…®ra kha gumagha thaesima aŇčm mb…®kar…®gh indera.  
\v 43 A inderasima, Iesus kha gumagha amaŇčga akamana aghavagharan kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi,  
\v 44 ‚ÄúN…®…® oragh. N…®…® maaŇč…® bighan khav…®n gun igharisi gumagha thav…®m mb…®k…®ma thagh…®ri. Moses fhom…®ra kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėN…®…® nom mb…®kar…®ghan Got…®na aphuraphurava am mb…®Ňčger gumaghan kh…®vaghtima a Got…®na aphuraphurami.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ Iesus kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúN…®…® Moses…®na akaman g…®n maŇč…®va nom mb…®kar…®ghan Got…®na aphuraphura am mb…®Ňčger gumaghan kh…®vaghtima gumasi rako amisi ganighi ikeeŇčgemi. N…®…®na ar…®mar…®m guisimbaaŇčra g…®va.‚ÄĚ  
\v 45 Kha gumagh Iesus aŇčm mb…®kemisi mogh…®n amuisi phat…®. A kha bighaaŇčn gun bar mem mb…®kemi. Mamagha amuigha phogh…®ni ikh…®v aŇčna akuva. Kamagha amuigha a uŇčuuni ikh…®va thav…®na aven mena ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn arui phat…®. A nomb…®ra gumasi iti phat…®sira aŇčanan kh…®nani itima gumasi rako amisi aŇčm…®usua zav…®re iti. 
\c 2  
\s1 Iesus…® usue rako afhari am…®rasi gumaghan mav aŇčga amuisima a nomthegha indera 
\r (Metiu 9.1-8 koma Luk 5.17-26) 
\p  
\v 1 Uthusir marsi g…®vasima, Iesus nomthegha Kaperneam…®n zee. A za r…®phenani itima gumasi rako amisira av…®rara a nomthegha zesira akamam mbaraghi.  
\v 2 Mee akaman khav…® oraegha zesima r…®phen bari iz…®vasima aŇčni it…®mam mburogh…®n iv…®re iz…®va. Uthughun khav…®n Iesus Got…®na akaman mem mb…®k…®ri.  
\v 3 Ana akam…® ukurima, gumasir marsi gumaghan…® usue rako afhari ar…®ghiresir mav nigha aŇčm…®usua zii. Gumaghan phunini ko phunini akuuna aŇčgi isaghuph…®gha zii.  
\v 4 Mee za garima r…®phenani it…®mam mburogh…®n bar iz…®vasima, mee Iesus…®usua azaaŇčni iŇčgura. Mee gumaghan khav nigha r…®phenani is…®…®Ňčn guavanambogha r…®phenani is…®…®Ňčn thooŇčga amuigha umbuera akuu rafhagha ana amandasima a Iesus…®usua zeghiri.  
\v 5 Uthughun khav…®n Iesus gumasir kharsir n…®ghn…®ghana aghavagharan ganigha kamagh…® usue rako afhari am…®rasi gumagham mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúNano otar, k…® n…®…®no othevir maghat…®si g…®na amanda.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 6 Iesus kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeema, Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi apiighav ikhava norira non navira averir kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi,  
\v 7 ‚ÄúGumaghan khav thoghousua kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi? A Got…®na aŇčan niam…®usua amui! Gumaghan kh…®na thav gumaghan igharisi thav…®no othevir maghat…®si g…®na amandagham phat…®ghami. Got nomb…®ra.‚ÄĚ  
\v 8 Mee kamagh…® n…®gh…®n…®sima, Iesus…® uzuam…®ra non navana aven men n…®gh…®n…®si ikeeŇčga kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee manmagh…®usua kamagh n…®gh…®n…®si?  
\v 9 K…® manmaghat…®sira akaman…® usue rako afhari am…®rasi gumagham mb…®k…®mti? Mana akamambaaŇč indera. K…® n…®…®no othevir maghat…®si g…®na amanda, o? K…® kamagh…®m mb…®k…®maŇčga n…®…® nomthegh inderagh…®ri. N…®…® r…®kavigh nona akuu nigh maŇč…®. K…® manmagha amuisi akamam mb…®k…®mti, gee aŇčm mbaragh…®v kamagh…®m mb…®k…®maŇčga a indera.  
\v 10 K…® oth…®vhan khav ramuightima, gee ganighi ikeeŇčgemi, Gumasir Otar\f * \fr 2:10 \ft Gumasir Otar a Iesus…®ni iz…®…®n mav, a kha iz…®…®n nomb…®ra nomb…® ar…®siri iz…®…®.\f* a unuagh…®nan khav…®no othevir maghat…®si g…®na amaaŇčgamiri iz…®…® iti.‚ÄĚ A kamagh gumaghan…® usue rako afhari am…®rasi thav…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi,  
\v 11 ‚ÄúK…® n…®…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, n…®…® r…®kavigh nona akuu nigh r…®phenan maaŇč…®ri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 Am mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima mee garima gumaghan khav r…®kavighava nona akuu nigha ak…®ran zui. Gumasi rako amisi bar aŇčn ganigha r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuigha Got…®ni iz…®…® ufhava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe ufhuaragha kamagha amuisi bigha thav…®n ganis phat…®!‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus nomb…®n g…®n maŇčam…®usua Livain deeghi 
\r (Metiu 9.9-13 koma Luk 5.27-32) 
\p  
\v 13 Iesus nomthegha Galilin r…®m…®m mb…®rogh…®n gueghiri. A gueghirima, gumasi rako amisira av…®rara zava nori akuvasima, a men surea amui.  
\v 14 A men surea amuava r…®m…®m mb…®rogh…®n gua Alfius…®n otar Livain garima, a gavman…® ran…®…®Ňčgamira aŇčg…®ro ov…®si nir r…®phenan apheraghav iti. Iesus aŇčn garava, kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® nan g…®n z…®ri.‚ÄĚ Magh…®ra Livai aŇčm mbaraegha, r…®khavigha aŇčn g…®n zui. \f * \fr 2:14 \ft Metiuni iz…®…®n mav Livai.\f* 
\p  
\v 15 G…®n Iesus Livain r…®phenani ikhava non suren gumasir phorughava aphi. AŇčg…®ro ov…®si nii gumasira av…®rara ko othevir maghat…®sigha amuir gumasira av…®rara, mee iv…®ra men phorugha aphi. Kamagha amuir gumasira av…®rara, mee iv…®ra Iesus…®n g…®na arui.  
\v 16 Mee apha itima, Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi FarisiiŇčn gumasi mee aŇčn ganigha, aŇčn suren gumasira azaaghi, ‚ÄúA manmagh…®usua aŇčg…®ro ov…®si nii gumasi rako othevir maghat…®sigha amuir gumasir phorughava aphi?‚ÄĚ  
\v 17 Iesus mena azaaŇčs…®gha oraegha kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAr…®mar…® phat…®sir gumasi, ar…®mar…®a r…®k…®rir gumaghaousua zui phat…®. Ar…®mar…® iti gumasi, mee ar…®mar…®a r…®k…®rir gumaghaousua zui. K…® othevira aghuigha amuir gumasi rako amisiv…®usua zesi phat…®. K…® othevir maghat…®sigha amuir gumasi rako amisir d…®mam…®usua zee!‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Mee aghae tham…®rasiro oth…®vhaousua Iesus…®na azaaghi 
\r (Metiu 9.14-17 koma Luk 5.33-39) 
\p  
\v 18 Uthughun mav…®n Jon…®n suren gumasi rako FarisiiŇčn suren gumasi mee Got…®n phorughum mb…®k…®mam…®usua aghae tham…®rasi. Iesus…®n suren gumasi uthughun khav…®n aphima gumasir marsi Iesus…®usua zava kamagh aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúKhara manmagh…®ra amuisiro oth…®v? Jon…®n suren gumasi rako FarisiiŇčn suren gumasi mee thighira Got…®n phorughum mb…®k…®mam…®usua aghae tham…®rasima, n…®…®n suren gumasi Got…®n phorughum mb…®k…®mam…®usua aghae tham…®rasi phat…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 19 Mem mb…®Ňčgeema Iesus kamagh mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúGumaghan mava amuuŇčni ikhaousua ishamani ikh…®va amuava gumasir marsir d…®…®sima mee zee. A men phorugh ikh…®tima, mee manmagh…®ra ramuti, mee aghaa tham…®raghami, o phat…®ghami. A men phorugh ikh…®tima mee aghaa thaeghem phat…®ghami.  
\v 20 Mee aghae tham…®rasir…® uthugh iti. Kha uthugh z…®tima, gumasir marsi amuuŇčni ikhaamir gumaghan…® usuiragh maŇč…®ti, mee kha uthughun aghaa tham…®raghami. 
\p  
\v 21 Gumagha thav…®m mb…®sasin ofh…®ghan ikama thav nigha shaaran gura thav…®n phorugha ana isamisi phat…®. A mamagh ramuigh…®va ana urutima mb…®sasin ofh…®ghan ikam ikonigh shaaran gure ikuigh…®va, anebiightima aŇčn thooŇč guisimbaaŇčra bar ikhevighemi.  
\v 22 Gumagha thav uainiro ov…®siri imbooriri iŇčgaa nigh…®va, as…®ghan ner…®m mb…®s…®van guro uruighem phat…®ghami. A kamagh ramuightima uainiro ov…®siri imboori bugh…®va as…®ghan ner…®m mb…®s…®van gura biigh…®va, uainiro ov…®siri imboori ko as…®ghan ner, aniiŇč iv…®ra maghatiighemi. A kamagh ramuighem phat…®ghami. A uainiro ov…®siri imbooriri iŇčgaa nigh as…®ghan ner…®m mb…®s…®van ikamaro uruighemi.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Gumasir Otar ana avhughususan…® uthughuni Ikh…®v 
\r (Metiu 12.1-8 koma Luk 6.1-5) 
\p  
\v 23 Iesus avhughususan…® uthughun mav…®n, rais…®n m…®n garira aghan mav, uit, mee aŇčn m…®gh…®ni ikh…®van thooŇčn zui. AŇčn suren gumasi aŇčn phorugha gua uitiro ov…®si ukuara zui.  
\v 24 Mee zuima FarisiiŇčn marsi men ganigha kamagh Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® gan…®ri. Mee manmagh…®usua oth…®vhan khav aŇčga amuava avhughususan…® uthughuno oth…®vhan g…®n zui phat…®?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 25 Iesus mee ikaragha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee, Devit amuisir bighaaŇč mee ana os…®risima a iti, gee aŇčn ganisi o, phat…®? A non gumasir phorugha mem mb…®tii mena azima a bighan khuaŇčga amui.  
\v 26 A gua Got…®n r…®phenana aven gugha Got…® aniiŇčsi uvisir…® uthuu ame. Ana anda aphava, iv…®ra marsi nigha non gumasigha aniiŇčsima, mee iv…®rama anda ame. Kha uthughun Abiatar, Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasira aphanani itima, Devit anda ame. Judariro oth…®vhan khav iti. Uvisir…® uthuur kharsir Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasira anda aphi, gumasir kh…®ni phat…®. Uthughun khav…®n Devit, gumaghan kh…®n, uvisir…® uthuur kharsi ame.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 27 Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGot gumasira akuruvaghaousua avhughususan…® uthugha ath…®. Ana avhughususan…® uthughuna akuruvaghaousua gumasi ath…®si phat…®.  
\v 28 Gumasir Otar ana avhughususan…® uthughuni Ikh…®v.‚ÄĚ 
\c 3  
\s1 Iesus avhughususan…® uthughuna afhari konisi gumaghan mav…®a amuisima a nomthegha indera 
\r (Metiu 12.9-14 koma Luk 6.6-11) 
\p  
\v 1-2 Igharisir…® uthughun mav…®n Iesus Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger r…®phenan gua, garima afhari konisi gumaghan mav r…®phenan khav…®na aven gumasi rako amisira av…®rar ar…®ghani iti. A itima gumasir marsi iv…®re iti. Iesus bigha thav…® ramuightima, mee akaman aŇčga asaousua bar inderaghav…®ra aŇčn gari. Mee kamagh…®usua aŇčn gari. Ana avhughususan…® uthughun gumaghan khav…®na akuraghami, o?  
\v 3 Mee bighan khav…®usua aŇčn garav…®re itima, Iesus kamagh…®na afhari konisi gumagham mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® r…®kavigh z…®…® bar eem mb…®n…®man…® utugh…®ri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 4 Gumagh r…®khavigha utusima, Iesus kamagh mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúOth…®vhan manav ana avhughususan…® uthughuni indera? Ee oth…®vhana aghuuŇč ramuaŇčga, o oth…®vhan maghat…®gha ramuaŇčga, o gumaghana akuruvaghami, o gumagha as…®ghas…®ghami?‚ÄĚ A kamagh mena azarasima, mee bar in…®m…®re iti.  
\v 5 Ana ar…®maghaniiŇč bar gumasi rako amisigha aruava, navana avera meŇčga avhesi. A men garima, men navia aghavagharigha ukuarukuvan n…®gh…®n…®si men phat…®. Kamagha amuisi a bar osemigha kha gumagh kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® nona afharimuu oneegh…®ri.‚ÄĚ Gumaghan khav nona afhari onesima, aŇčna afhari nomthegha indera.  
\v 6 FarisiiŇč ikha ganigha r…®phena thaegha azenan zegha Herot…®n g…®na aruir gumasir phorugha ikha Iesus…®m mb…®soghousua akaar r…®k…®ri. 
\ms1 Iesus non gamgaaŇčn men kh…®vasima ana andarsi n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar aŇčni iti phat…® 
\mr (Sapta 3.7--6.6) 
\s1 Gumasi rako amisira av…®rara Iesus…®n g…®n zui 
\r (Luk 6.17-19) 
\p  
\v 7 Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha Galilin r…®m…®n gueghiri. A gueghirima gumasi rako amisira av…®rara Galilin distrigh…®ni ikegha aŇčn g…®n gueghiri.  
\v 8 Judian distrigh ko Jerusalem…®n…® uŇčuu phorugha Idumean distrigh…®n gumasi rako amisira av…®rara Iesus…®usua gueghiri. Tair…®n…® uŇčuu ko Saidon…®n…® uŇčuum mb…®rogh…®ni iti marsi koma Jordan…® r…®m…®n muaaŇčmogh itir gumasi rako amisi iv…®ra Iesus…®usua gueghiri. Gumasi rako amisir av…®rir kharsi, mee ana amuisir bisira akamam mbaraegha aŇčm…®usua gueghiri.  
\v 9-10 Mee gueghiresima, Iesus gumasi rako amisira av…®rara mena akurasima, mena ar…®mar…® g…®va. Ar…®mar…® itir gumasi rako amisira av…®rara nona ar…®mar…®a g…®vaousua Iesus…®na aghan nori akuvagha, Iesus…®n…® usuighaousua nori munamandi. Kamagha amuisima, Iesus non suren gumasi v…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGee akema thav nigh z…®…® phura anarat…®ghti a ikh…®ri. Gumasi rako amisi bar z…®…® na akuvaghtima k…® akeman anamboghomi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 11 Iesus mem mb…®Ňčgeema, unduur maghat…®si aphasasi gumasir marsi zava, Iesus…®n garava unduur maghat…®si uzuam…®ra meŇčga amuima mee Iesus…®m mb…®n…®man daaghira kamagh araaghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® Got…®n Otar.‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 Mee kamagha amuima, ana akamana aghavagharan mem mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGee kamagh…®m mb…®k…®man bar thaghri, ‚ÄėK…® Got…®n Otar.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus…®m mb…®sevisir gumasir 12 p…®la 
\r (Metiu 10.1-4 koma Luk 6.12-16) 
\p  
\v 13 Iesus r…®m…®m mb…®rogh…®ni ikegha r…®kavighava oragh…®n guavanambogha non vhusvhusan gumasir deema, mee aŇčm…®usua zii.  
\v 14 Mee ziima a gumasir 12 p…®lam mb…®sevigha iz…®…®n khav…®n meŇčga ath…®, mb…®sevisir gumasi. Mee aŇčn phorugh ikh…®tima, a g…®n mee amandaghti mee maaŇč…® Got…®na akamana aghuuŇč ukunaŇčga.  
\v 15 A non gamgaaŇčn mee raniiŇčtima mee iv…®ra unduur maghat…®si vatoghomi iz…®…®ri ikhami.  
\v 16 Am mb…®sevisir gumasir 12 p…®lani iz…®…®ri khara. Saimon (Iesus g…®ni iz…®…®n khav…®n aŇčga ath…® Pita),  
\v 17 Sebedin otaraniiŇč Jems ri Jon (A iz…®…®n khav…®na aniiŇčga ath…®, Boanerges. Iz…®…®n khav…®m mb…®n…®…®Ňč kamagh gu, avhesa mb…®gh…®rav…®ram mb…®Ňčger gumaghaniiŇč),  
\v 18 Andru ri Filiv, Bartolomiu, Metiu, Tomas, Alfius…®n otar Jems, Tadius, Saimon (A SelotiiŇčna akogh…®n gumaghan mav),  
\v 19 ko Judas Iskariot, Iesus nigha, aphanigha aniiŇčsi gumagh. 
\s1 Mee kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúIesus Belsebul…®n gamgaaŇčni iŇčaari‚ÄĚ 
\r (Metiu 12.24-32 ko Luk 11.14-23 koma Luk 12.10) 
\p  
\v 20 Iesus nomthegha r…®phenana aven gugha itima gumasi rako amisira av…®rara zava ana akuva. Mee bar ana akuvasima, a non suren gumasir phorugh mee aghae ramaŇčgami mbaaŇčn iŇčgura. Mee ramaŇčgamir…® uthusi phat…®.  
\v 21 Gumasi rako amisir marsi kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAna oŇčani.‚ÄĚ Iesus…®na andarsi akaman khav…® oraegha, ana nigh maŇčam…®usua zii. 
\p  
\v 22 Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasir marsi Jerusalem…®ni ikegha zeghirava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúBelsebul aŇčga aphasa. A unduur maghat…®sir gumaghana aphanan gamgaaŇčn…® unduur maghat…®si andavathosi.‚ÄĚ \f * \fr 3:22 \ft Satan…®ni iz…®…®n mav…®ra khara, Belsebul.\f* 
\v 23 Iesus mem mb…®Ňčgera akamam mbaraegha, kamagha amuigha a gumasi rako amisir d…®…®va aghunambagha asira akaar marsir mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúSatan manmagh…®ra nomb…®ra nomb…® athueghti?  
\v 24 Kantri thav thooŇčra nomba biigh…®va norira nori v…®sogh…®va kantrin khav ikeghem phat…®ghami.  
\v 25 Kamagh…®n iv…®ra, r…®phenan…® uvav…®ra iti tharsi mee thooŇčra noria biigh…®va norira nori v…®sogh…®va r…®phenan khav…®ni iti tharsi ikeghem phat…®ghami.  
\v 26 Kamagh…®ra Satana andarsi norira noria biigh…®va nori v…®soghtima aŇčn gamgaaŇč bar g…®vagh ikeghem phat…®ghami. 
\p  
\v 27 Gumaghan manav phura aven maaŇč…® gumaghana aghavaghara thav…® r…®phena akarigh…®va aŇčn bisi nitii? Phat…®ghami. A ufhuaragh…®v…®ra umbuer gumaghana aghavagharan khav ikeghemi. A kamagh aŇč ramuigh…®va gumaghan khav…®n r…®phenana aven maaŇč…®, aŇčn bisi niaŇčga.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 28-30 Mee ufhuaragha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúUtuman maghat…®ghan mav aŇčga aphasa.‚ÄĚ A bighan khuaŇčm…®usua, akaar kharsir mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® guisimbaaŇčra gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, gumasi rako amisi mee othevir maghat…®sigha amua Got…®ni iz…®…®ra afharavaeghtima Got anda g…®na amaaŇčgamir…® utuav iti. Gumagha thav Got…®n…® Utumani iz…®…®ra afharavaeghtima Got aŇčno oth…®vhan maghat…®ghan khav, ana g…®na amandagham phat…®ghami. Os…®mnd…®ghan khav aŇčni ikh…®v…®re ikaami.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus…®ni inaghamuuŇč ko aŇčn…® undoosi 
\r (Metiu 12.46-50 koma Luk 8.19-21) 
\p  
\v 31 Uthughun khav…®n Iesus…®ni inaghamuuŇč ko aŇčn…® undoosi zava, a itir r…®phenani it…®mana akamaniiŇčn…® utughava gumaghan mava amandasima a Iesus…®m mb…®k…®mam…®usua aven zui.  
\v 32 Gumasi rako amisira av…®rara aŇčn phorugha apiighav ikhava kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúNo oraesire! N…®…®ni inaghamuuŇč ko undoosi mee n…®…®m…®usua zeghava ak…®rani iti.‚ÄĚ  
\v 33 Mee aŇčm mb…®kemisima a kamagh mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúTh…®…®Ňčra nani inaghamuuŇč? ThaeŇč nan…® undoosi?‚ÄĚ  
\v 34 A kamagh mena azaraghava, ana ighuighav apiighav itir gumasi rako amisir garava, kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee gan! Nani inaghamuuŇč ko undoosira khara.  
\v 35 Got vhusvhuisiro othevir g…®n zui gumasi rako amisira, mee nan…® undoosi rako umbuaramisi koma nani inaghamuuigha.‚ÄĚ 
\c 4  
\s1 Iesus aghunamana akamaŇčga asa kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumaghan mav uitiro ov…®si nigha m…®gh…®n anda ukuragha arui‚ÄĚ 
\r (Metiu 13.1-9 koma Luk 8.4-8) 
\p  
\v 1 Igharisir…® uthughun mav…®n Iesus nomthegha r…®m…®m mb…®rogh…®ni ikhava, gumasi rako amisir marsir surea amui. Gumasi rako amisir av…®rani ikh…®v ana akaava oraghaousua zava ana akuavasima, aŇčani iz…®vasi a b…®ragha akemana anambogha r…®m…®ni iph…®na apheraghav itima gumasi rako amisir kharsi aŇčna aghan ataaŇčn apiighav iti.  
\v 2 Ana akaar av…®rar aghunambagha asava men surea amua kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi,  
\v 3 ‚ÄúGee oragh. Gumaghan mav rais…®n m…®n garir aghaan mav, uit, ana nigha gua non m…®gh…®n anda ukuragha arui.  
\v 4 Ana anda ukurima uitiro ov…®sir marsi utuav…®ni iresima, ukuarasi zava anda ame.  
\v 5 Marsi aŇčg…®ri iph…®ni itir…® unuagh…®nani ivamnd…®ghaaŇčgi ire. Unuagh…®nan khav phum mb…®themis phat…®sima uitiro ov…®si uzuam…®ra afhuaaŇči.  
\v 6 Andar bii bar…® unuagh…®nana aven gueghiresi phat…®si aro anaŇčgava andaghi isirasima anda sia mb…®s…®…®Ňči.  
\v 7 Uitiro ov…®sir marsi r…®khonir…® umbue itir…® unuagh…®naŇčgi iregha, umbuer thooŇčna afhueŇčsima, r…®khonir…® umbue aghuuva umbue anda ikhaa davi. Andaro ov…®si v…®sevisi phat…®.  
\v 8 Uitiro ov…®sir marsi unuagh…®nana aghuuŇčgi iregha aghuuva ov…®si v…®sevi. Marsi 30 p…®lam mb…®sevi, marsi 60 p…®lam mb…®sevi, marsi gua 100…®n…® utu.‚ÄĚ  
\v 9 Iesus mem mb…®Ňčg…® gua kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúTh…®…®Ňčra ukuaraniiŇč iti, ana oragh…®ri.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus manmagh…® usuav…®ra aghunambara akaagha asi 
\r (Metiu 13.10-17 koma Luk 8.9-10) 
\p  
\v 10 Gumasi rako amisira av…®rara bar guesima, Iesus nomb…®re itima, an 12 p…®lam mb…®sevisir gumasi rako ana aghani itir gumasi, mee aŇčna aghunamana akamam mb…®n…®…®Ňčm mb…®um…®usua aŇčna azaaghi.  
\v 11 Mee aŇčna azarasima a kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGot ikaaŇčmaran geŇčga aniiŇčsima, gee ma mondusir akaa anda ikaaŇči. Ma mondusir akam khara Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthugh. K…® azenani itir gumasi rako amisi phura aghunambara akaar mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 12 Kamagha amuisima, ‚ÄėMee m…®ghas…®gh gan…®va, mee bigha thav ikeeŇčgem phat…®ghami. Mee iv…®ra m…®ghas…®gh oragh…®va, mee inderagh…®v…®ra akamam mb…®n…®…®Ňč thav ikeeŇčgem phat…®ghami. Mee amuava akaa v…®n…®…®Ňčgari ikeeŇčsi phat…®gha men navia aghavagharisi, Got meno othevir maghat…®si g…®na amandasi phat…®.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ \f * \fr 4:12 \ft Iesus Got…®n g…®n maŇčam…®usua gumasi rako amisir thevi phat…®. Marsi nori Got…®n g…®n maŇčani iph…®rph…®ri.\f* 
\s1 Uitir aghunamaŇčga asira akamam mb…®n…®…®Ňč 
\r (Metiu 13.18-23 koma Luk 8.11-15) 
\p  
\v 13 Ana akaman khav…®n mem mb…®Ňčg…® gua kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee uitir aghunamana akaman khav…®m mb…®n…®…®Ňč ikeeŇčsi phat…®sire? Gee manmagh…®ra igharisi aghunambar akaa tharsi ikeeŇčg…®ti?  
\v 14 Got…®na akam…® ukuragha arui gumagh a uitiro ov…®si ukurir gumaghan m…®na amui.  
\v 15 Gumasir marsi utuav…® iresir…® uitiro ov…®sir m…®na amui. Mee Got…®na akaava oraesima Satan…® uzuam…®ra zava mee oraesir Got…®n akaa, mena aghan anda vatoghi.  
\v 16 Gumasir marsi aŇčg…® itir…® unuagh…®naŇčgi iresir…® uitiro ov…®sir m…®na amui. Mee Got…®na akaava oraegha andavhagha bar inighinisi.  
\v 17 Men bii gueghiresi phat…®gha mamagha amuigha uthughun…® uruarani iti phat…®. Mee Got…®na akaar g…®n zuima, gumasir marsi mera afharavaghava os…®mnd…®sir meŇčga n…®ndima mee phura Gota thaghi.  
\v 18 Gumasir marsi umbuera atari itir…® unuagh…®naŇčgi iresir…® uitiro ov…®sir m…®na amui. Mee Got…®na akaava arasi.  
\v 19 Mee andava oraegha mee iv…®ra unuagh…®nan khav…®no os…®mnd…®siv…®usua n…®gh…®n…®ghava, aŇčg…®ro ov…®sira av…®rara niam…®usua khorigha amuir n…®gh…®n…®sigha amuava, unuagh…®nan khav…®n bisir av…®rar garava andavhagha in…®si. Bisir kharsir n…®gh…®n…®si zava Got…®n akaa disima anda aghaa oti phat…®.  
\v 20 Gumasir marsi unuagh…®nana aghuuŇčgi iresir…® uitiro ov…®sir m…®na amui. Mee Got…®na akaava oraegha andar…® usuiragha, andar g…®n zui tharsi mee aghaa oti. Marsi 30 p…®lan aghaeva atima, marsi 60 p…®lan aghaeva atima marsi gua 100…®n…® utu.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Lamana aŇčanara ana rananda 
\r (Luk 8.16-18) 
\p  
\v 21 Iesus kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGena th…®…®Ňčra lamaŇčga amborugha ana nigha ithaaŇčni ikh…®van ana avhara? O ana nigha akogh…®n apheeŇčn ana ananda? Bar phat…®! Gee aŇčra amborughuva ana nigh…®va azenan aŇčna aŇčanara ana ranandagh…®ri.  
\v 22 Kamagh…®ra mooŇčgamir bisi anda g…®na azenan otuivami. Bisigha amuigha anda ave tharsi anda iv…®ra g…®na azenan otuivami.  
\v 23 Th…®…®Ňčra ukuaraniiŇč iti, ana oragh…®ri.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 24 Am mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee orasir akaa gee inderagh…®v…®ra andava oragh…®va inderagh…®v…®ra andagh…® n…®gh…®n…®gh…®ri. Gee gumasigha amui mogh…®ra Got andar gee ikaragh…®va a nomthegh thove phorugh gera an…®…®Ňčga.  
\v 25 Got…®na akami ikeeŇčsi gumagha thav Got nomthegh ikhaaŇčmari tharsi phorugh aŇčra an…®Ňčga. Gumagh ikhaaŇčmaran sovange Got…®ni iti thav Got nomthegh aŇčna aghan noni ikhaaŇčmar nighemi.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 AfhueŇčsi aghaero ov…®sir aghunamana akam 
\p  
\v 26 Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGot kha bisigha ativamir…® uthughuno oth…®v kamagh…®n. Gumaghan mav aghaero ov…®si nigha unuagh…®nan anda ukuri.  
\v 27 Gumaghan khav anda ukunighava, r…®maŇčgarir akuava, aroer r…®kavighava arui. Ana aruima aghaero ov…®sir kharsi anda afhueŇčga aghuughi. Aghaero ov…®sir kharsi manmagh…®ra afhueŇčga aghuughi? Gumaghan khav ikeeŇčsi phat…®.  
\v 28 Unuagh…®nara aghaero ov…®sir kharsigha amuisima anda aghuuva mb…®sevi. Anda ufhuaragha afhueŇčga aghuu gua aŇčguu is…®gha ava gua ak…®mari otuivigha mb…®sevi.  
\v 29 Anda v…®sevigha aghae itima, gumaghan khav akos nighava andara akori. A ikaaŇči, aghae itima andara akoromir…® uthugho oto.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Mastet…®no ov…®ghan aghunamana akamaŇčga asi 
\r (Metiu 13.31-32 ko Luk 13.18-19 koma Metiu 13.34-35) 
\p  
\v 30 A nomthegha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe manmagh…®ra Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthughuno oth…®vham mb…®k…®mti? O, ee aghunamana akaman manav…®n aŇčm mb…®n…®…®Ňčgarir gun…®m mb…®k…®mti?  
\v 31 A mastet…®no ov…®ghan m…®n gari. Mastet…®n…® uzuirafariro ov…®si bar sovi. Igharisi thero ov…®si bar aŇčga afhiragha ikhevi.  
\v 32 Gumaghan mav ana ukunisima a g…®na aghuuva bar ikhevighava m…®gh…®ni itir…® uzuirafari bar andagha afhiragha bare ikhevi. Ani ikhevigha aŇčna aŇčguuri ikii nori amaeŇčsima ukuarasi zava ana aŇčguur r…®ghughana aveni ikha v…®koniri iŇčaari.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 33 Iesus men n…®gh…®n…®si uthusi utuir…®van m…®na amuira akaar av…®rar aghunambagha asava Got…®na akaar mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 34 Ana akaar gumasi rako amisi v…®Ňčg…®va m…®ghas…®gha aghunambara akaar mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi. A non suren gumasir phorugha mee norira ikhava a bisi v…®n…®…®Ňčgaria b…®gha mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi. 
\s1 Iesus…®m mb…®kemisima gamiiŇčni ikh…®v ko r…®ph…®raghirir r…®m…® aniiŇč phura am…®nat…® 
\r (Metiu 8.23-27 koma Luk 8.22-25) 
\p  
\v 35 Aron khav…®n am…®n ph…®raousuava amuima Iesus kamagh non suren gumasi v…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe r…®m…®n khava r…®tugh aŇčn muaaŇčmogh maŇčŇčaŇčga.‚ÄĚ  
\v 36 A kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeema gumasi rako amisi mb…®rogh…®ni ikhav…®re itima mee Iesus apheraghav itira akeman guavanaeŇčga muaaŇčmogh zui. AŇčgaeri igharis tharsi iv…®ra men phorugha muaaŇčmogh zui.  
\v 37 Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha zuima, gamiiŇčni ikh…®v r…®kavi. Uthughun khav…®n r…®p…®raghiri r…®m…® zava akemaŇčga afhims…®sima r…®m…® akemana aven gueghira, akemaŇčgi iz…®vasima, ana atam r…®m…®na aven meghiraousuava amui.  
\v 38 Akem meghiraousuava amuima, Iesusa akeman khav…®n g…®raŇčg…®ran aghoran mav nona aphanan aghorugha akui. AŇčn suren gumasi aŇčga aghuragha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumagh, ee g…®vaousuava amui! N…®…® em…®usua n…®gh…®n…®si, o phat…®?‚ÄĚ  
\v 39 Iesus r…®khavigha utugha gamiiŇč mbatogha, r…®p…®raghiri r…®m…® kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAŇčgo am…®ragh, in…®m…®re ikh…®…®!‚ÄĚ Am mb…®Ňčgeema, gamiiŇč am…®rasima, r…®m…® phurama am…®nat…®.  
\v 40 Iesus kamagh non suren gumasi v…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee thoghousua phuv…®ra atitiiŇči? Gee n…®ghn…®ghana aghavagharo othevigha kamagh…®re iti?‚ÄĚ  
\v 41 Mee bar ana atitiiŇčga kamagh norira nori v…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumaghan khav th…®…®Ňčra? GamiiŇč ko r…®p…®raghiri r…®m…® iv…®ram aŇčna akamam mbarasi!‚ÄĚ 
\c 5  
\s1 Iesus Gerasan gumaghan mav…®n…® unduur maghat…®sigha avarasima anda ana thaghi 
\r (Metiu 8.28-34 koma Luk 8.26-39) 
\p  
\v 1 Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha r…®m…®a r…®thugha muaaŇčmogh Gerasana aŇčanan oto.  
\v 2 Mee otuiva, Iesusa akema thaegha ataaŇčn anandima utuman maghat…®gh aphasasi gumaghan mav, a khuur…® uŇčuuni ikegha Iesus…® otuivousua zii.  
\v 3-4 A khuur…® uŇčuuni ikhava aŇčga akui. Mee uthusira av…®rara ukuaghaviir aŇčna agharaniiŇč ikhava, phiv…®sir aŇčn…® usuaniiŇč iti. Mee aniiŇč itima, a m…®ghas…®gha ukuaghaviir kharsir…® usuighava anda r…®ghoragh…®usuava aŇčn…® usuaniiŇč ikesir phiv…®ghaniiŇčm mb…®sogha aniia r…®ghoragh…®usui. Kamagha amuisima gumagha thav gumaghan khav…®n…® usuiragh ana ikh…®va aveeŇčgemi. Mee iv…®ra ukuaghaviir ana ikeghtima anda aŇčn…® usuiragham thughath…®gham phat…®ghami. Gumagha thav kha gumagh ana ikeghem thughat…®s phat…®.  
\v 5 A r…®maŇčgari rako aroer khuur…® uŇčuimba rako orasir phurama aruava mb…®gh…®rav…®ra d…®…®va aŇčg…®r nom mb…®kar…®gha r…®ghoragh…®usui. 
\p  
\v 6 A isaghuni ikha Iesus…®n ganigha akh…®ghavt…®gha aŇčm…®usua zava aŇčm mb…®n…®man noni it…®v…®nia r…®p…®ri.  
\v 7-8 Mauthughura Iesus kamagh…® utuman maghat…®gham mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® utuman maghat…®gh, n…®…® gumaghan khava thaegha ak…®ran z…®…®.‚ÄĚ Iesus kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeema, gumaghan khav…®m mb…®gh…®rav…®ra arava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúKha bisi bar andari iph…®ni iti Got…®n Otar Iesus, n…®…® manmagh na ramuam…®usua. K…® Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn…®m mb…®gh…®rav…®ra n…®…®na azaaghi, n…®…® naŇčga as…®ghas…®gha thaghri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 9 A kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeema Iesus kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® noni iz…®…® r…®mboru.‚ÄĚ Utuman maghat…®ghan khav ana ikaragha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe bar av…®rekevi, kamagha amuisi nani iz…®…® Av…®rira.‚ÄĚ  
\v 10 A Iesus igharisi aŇčana thav…®n mee amaaŇčn agharkuvigha Iesus…®na av…®gha aŇčga aghori. 
\p  
\v 11 Kha uthughun, mem mburogh…®re itiro oragh…®n mav daar av…®rire ikhava aphi.  
\v 12 Anda aphima, unduur maghat…®sir kharsi kamagh Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčg…®va aŇčga aghori, ‚ÄúN…®…® eem mb…®k…®m…®va ee amandaghtima ee maŇč…®va daar b…®sir muna andarsigha aphasaghami.‚ÄĚ  
\v 13 Mauthughura a mee amandasima unduur maghat…®sir kharsi gumaghan khava thaegha ak…®ran zegha guava daar b…®sigha aphasa. Daar av…®rir kharsi, andar r…®mbomboni 2,000…®na aghan gu. Mauthughura daa phuv…®ra akh…®r…®s…®igha gueghira avaran…® ukond…®ghan gueghirava r…®m…®na aven guegha r…®ma aphava ar…®…®ghire. 
\p  
\v 14 Mauthughura daar garir gumasi daava otuivisi bisir ganigha guava uŇčuimbari ikiir gua kha aŇčanani itir…® uŇčuimbar sovsegher guava kha otuivisi bisir gun…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi. Gumasi rako amisi bighan khav…®n ganam…®usua r…®khavigha zii.  
\v 15 Mee zava Iesus…®na aghan…® unduur maghat…®si aphasasir gumaghan garima, aŇčn n…®ghn…®gh nom inderasima, a non shaaria sharigha apheraghav iti. Mee aŇčn ganighava atitiiŇči.  
\v 16 Kha otuivisi bisir ganisi gumasi rako amisi, mee unduur maghat…®si aphasasir gumagha otosir bisir kharsir gun igharisi gumasi v…®Ňčgeeghi. Mee andar gun…®m mb…®Ňčg…® gua iv…®ra daava otosi bisir gun…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 17 Gumasi rako amisir kharsi bighan khav…® oraegha mee ma aŇčanambaaŇč thaegh maŇčam…®usua Iesus…® aghori. 
\p  
\v 18 Mem mb…®Ňčgeema, Iesus aŇčanan khava thaegh maŇčam…®usua akeman b…®rima unduur maghat…®si fhom aphasagha ikesi gumagh, Iesus…®n phorugh maŇčam…®usua mb…®gh…®rav…®ra aŇčga aghori.  
\v 19 An aŇčga aghorima, Iesus aŇčn th…®va kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® nomthegh nona andarsiv…®usua r…®phenan maŇč…®va Ikh…®v n…®…®na akuragha n…®…®Ňčga amuisir bisi andar gun mem mb…®k…®m…®va a iv…®ra bar n…®…®n…® ukuarukuvisi bisir gun mem mb…®k…®m.‚ÄĚ  
\v 20 Gumaghan khav ana oraegha guava Iesus aŇčna akurasir bisir gun Dekapolis…®n distrigh…®ni itir…® uŇčuimbar guava bar mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi. Gumasi rako amisir kharsi aŇčmba oraegha r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui. 
\s1 Iesusa aremisir guivan mav koma ar…®mar…®m itira amighan mav…®a amuisima aniiŇč nom indera 
\r (Metiu 9.18-26 koma Luk 8.40-56) 
\p  
\v 21 Iesus akem nigha nomthegha r…®m…®n khuaŇčmogh zee. A zegha r…®m…®na ataaŇčni itima gumasi rako amisira av…®rara zava ana akuva.  
\v 22-23 Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger r…®phenan bisir gari gumaghan mav, aŇčni iz…®…® Jairus, a zava, Iesus…®n garav aŇčn khoman nomb…® ukunigha kamagh phuv…®ra aŇčga aghori, ‚ÄúNan guiva aremighaousua aŇčn r…®ghor…®n k…®nare iti. N…®…® z…®va nona afhar…®n aŇčra ath…®ghtima aŇčna ar…®mar…®m g…®vagh nom ikaami.‚ÄĚ  
\v 24 Kamagha amuisima Iesus aŇčn phorugha zui. 
\p A zuima gumasi rako amisira av…®rara bar ana akuvaghava aŇčn g…®n zui.  
\v 25 Mee zuima men thooŇčn Ňčaanambatir ar…®mar…®m itira amighan mav iv…®ra men phorugha zui. Amighan khav Ňčaanambatir ar…®mar…®m aŇčni itima 12 p…®lan ombari g…®va.  
\v 26 A fhom…®ra nona ar…®mar…®ma g…®vaousuava ar…®mar…®a r…®k…®rir gumasiv…®usua zuima, mee aŇčna ar…®mar…®ma g…®vasi phat…®. Thighira am mb…®zagh…®n maghat…®gh nii. A nona ar…®mar…®m ana g…®vaousua phura nona aŇčg…®ro ov…®sir meŇčg…® uvhuesima aŇčna aŇčg…®ro ov…®si bar g…®va. Bisir kharsi aŇčna ar…®mar…®mana akuruvasi phat…®. Ana ar…®mar…®mi ikh…®va guav…®re iti.  
\v 27-28 A Iesusa amuisi bisira akamam mbaraegha, a kamaghi n…®gh…®n…®si, ‚ÄúK…® phura aŇčna ak…®rani iti shaaran kh…®ghtima nana ar…®mar…®m g…®vaghami.‚ÄĚ A kamaghi n…®gh…®n…®ghava anaaŇč ramuam…®usua. A gumasi rako amisir av…®rar g…®n zava mee munamaŇčga zava Iesus…®n shaaran…® usuira.  
\v 29 Amigh aŇčn shaaran…® usuiraghav…®ra, aŇčn…® Ňčaanambatir ar…®mar…®m phura r…®thugha gu. A nomb…®ra nomb…® oraegha ikaaŇči, aŇčm mb…®kar…®gh nom indera.  
\v 30 A kamagha amuim…®ra, Iesus uzuam…®ra nomb…®ra nomb…® orasi a Got gumasir ar…®mar…®a g…®vaousua aŇčga aniiŇčsi gamgaaŇč, aŇčm mb…®kar…®gha thaesi a ikaaŇči, nan gamgaaŇč iŇčaari. Mauthughura a ragha gumasi rako amisir garava mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúTh…®…®Ňčra nan shaaran kh…®…®?‚ÄĚ  
\v 31 Am mb…®Ňčgeema, aŇčn suren gumasi ana ikaragha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® garima, gumasi rako amisira av…®rara n…®…® akuvagha iti. Kamagha amuisima n…®…® thoghousua kamagha azaaghi, ‚ÄėTh…®…®Ňčra nan shaaran kh…®…®?‚Äô ‚ÄĚ  
\v 32 Mee kamagh Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima Iesus non shaaran kh…®si gumagh ikaaŇčm…®usua ighaghira garagharui.  
\v 33 A uruiav…®re itima, amighan khav aŇčm mbatosi bighan khav ikeeŇčga zava Iesus…®n khomani ir…®ghava, atitiiŇčga in…®gha guisimbaaŇčra aŇčm mbatosi bighaaŇčn gun aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 34 Am mb…®Ňčgeema, Iesus kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúNan guiv, n…®…® n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar nani iti. Kamagha amuisima n…®…®na ar…®mar…®m g…®va. N…®…® navana am…®Ňčnd…®ghan maŇč…®ri, n…®…®na ar…®mar…®man khav nomthegh n…®…® ramuighem phat…®ghami.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 35 Iesus amighan khav…®m mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima gumasir marsi Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger r…®phenan bisir garir gumagh, Jairus…®n r…®phenani ikegha zee. Mee zegha kamagh Jairus…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® os…®mnd…®ghan fh…®gh…®n gumagha ran…®…®Ňčva aŇčga aghora thaghri. N…®…®n guiva aremigha g…®va.‚ÄĚ  
\v 36 Mee kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeema Iesus mem mbaraegha kamagh Jairus…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® atitiiŇčn thaghri. N…®…® phura n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar nani ikh…®…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 37 AŇčn g…®na arui gumasi aŇčn phorugh maŇčam…®usuava amuima a men th…®va, Pita ri Jon koma aŇčn…® undooghan Jems, mera nigha mee zui.  
\v 38 Mee guava Jairus…® r…®phenan otuivigha Iesus gumasi rako amisiva arasima, mee bar azia n…®Ňčn…®…®Ňčni ikh…®va amui.  
\v 39 A mem…®usua aven guava kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee thoghousua azia n…®Ňčn…®…®Ňčni ikh…®va amui? Guivan khava aremisi phat…®. Ana akui.‚ÄĚ  
\v 40 A kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeema, mee aŇč r…®phovava akavar…® nori v…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe ikaaŇči, a guisimbaaŇčra aremi.‚ÄĚ Gumasi rako amisi kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeema a bar mem mbatuegha guivani inaghaves ko inaghamuuŇč nigha aŇčn suren gumaghan phunini ko mb…®kethav, mera aŇčn phorugha zui. A mee nigha mee guivan khum itira aŇčanana aven zui.  
\v 41 Mee guegha a guivana afharimuun…® usuragha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúTalita kum!‚ÄĚ Akaman khav…®m mb…®n…®…®Ňč kamagh iti, ‚ÄúGuivan sovange, k…® n…®…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, n…®…® r…®kavi!‚ÄĚ  
\v 42 An aŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima, guiv r…®khavigha utughava arui. AŇčno ombarir 12 p…®la. A r…®khavigha utughava aruima, mee kamagh guisimbaaŇčra r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui.  
\v 43 Mauthughura ana akamana aghavagharan guisimbaaŇčra mem mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGee bighan khav…®n gun igharisi gumagha thav…®m mb…®k…®ma thaghri.‚ÄĚ A kamagh mem mb…®Ňčg…®va aghaa thav aŇč ran…®…®Ňčm…®usua mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi. 
\c 6  
\s1 Iesus…®n…® uŇčuuna andarsi mee aŇčgi iph…®rph…®righa ak…®ran aŇčga ase 
\r (Metiu 13.53-58 koma Luk 4.16-30) 
\p  
\v 1 Iesus khagh thaegha non…® uŇčuun guavanandima aŇčn suren gumasi aŇčn phorugha zui.  
\v 2 Thighira, avhughususan…® uthugho otosima a Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger r…®phenana aven guava, gumasi rako amisir surea amui. Gumasi rako amisira av…®rara aŇčna akaava oraegha r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui. Mee r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuigha azaaghi, ‚ÄúKha gumagh a managha akaar kharsi nii? A managh n…®gh…®n…®sira aghuui nii? A iv…®ra managh kha bisigha amuir gamgaaŇč nii?  
\v 3 Ee ikaaŇči, khara phura r…®pheniri iŇčaarir gumagh. A Marian otar, a Jems ri Josev koma Judas ri Saimon, a mena aveeŇčnafhesra. AŇčn…® umbuaramisi en phorugha iti.‚ÄĚ Kamagha amuisima mee r…®mbovira akaar aŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®va navira averir aŇčga avhesi.  
\v 4 Mee avhesima, Iesus kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGot…®na akam nigha zii gumagh, a uŇčuimbari igharisi tharsir zuima, mee aŇčni iz…®…® ufhi. AŇčn…® uŇčuun ana andarsi, mee aŇčni iz…®…® ufhi phat…®. AŇčn phorugha r…®phenan…® uvav…®re iti tharsi iv…®ra aŇčni iz…®…® ufhi phat…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 Kamagha amuisima a uŇčuun khav…®n non gamgaaŇč kh…®vasi phat…®. A phura afhar…®n ar…®mar…® iti gumasir…® uvhovhera meŇčga ar…®sima, mena ar…®mar…® g…®va.  
\v 6 Mee n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar aŇčni iti phat…®sima, kamagha amuigha a r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui. 
\ms1 Iesus non gamgaaŇč khevima aŇčn suren gumasi inderagha ana ikeeŇčsi phat…® 
\mr (Sapta 6.6--8.21) 
\s1 Iesus…®m mb…®sevisir gumasir 12 p…®la, iŇčaarir meŇčga aniiŇčgava mee amanda 
\r (Metiu 10.5-15 koma Luk 9.1-6) 
\p Iesus…® uŇčuimbagha aruava gumasi rako amisir surea amui.  
\v 7 Iesus men surea amuava, mb…®sevisi gumasir 12 p…®lan d…®…®sima, mee aŇčm…®usua zesima, a mee akuvagha, mem mb…®Ňčg…®va mee amandi. Gumaghan phunini noniiŇč nigh maŇč…®ri, mamagha amuigha gumaghan phunini noniiŇč nigha zui. A non gamgaaŇčn mee raniiŇčtima mee iv…®ra unduur maghat…®si vatoghomi iz…®…®ri ikhaami.  
\v 8-9 Am mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®man khav…®n meŇčga amuighava mee amandi, ‚ÄúGee maaŇč…®, bisi tharsi noriv…®usua anda nia thaghri. Gee uvighan…® utuma thav ko mb…®thar thav koma aŇčg…®ro ov…®si nia thaghri. Gee nona aŇčgarir shaaria sharigh…®va, nomthegh shaara thav nia thaghri. Gee nona ashathevi ifhisira usuiragh maaŇč…®.  
\v 10 Gee kamagh ramuigh, maaŇč…®va uŇčuu thav…®n maŇč…®ti mee r…®phena thav…®n gee raniiŇčtima, gee r…®phenan khav…®re ikh…®…® maaŇč…®va, maŇčaŇčgamir…® uthughun gee uŇčuun khava tham…®ragh…®ri.  
\v 11 Gee kamagh…®ra ramu maaŇč…® uŇčuu thav…®n maŇč…®tima, mee gena agharkuvigh gee nigh no r…®phenir maŇčan agharkuvigh…®va, mee iv…®ra gem mb…®Ňčgera akaava oraghan agharkuvightima, gee kamagh…®ra ramu. Gee uŇčuun khava thaegh maŇčam…®usua nona aŇčgarir…®m mb…®nisi aphoegh…®va uŇčuun khava thaegh maaŇč…®. Gee kamagh ramuighti, mee ganighi ikeeŇčgemi, mee oth…®vhana aghuuŇčn geŇčga amuisi phat…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 A kamagh mem mb…®kemigha mee amandasima mee uŇčuimbar guava Got…®na akam…® ukura kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGee non navi igh…®ghiregh…®ri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 13 Mee kamagh mem mb…®Ňčg…®va, iv…®ra gumasir av…®rar…® unduur maghat…®si vathogha ar…®mar…®r gumasira av…®rara mb…®ruer mena aphanighi Ňčava meŇčga amuima, mee nom indera. 
\s1 Herot…®m mb…®kemisi mee Jon gumasi uruer gumaghan…® ufh…®ra r…®tu 
\r (Metiu 14.1-12 ko Luk 3.19-20 koma Luk 9.7-9) 
\p  
\v 14 Iesus bisira av…®rara amuisima aŇčni iz…®…® otogha ikhevisima, gumasira av…®rara ana ikaaŇči. Thighira kha aŇčanaŇčga ativasir gumagh, Herot aŇčm mbaraghi. Gumasir marsi kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúJon gumasi uruer gumagha aremigha nomthegha r…®kavi. Kamagha amuigha a kha bisigha amuir gamgaaŇč iti.‚ÄĚ  
\v 15 Igharis tharsi kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúA Elaija.‚ÄĚ Marsi kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúKhara Got…®na akam nigha zesi gumaghan mav, a fhom…®ra ikesir Got…®na akam nigha zesi gumasir m…®na amui.‚ÄĚ  
\v 16 Mee akaar kharsi v…®Ňčgeema, Herot andava araegha a ikaaŇči, a fhom…®ram mb…®kemisi mee ufhuaragha Jon…® ufh…®ra r…®tu. Kamagha amuisima a kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® fhom…®ram mb…®kemisima, mee gumaghan mav Jon, gumasi uruer gumaghan…® ufh…®ra r…®tusima, a nomthegha r…®kavi.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 17-20 Herot kamagha amuigha a ikaaŇči, a fhom…®ra non…® undooghan Filiv…® ot…®gh…®n aŇčna amuuŇč Herodias ana nigha aŇčga ath…®. Jon m…®ghas…®gha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúHerot, n…®…® oth…®vhan maghat…®gha amuava non…® undoogha ot…®gh…®n aŇčna amuuŇč nigha aŇčga ath…®…®.‚ÄĚ Jon kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeema, Herodias guisimbaaŇčra nav aŇčn siima, kamagha amuigha a Jon…®m mb…®sueghti ana aremighaousua phuv…®ra Herot…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi. Am mb…®Ňčgeema, Herot Herodias vhusvhuisi mogh…®n ramuan agharkuvighava, a non gumasir marsi v…®kemisima mee Jon…®n…® usuiragha ana nigha r…®v…®nan kh…®rth…®gha ath…®. Herot ikaaŇči, Jon Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn inderasi gumaghara ano othevira aghuuira amui. Kamagha amuisima Herot aŇčna avhighavhiighava, ana nigha inderaghav…®ra aŇčn gari. Herot iv…®ra Jon…®m mb…®Ňčgera akaava oraegha n…®gh…®n…®sira av…®rara amuava, aŇčna akaava oraghaousua vhusvhusi. 
\p  
\v 21 Herodias thighira Jon…®m mb…®sueghti ana aremighaousua utuav…® oto. Herot aŇčni inaghamuuŇč aŇčm mbatesir…® uthugho otosima, a kha uthughi n…®ghn…®gha ishamani ikh…®va amui. Herodias Jon…®m mb…®soghomir…® uthugh thighira oto. Herot ishaman khav…® amuava, noni iŇčaariri ikiir garir gumasiri ikii, rako nom mb…®zorsir gumasir garir gumasiri ikii, rako Galilin distrigh…®ni iti gumasiri ikii, a men d…®…®sima mee aŇčn phorugh ramam…®usua zee.  
\v 22 Mee zegha isham aphima Herodias…®n guiv zava mee aphira aŇčanan gugha mem mb…®n…®mani izi. A izima, Herot…®n phorugha zeghava aphir gumasi, mee aŇčni igh…®…®n ganigha guisimbaaŇčra aŇčni igh…®…®n vhusvhusigha bar aŇčgi iphui. Mee bar aŇčgi iphuigha, mamagha amuigha Herot kamagh guivani ikamam mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® mana bighan vhusvhusigh…®v, nana azaaŇč. K…® ma bighan n…®…® ran…®…®Ňčga.‚ÄĚ  
\v 23 A kamagh aŇčm mb…®kemigha, akama r…®Ňčg…®rana aghavagharan kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® guisimbaaŇčra n…®…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, n…®…® bigha thav…®n vhusvhusigh…®va, nam mb…®k…®m. K…® garir bisi n…®…® andar vhusvhusigh…®va, n…®…® nam mb…®k…®mtima k…® ar…®ghara anda biigh…®va, tharsir n…®…® ran…®…®Ňčga.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 24 Guivani ikaman khava akaman khav…® oraegha, ak…®rasegha gua kamagh noni inaghamuum mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúInaghamuuŇč, k…® theghan bighousua azaaŇčti?‚ÄĚ Mauthughura aŇčni inaghamuuŇč kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúJon, gumasi uruer gumaghana aphanam…®usua ana azaaŇčtima, an aŇčna aphan nigh n…®ra aniiŇčg…®ri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 25 Guivan khava akaman khav…® oraegha, uzuam…®ra nomthegha aven gugha kamagh Herot…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® thighira Jon, gumasi uruer gumaghana aphan nigh ithaaŇč thav rat…®gh nara aniiŇčg…®ri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 26 Am mb…®Ňčgeema, Herot aŇčm mbaraeghava aŇčn nav bar aŇčno osemi. A ufhuaragha akama r…®Ňčg…®rana aghavagharam mb…®Ňčgeema aŇčn phorugha aphir gumasi aŇčm mbaraghi. Kamagha amuisima an aŇčna azaaŇčs…®gha athoeghem thughat…®s phat…®.  
\v 27 Herot aŇčm mbaraghav…®re ikha, akamana aghavagharan nom mb…®zorughan gumagham mb…®kemigha ana amandasima a gua r…®v…®nan k…®rth…®ghana aven gueghir…®gha Jon…® ufh…®rar r…®tu.  
\v 28 A Jon…® ufh…®rar r…®thugha aŇčna aphan nigha ithaaŇčn mav…® ath…®gha ana nigha zava guivan khav…® aniiŇčsima ana na nigha guava noni inaghamuuŇčga an…®…®Ňči. 
\p  
\v 29 Gumughun Jon…®n suren gumasi aŇčno ovhevheeŇčna akamam mbaraegha zava aŇčn khum nigha gua ana umogh…® ath…®. 
\s1 Iesus aghaer 5,000…®n gumasigha an…®ndi 
\r (Metiu 14.13-21 ko Luk 9.10-17 koma Jon 6.1-13) 
\p  
\v 30 Gumughun Iesus…®m mb…®sevisir gumasi nomthegha zegha aŇčna aghan nori akuvaghav iti. Mee aruava amuisi bisi rako, gumasir surea amuisira akaar gun Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 31 Kha uthughun gumasi rako amisira av…®rara mem…®usua za zuima, mee ramaŇčgamir…® uthugh phat…®. Kamagha amuisima Iesus kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee norira nan phorugh maŇč…®va gumasi iti phat…®sira aŇčanan maŇč…®va ee thange avughusuami.‚ÄĚ  
\v 32 A kamagh mem mb…®Ňčg…®va mee norira akem nigha gumasi iti phat…®sira aŇčanan mav…®n zui. 
\p  
\v 33 Mee zuima, gumasi rako amisira av…®rara men ganigha mee ikaaŇči. UŇčuimbari iti gumasi rako amisi bar men…® ufhuaraghav…®ra akh…®r…®siigha gua mee zuira aŇčanan otuivi.  
\v 34 Mee gua mb…®keeŇčn guegha Iesus gumasi rako amisir av…®ran garima, mee guisimbaaŇčra bar av…®rekevi. A men garima, mee sivsiviir m…®na amui, mee gueeŇč khekhaeŇčsi phat…®, mee phura asasir m…®na arui. A kamagh bar men…® ukuarukuvi. Kamagha amuigha a bisira av…®rara men surea amui.  
\v 35 Am mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima, aro gevima aŇčn suren gumasi aŇčm…®usua za kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúKhara gumasi iti phat…®sira aŇčan, aro gevi.  
\v 36 N…®…® gumasi rako amisi amandaghti, mee maaŇč…® kha aŇčanani itir…® uŇčuimba rako aghangera itir…® uŇčuimbar sovsegher maŇč…®va mee ramam…®usua nori vagha aghaeghu uvhuesami.‚ÄĚ  
\v 37 Mem mb…®kemisima a mee ikaragha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee nori aghae tharsir mee ran…®…®Ňč.‚ÄĚ A mem mb…®kemisima mee kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe mem…®usua uvisir…® uthughu uvhuesamira aŇčg…®ro ov…®si anda 200t…® utu. Ee anda nigh, maaŇč…®, mem…®usua uvisir…® uthughu uvhuesigh mee ran…®…®Ňčm…®usua, n…®…® vhusvhuisi o?‚ÄĚ  
\v 38 Iesus mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúGee manmagh…®ra uvisir…® uthuu iti? Gee maaŇč…® gan.‚ÄĚ Am mb…®kemisi, mee gua ganigha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe uvisir…® uthuur 5 p…®la koma os…®ran phuninira khari iti.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 39-40 Mauthughura Iesus mem mb…®kemisi mee gumasi rako amisi v…®Ňčgeema, mee norira nori is…®gha iz…®gh…®nani iph…®na apiigha. Mee nori isiragha phosigha amuigha apiigha marsi 50 p…®lan amemeeŇčn apiighi, marsi 100 p…®lan amemeeŇčn apiigha gue.  
\v 41 Mee apiighav itima, Iesus uvisir…® uthuur 5 p…®la koma os…®ran phunini nighava, iph…®n ovheen garav Got…®m mb…®nambagha uvisir…® uthuua b…®…®gh…®usue. Iesus non suren gumasi v…®Ňčgeema, mee anda nia, gumasi rako amisi meŇčga an…®ndi. A iv…®ra os…®rani phorugha b…®…®gh…®usuesima, mee anda nigha, meŇčga an…®ndi.  
\v 42 Gumasi rako amisir kharsi bar amegha, navi bar iz…®va.  
\v 43 Men navi bar iz…®vasima Iesus…®n suren gumasi, mee thaesira aghaero othevi nigha 12 p…®la ak…®ragha aghuisima, anda bar iz…®va.  
\v 44 Aghae amesi gumasir r…®mbomboni gua 5,000…®n…® utu. 
\s1 Iesus r…®m…®ni iph…®n…® utuiva zui 
\r (Metiu 14.22-36 koma Jon 6.16-21) 
\p  
\v 45 Gumasi rako amisi aghae amesima, Iesus kamagh non suren gumasira afh…®r…®gha kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGee akeman b…®nigh…®va ufhuaragh Betsaidan…® uŇčuun muaaŇčmogh maaŇč…®. K…® nomb…®re ikh…®va gumasi rako amisi amandaghtima mee nomthegh non…® uŇčuimbar maŇčŇčaŇčga.‚ÄĚ  
\v 46 A mee amandasi, mee guesima, a Got…®n phorughum mb…®k…®mam…®usua oragh…®n guavanambo.  
\v 47 Kha uthughun am…®n ph…®rima, mena akem r…®m…®n thooŇčni itima, Iesus nomb…®ra ataaŇčni iti.  
\v 48 A ikhava non suren gumasir garima, gamiiŇčna aghavaghar zava mena akemaŇčg…® uvhaaghi. Mee aghosava amua iŇčaarani ikh…®va amuava gamiiŇčn phorugha mee nori vathosi. Am…®ni itiisuava amuima, Iesus r…®m…®ni iph…®n…® utuiva mem…®usua zui. A gua meŇčgi ind…®ragh maŇčam…®usuava amuima,  
\v 49-50 mauthughura mee aŇčn garima, a r…®m…®ni iph…®n…® utuiva zuima, mee kamagh…® n…®gh…®n…®si, ‚ÄúKhara ti asaaŇč thavti.‚ÄĚ Mee n…®ghn…®ghan khav…® amuava, bar aŇčn ganigha phuv…®ra atitiiŇčga araaghi. Mee araema, a uzuam…®ra kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee gamgaeŇčgiri, k…®ra khara. Gee atitiiŇčn thaghri!‚ÄĚ  
\v 51-52 A kamagh mem mb…®Ňčg…®va, mem mbath…®gh…®n akemana aven gusima, gamiiŇč phura r…®thugha gu. Iesus 5,000…®n gumasi uvisir…® uthuur meŇčga aniiŇčsi, mee anda amesima, mee bighan khav…®n ganigha, thange ikeeŇčsi bar phat…®. Men navia aghavagharigha n…®gh…®n…®si othevigha bar isaghure iti. Kamagha amuigha mee bisir kharsighi n…®gh…®n…®ghava guisimbaaŇčra r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui. 
\p  
\v 53 Gumughun Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha r…®m…®n muaaŇčmogh guegha, guava Genesaret…®n…® uŇčuun otuivigha, akemi ike.  
\v 54 Mee akemi ikegha ataaŇčn anandima, gumasi rako amisi Iesus…®n garav…®re ikha ana ikaaŇči.  
\v 55 Mee ana ikeeŇčga, gumasi rako amisi Iesus itira aŇčanam mbaraegha, akh…®r…®s…®gha aŇčanan khav…® aruava nona ar…®mar…®r gumasi nia mee akhuriigha ariigha mee nia Iesus…®usua zii.  
\v 56 Iesus…® uŇčuimbari ikii rako uŇčuimbar…® undoosi rako uruarir…® uŇčuimba andar zui. A zuir…® uŇčuimbar kharsi mee oth…®vhan khav…®ra amui, mee ar…®mar…®r gumasi nigha zava uŇčuun thooŇčn anda ar…®ghava, aŇčga aghora kamagh…®usue, a men m…®rat…®ghtima, ar…®mar…® iti tharsi aŇčn shaarana avaraniiŇčn kh…®skh…®sami. Gumasi rako amisi aŇčn shaaran kh…®si tharsi, mena ar…®mar…® gevi. 
\c 7  
\s1 Got…®n othevi Judarir avaviro othevigha afhira 
\r (Metiu 15.1-9) 
\p  
\v 1 FarisiiŇčn gumasir marsi rako Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasir marsi, mee Jerusalem…®ni ikegha, zeghirava, Iesus…®usua zava ana akuva.  
\v 2 Mee za ikha garima, Iesus…®n suren gumasir marsi mena avaviro othevir…® usuiraghav…®re ikha afhari uruegha aghae aphi phat…®. Mee phura aghae aphi.  
\v 3 FarisiiŇčn kharsi koma igharisi Judarir gumasi rako amisi bar, mee nona avaviro othevir…® usuiraghav…®re ikhava, mee afhari uruava aphi. Mee phura aghae raman thughat…®s phat…®.  
\v 4 Mee iv…®ra phogh…®n nigha ziir aghae, mee anda raman thughat…®s phat…®. Mee ufhuaragh anda uruegh…®va anda ramaŇčga. Mee iv…®ra nona avaviro othevir av…®rar marsi phorugha usuiragha kh…®ghav…®re iti. Mee phura aghae ishamigh rameghem thughat…®s phat…®ghami. Mee ufhuaragh nom mb…®ne rako ithaarigha, baghaa rako apiisira akosi, uruegh…®va mee aghae ishamaŇčga.  
\v 5 Kamagha amuisi, FarisiiŇč rako Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi, mee Iesus…®na azaaghi, ‚ÄúManmagha amuigha n…®…®n suren gumasi ena avaviro othevir g…®n maaŇč…® afhari uruani iph…®rph…®righa, phura aghae aphi?‚ÄĚ  
\v 6 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus mee ikaragha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee norira norir khorigha amuir gumasira. Got…®na akam nigha zesi gumagh Aisaia, a guisimbaaŇčra gee amuiro othevir gun…®m mb…®Ňčg…®va kamagh os…®ri, ‚ÄėGumasi rako amisir kharsi, mee nona akaa thoorir nani iz…®…® ufhi, men navi rako n…®gh…®n…®si bar isaghuni iti.  
\v 7 Mee gumasira akaar norir surea amua norir khorigha amua kamagh…®usue, khara Got…®na akam. Kamagha amuigha, mee nani iz…®…® guisimbaaŇčra ana ufhi phat…®.‚Äô  
\v 8 Gee kamagha amua, Got…®na akaa, gee anda thaegha, nona avaviro othevi, andar…® usuragha aghavaghari.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 9 Am mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee kamagh…®usue, gee oth…®vhana aghuuŇčga amua Got…®n akaa thaegha nono othevir g…®n zui. Geno othevir kharsi bar maghat…®ghi.  
\v 10 Moses fhom…®ra kamagh…®m mb…®kemi, ‚ÄėGee noni inasi rako inaghamuuira akaava oraegh mena apheeŇčni ikh…®va, gumagha thava akaman maghat…®gha thav noni inaghaves ko inaghamuum mb…®kemighti, gee gumaghan khav…®m mb…®sueghtima ana aremigh…®ri.‚Äô  
\v 11 Gee kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄėGumagha thav noni inaghamuuŇč ko inaghaves…®na akuruvaghaousua aŇčg…®ro ov…®si rar…®ghan n…®gh…®n…®ighava g…®n a nomthegha kamagha aniiŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAŇčgona akuruvaghaousua ath…®si aŇčg…®ro ov…®si, aŇčgo marik…®…®. Kha anda nigh Got ran…®…®Ňčgami.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô  
\v 12 Gee kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeema, gumaghan khav bigha thav noni inaghamuuŇč ko inaghaves…®na akurasi phat…®.  
\v 13 Gee kamagha amuava, nona avavi nisiro othevir g…®n gua, anda igharisi gumasigha an…®ndi. Gee othevir kharsigha amua, Got…®n othevia thaegha, nona avaviro othevi ufhuaraghav…®ra anda ar…®si. Gee Got…®na akamaŇčga amuima a phura bigh…®n magh…®. Gee amuir bisir av…®rar marsi iv…®re iti.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn maghatiisir bisi, Iesus anda v…®Ňčgeeghi 
\r (Metiu 15.10-20) 
\p  
\v 14 Iesus nomthegha nomb…®na aghani iti gumasi rako amisir d…®…®sima, mee aŇčm…®usua zima, a kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee bar nam mbaraegh…®va nana akaar kharsi, inderagh…®v…®ra anda ikeeŇčg…®ri.  
\v 15-16 Bigha thava ak…®rani ikegh…®va gumaghan navana aven meghir…®gh aŇčn ramuighti, a Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn maghatiighem phat…®. Phat…®, gumaghan navana aveni ikegha ak…®ran zesi bisi, aŇčn ramuightima, a Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn maghatiighemi.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 17 Iesus akaar kharsir gumasi rako amisira av…®rara mb…®kemigha, mee thaegha guava r…®phenana aven gusima, aŇčn suren gumasi aghunamana akamam mb…®n…®…®Ňč mbaaŇčm…®usua aŇčna azaaghi.  
\v 18-19 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEei! Gee oŇčanisire? Gee iv…®ra akaman khav inderaghav…®ra ana ikeeŇčsi phat…®sire? Gee bighan khav ikeeŇčsire? Aghaa thav guisimbaaŇčra gumaghan navana aven meghir…®gh ikeghem thughat…®s phat…®. Anda aŇčn navana aven meghir…®gh…®v, aŇčn…® umuun meghir…®ghtima a g…®na andar avighemi. Kamagha amuisi gumagha aphir bigha thav ak…®rani ikegh aŇčna akamndooŇčniiŇč ko umuun meghir…®gh…®v, aŇčn…® umu ramuightima a Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn maghatiighem thughat…®s phat…®.‚ÄĚ Iesusa akamana aghavagharan kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, aghae bar Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn bar indera. Or…®r…®vi phat…®.  
\v 20 Am mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumaghan navana aveni ikegha ak…®ran zesi bisi, anda othevir maghat…®si, anda aŇčga amuima, aŇčn navana avee Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn maghat…®.  
\v 21 Gumaghan navana aveni ikegha ak…®ran zesira othevi khara, n…®gh…®n…®sir maghat…®si, gumasi rako amisi atamatam norir phorughava akui, bisi okeeghi, gumasi v…®sosi anda ar…®ghiri,  
\v 22 pharaghamuui norir okeeghi, mb…®gh…®rav…®ra bisir vhusvhusi, igharisi gumasi meŇčga as…®ghas…®ghaousua n…®gh…®n…®si, khoriro othevi, ameri phat…®siro othevir maghat…®si, bisivagha nav oseeghi, igharisi gumaghani iz…®…®ra afharavasi, nomb…®ra nomb…® ufhi, oŇčanisiro othevi,  
\v 23 othevir maghat…®sir kharsi bar navana aveni ikegha ak…®ran za, gumagha amuima a Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn maghat…®.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Fonisiana aŇčanana amighan mav n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar Iesus…®ni iti 
\r (Metiu 15.21-28) 
\p  
\v 24 Iesus Genesareta thaegha Tair…®n…® uŇčuuni ikh…®van aŇčanan gu. A gumasi rako amisi ana ikhaaŇčgamim mbaaŇčn aŇčna agharkuvigha, mondugha guava r…®phenan mav…®na aven gugha mondusi phat…®. Mee bar ikaaŇči, a r…®phenana aveni iti.  
\v 25 A r…®phenan khav…®ni itima, utuman maghat…®gh aphasasir guivani inaghamuuŇč, a Iesus zesir aror…® oraegha, uzuam…®ra aŇčm…®usua zava aŇčn aŇčgariri ir…®.  
\v 26 Amighan khav, aŇčni inaghamuuŇč Fonisiana aŇčanan aŇčm mbate. A Sirian distrigh…®ni ikh…®vana aveni iti. A GrighiiŇčna akamam mb…®Ňčgeeghi. A non guiva aphasasir…® utuman maghat…®ghan khav…® avharaghaousua Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčg…®va aŇčga aghori.  
\v 27 Am mb…®Ňčgeema, Iesus kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe ufhuaragh boorir aghae mee raniiŇčti, mee ramaŇčga. Oth…®vhan maghat…®gh, k…® boorir aghae nigh afhee v…®k…®naŇčga.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 28 Am mb…®Ňčgeema amigh kamagh Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúIkh…®v, K…® ikaaŇči, afhee iv…®ra boorir akogh…®n apheeŇčni iresir aghae v…®zuii aphi.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 29 Am mb…®Ňčgeema Iesus kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…®m mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®m indera. Kamagha amuisi n…®…® nomthegh no r…®phenan maaŇč…®. Utuman maghat…®ghan khav n…®…®n guiva thaegha ak…®ran zee.‚ÄĚ  
\v 30 Ana aŇčm mb…®kemisima, a nomthegha no r…®phenan gua garima, aŇčn guiv nona akoghi ir…®ghav iti. Mauthughura an aŇčn ganigha ikaaŇči, utuman maghat…®ghan khav ana thaegha ak…®ran gu. 
\s1 Iesus gumaghan…® ukuaraniiŇč oŇčanisi mav…®n akurasima a indera 
\p  
\v 31 Iesus r…®khavigha Tair…®n…® uŇčuum mb…®rogha thaegha, guava Saidon…®n…® uŇčuun otogha guava, Dekapolis…®n distrigh…®n otogha gua, Galilin r…®m…®m mb…®rogh…®n gueghir…®.  
\v 32 A gusima, gumasir marsi gumaghan…® ukuaraniiŇč oŇčanisi mav nigha Iesus…®usua zii. A iv…®ram mb…®z…® osemigha inderaghav…®ram mb…®Ňčge phat…®. Mee zegha afhar…®n aŇčra r…®ghaousua Iesus…® aghori.  
\v 33 Am mb…®Ňčgeema Iesus gumaghan khav nigha gumasira av…®rara thaegha aniiŇč noniiŇčra mb…®Ňč…®niiŇčn gugha, a nona afhar…®n gumaghan…® ukuaraniiŇčga ath…®gha aniiŇč asigharafha, a magh…®ra nona afhar…®n…® ufheeniiŇčgi ipharigha aŇčm mb…®zaan kh…®…®.  
\v 34 Mauthughura Iesus iph…®no ovheen garav, gumaghan khav…®usua nav biigha arava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEfata!‚ÄĚ Akaman khav…®m mb…®n…®…®Ňč kamagh gu, ‚ÄúUkuighir…®gh…®ri!‚ÄĚ  
\v 35 Iesus kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima, aŇčn…® ukuarani ukuighir…®. Mauthughura aŇčm mb…®z…® mb…®gh…®v…®gh…®ghi. A inderaghav…®ra bisi v…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 36 Iesusa akamana aghavagharan bighan khav…®n gun…®m mb…®k…®man mee r…®ghorigharui. A mee r…®ghorigharuisima mee nomthegha phuv…®ra bighan khav…®n gun…®m mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re iti.  
\v 37 Mee akaman khav…®m mb…®Ňčgeema, gumasi rako amisir kharsi aŇčm mbaraegha guisimbaaŇčra r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuigha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumaghan khav ana amuir bisi anda bar indera. A ukuari oŇčanisi tharsigha amuima, mee nomthegha orasi. Am, mb…®zeri osemisi tharsigha amuima, mee nomthegha inderaghav…®ra bisi v…®Ňčgeeghi.‚ÄĚ 
\c 8  
\s1 Iesus aghaer 4,000…®n gumasi rako amisigha an…®ndi 
\r (Metiu 15.32-39 koma Metiu 16.1-4) 
\p  
\v 1 Kha uthughun gumasi rako amisir av…®rari igharis tharsi nori akuvaghav iti. Mee ramaŇčgamir aghae phat…®. Kamagha amuisima Iesus non suren gumasir d…®…®sima mee aŇčm…®usua zima a kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúGumasi rako amisir kharsi, mee nan phorugh aron phunini ko mb…®kethav…®ni itima, aghae mange othevisima mb…®tii mena azi, kamagha amuisima k…® men…® ukuarukuvi.  
\v 3 Gumasir marsi isaghuni ikegha zee. Kamagha amuisi k…® mee amandaghtima mem mb…®tiir navira nori non…® uŇčuimbar maŇč…®va ar…®masi meŇčgi ighutima mee iraami.‚ÄĚ  
\v 4 Am mb…®kemisima aŇčn suren gumasi aŇčna akam ikara, ‚ÄúEe gumasi iti phat…®sira aŇčanan khav…®ni iti. Ee managh membagha uvisir…® uthuu nigh mee ran…®…®Ňčti?‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 Mee kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeema Iesus kamagh mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúGee manmagh…®ra uvisir…® uthuu iti?‚ÄĚ Mee ana ikaragha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚Äú7 p…®la.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 6 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus unuagh…®nara apiighousua gumasi rako amisi v…®kemisi mee apiigha. Mauthughura a 7 p…®la uvisir…® uthuu nigha Got…®m mb…®nambagha anda b…®…®gh…®usuegha, gumasi rako amisir an…®…®Ňčm…®usua non suren gumasigha aniiŇčsima mee andar meŇčga an…®ndi.  
\v 7 Mee iv…®ra os…®rir sovsegher move iti. A iv…®ra andavhagha Got…®m mb…®nambagha andar mee ran…®…®Ňčm…®usua non suren gumasi v…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 8 Gumasi rako amisira av…®rara mee amegha bar iz…®va. G…®n aŇčn suren gumasi aghaero othevi mee tham…®raesi tharsi, mee anda nigha 7 p…®la ak…®rari ikhiigha aghuisima, anda iz…®va.  
\v 9 Uthughun khav…®ni itir gumasi rako amisir r…®mbomboni 4,000…®na aghan gu. Mee amesima, a mee amandasi, mee non…® uŇčuimbar gue.  
\v 10 Mee zuima, a non suren gumasir phorugha akeman b…®nigha, Dalmanutana aŇčanan gue. 
\p  
\v 11 Mee guesima FarisiiŇč zegha khoruo amuir azaaŇčs…®sir Iesus…®a amui. Gota aghavagharan aŇčra raniiŇčti, a non gamgaaŇčn bigha thav…® ramuightima mee ganighi ikeeŇčg…®m mb…®k…®maŇčga, ‚ÄúGot guisimbaaŇčra ana amanda.‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 Mem mb…®kemisima a men khoruo amuir azaaŇčs…®sir kharsighi iph…®rph…®righa ughurii usuegha, mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee thighira khari iti gumasi rako amisi, thoghousua bisigha amuir gamgaaŇč kh…®vaousua nana azaaghi? K…® guisimbaaŇčra gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, Got kha bisigha amuir gamgaaŇčno oth…®vha thav…®n gen kh…®vagham thughath…®s phat…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 13 A mem mb…®kemigha a mee thaegha nomthegha akemana anambogha, r…®m…®n muaaŇčmogh gu. 
\s1 FarisiiŇč rako Herot…®n iis…®n aghunamana akam 
\r (Metiu 16.5-12) 
\p  
\v 14 Mee gua Iesus…®n suren gumasi uvisir…® uthuur n…®ghn…®gh oŇčanigha gue. Mee uvighan…® utuman…® uvav…®ra nisima a men phorugha akemani iti.  
\v 15 Thighira Iesusa akamana aghavagharan kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee inderagh…®v…®ra noriv…®usua gan! Gee inderagh…®v…®ra FarisiiŇčn iis ko Herot…®n iis…®usua phorugh inderaghav…®ra gan…®ri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 16 Iesus mem mb…®kemisima, mee kamagh norira nori v…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe uvighan…® utuma thav nigha zesi phat…®sima, kamagha amuisima an eem mb…®Ňčgeeghi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 17 Mee norira nori v…®Ňčgeema, Iesus mem mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…® ikeeŇčga kamagh mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúGee thoghousua kamagh…®usue, ee uvighan…® utuma thav nigha zesi phat…®? Eei, gee kha amui bisir garava anda iŇčgaere? Gee thighari inderagh…®v…®ra anda ikaaŇčtire? Gen navia aghavagharigha n…®gh…®n…®si othevigha bar isaghure iti.  
\v 18 Gee ar…®masi ikha, garir phat…®sire? Gee ukuari ikha, orasi phat…®sire? Gee bisir kharsighi n…®gh…®n…®si phat…®sire?  
\v 19 Gee, k…® uvisir…® uthuur 5 p…®la b…®…®gh…®usuegha geŇčga aniiŇčsima, gee 5,000…®n gumasigha aniiŇčsima, mee anda apha iz…®vagha, thaesiro othevi gee andar manmagh…®ra ak…®ragha aghui?‚ÄĚ Mee kamagh ane ikara, ‚ÄúEe 12 p…®la ak…®ragh aghui.‚ÄĚ  
\v 20 A nomthegha kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® uvisir…® uthuur 7 p…®la b…®…®gh…®usuegha geŇčga aniiŇčsima, gee 4,000…®n gumasi rako amisigha aniiŇčsima, mee anda apha iz…®vasi gee andaro othevir ak…®rar manmagh…®ra aghui?‚ÄĚ Mee kamagha ana ikara, ‚ÄúEe 7 p…®la ak…®rari ikhiigha aghui.‚ÄĚ  
\v 21 Mee kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeema, a kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGii, gee thighar bisi ikaaŇčtire.‚ÄĚ 
\ms1 Iesus non suren gumasir surea amui 
\mr (Sapta 8.22--10.52) 
\s1 Iesus Betsaidan gumaghan ar…®maghan thughaniiŇčm mb…®zesi mav…®n akurasi, ana ar…®maghaniiŇč nom indera 
\p  
\v 22 Mee Betsaidan guesima, gumasir marsi gumaghan ar…®maghan thughaniiŇčm mb…®zesi mav nigha, Iesus…®usua zii. Mee zegha afhar…®n aŇčra r…®ghaousuava Iesus…® aghori.  
\v 23 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus gumaghan ar…®maghan thughaniiŇčm mb…®zesi thav…®na afharimuun…® usuragha, ana nigha uŇčuua thaegha ak…®ran gu. AniiŇč ak…®ran gugha, Iesus gumaghan ar…®maghaniiŇčgi ipharigha nona afharimuun aŇčni iph…®a ath…®gha kamagh aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® bigha thav…®n gari?‚ÄĚ  
\v 24 Ana aŇčm mb…®kemisima gumaghan khav khogha garava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAŇčre, k…® garima, gumasi ther m…®n garava arui.‚ÄĚ  
\v 25 Mauthughura Iesus nomthegha nona afharimuun aŇčn ar…®maghaniiŇčn…® usuirasima, gumaghan ar…®maghaniiŇč ukuighir…®sima, a nom inderagh…®v…®ra bisir gari.  
\v 26 A garima, Iesus ana amandagha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® nomthegh…®va uŇčuun khav…®na aven maŇčan thaghri. N…®…® nor r…®phenan maaŇč…®ri.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Pita Iesus…®n gun…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi 
\r (Metiu 16.13-20 koma Luk 9.18-21) 
\p  
\v 27 Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha r…®khavigha Sisariafilipain…® uŇčuuna aghani itir…® uŇčuimbar sovsegher zui. Mee gua a utuav…®n mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúGumasi rako amisi th…®…®Ňčra naŇčga ar…®si?‚ÄĚ  
\v 28 Mee ana ikaragha, ‚ÄúMarsi kamagh…®usue, n…®…® Jon, gumasi uruer gumagh. Igharisi gumasi kamagh…®usue, n…®…® Got…®na akam nigha zesi gumagh Elaija. Marsi kamagh…®usue, n…®…® fhom…®ra ikesir Got…®na akam nigha zesi gumaghan mav.‚ÄĚ  
\v 29 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúGeegha? Gee th…®…®Ňčra naŇčga ar…®si?‚ÄĚ A mem mb…®kemisima Pita kamagh ana ikara, ‚ÄúN…®…® Krais, Got nom ee niam…®usua mb…®sevisir gumagh.‚ÄĚ  
\v 30 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima, Iesusa akamana aghavagharan kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee nan gun gumagha thav…®m mb…®k…®ma thaghri, k…® th…®…®Ňčra.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus nono ovhevheeŇčna akam koma nomthegh…® r…®kavamir mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®maŇčga amui 
\r (Metiu 16.21-28 koma Luk 9.22-27) 
\p  
\v 31 Iesus men surea amuava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumasir Otar bar…®m mb…®zasiri ikii rako os…®mnd…®si niaŇčga. Gumasira aphani, koma Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii, koma Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi, mee aŇčna agharkuvigh…®va ana nigh igharisi mbuzorsir gumasir raniiŇčtima mee aŇčm mb…®sueghtima ana aremighemi. Gumughun, uthughun phunini ko mb…®kethav g…®vaghtima a nomthegh…® r…®kavighemi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 32 Iesus kamagh nono ovhevheeŇčna akama aghurigha mem mb…®Ňčgeema, Pita ana nigha mb…®keeŇčn gugha, aŇčga atarava kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® kamagh…®m mb…®k…®man bar thaeghri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 33 A kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeema, Iesus oragha non suren gumasir garava, Pita avesa kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúSatan, n…®…® nam…®usua isagh muna maaŇč…®! N…®…® gumasir bisighi n…®ghn…®gha, Got…®n bisighi n…®gh…®n…®si phat…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 34 Gumughun Iesus, gumasi rako amisir d…®…®va iv…®ra non suren gumasir d…®…®sima, mee aŇčm…®usua zima, a kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumagha thav nan g…®n zaasa, a vhusvhuisi bisi g…®na amandagh non khani ighuuve isaghuphughuva nan g…®n z…®…®.  
\v 35 Gumagha aŇčam…®re ikaaousua n…®gh…®n…®si, aŇčn…® utum a m…®ghas…®gh ikhaamiri ik…®rana aghuuŇč nighem phat…®. Gumagh naŇčgi n…®ghn…®gha nana akamana aghuuŇč ukurava arui thav ana aremightima aŇčn…® utum a m…®ghas…®gh ikhaamiri ik…®rana aghuuŇč niaŇčga.  
\v 36 Gumagha thav unuagh…®nani iti bisi bar anda nigh…®va, a g…®na aremighti, bisir kharsi manmagh…®ra aŇčna akuraghti? Bar phat…®.  
\v 37 A uvhuesan manav…®n non…® utum aŇčm…®usua aŇč raniiŇčti? Bar phat…®.  
\v 38 Thighire itir gumasi rako amisi mee Got…®n ak…®rasegha othevir maghat…®sigha amui. Mena th…®…®Ňčra nani iz…®…® ko nana akaman gun…®m mb…®k…®man aŇčemsiightima, g…®n Gumasir Otar noni inaghaves…®n…® uŇčuuni ikegh z…®va iv…®ra mena aŇčemsiighemi. A enselir aghuuir phorugh Got…®n aŇčarana aven zighiraami.‚ÄĚ 
\c 9  
\p  
\v 1 Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® guisimbaaŇčra gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, gee khagh…® utuivighav iti tharsi, gena tharsi aremighem phat…®ghami. Gee ikh…®v…®re ikh…®…® gantima, Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthugh, aghavagharan phorugh zighiraami.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus…®m mb…®kar…®gh igharagha oto 
\r (Metiu 17.1-13 koma Luk 9.28-36) 
\p  
\v 2 Uthusir 6 p…®la g…®vasima, Iesus Pita ri Jems koma Jon mee nigha oragh…®ni ikh…®van guavanambogha, mee norira anamoghi iti. Ana anamogh aŇčm mb…®kar…®gh mena ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčni igharaghavo oto.  
\v 3 AŇčn shaarana aŇčarana aghavagharan khav guisimbaaŇčra ughurighava afho. Ughuran khav unuagh…®nan gumagha thav…® uruesir bighan…® ughura thav…®n m…®n gari phat…®.  
\v 4 Mauthughura mee garima Elaija ri Moses otogha Iesus…®n phorugha mee nori v…®Ňčgeeghi.\f * \fr 9:4 \ft Moses ri Elaija bar fhom…®ra aremisima, Iesus boghum…®ra unuagh…®n khav…®n zee.\f* 
\v 5-6 Mee nori v…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima, Pita ri Jems koma Jon mee bar atitiiŇčga, Pita mb…®k…®maŇčgamir…®m mb…®Ňčg…®g…®gha asagha phura kamagh Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumagh, ee bar inderagh…®v…®ra amuigha khagh iti! Ee amb…®khavan phunini ko mb…®kethav ramuaŇčga. N…®…®m…®usua thav, Moses…®usua thav, Elaijagha thav.‚ÄĚ  
\v 7 Mauthughura, gu usuiragha mee avarasima it…®…®Ňčn mav guan thooŇčn otogha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúKhara nano Otar, k…® bar aŇčn vhusvhusi. Gee anara oraagh…®ri!‚ÄĚ  
\v 8 Mauthughura uzuam…®ra mee gara nomthegha gumagha thav…®n ganisi phat…®. Iesus nomb…®ra men phorugha iti. 
\p  
\v 9 Mee nomthegha oragh…®n zighirava Iesus mee ganisir bisir gun gumagha thav…®m mb…®k…®man bar men th…®va. Kamagh…®re ikh…®…® maaŇč…® Gumasir Otar aremigh nomthegh…® r…®kavighemi.  
\v 10 Mee ganisi bighan khav mere itima, mee ana aremigh nomthegh…® r…®kavamira akamam mb…®n…®…®Ňč mbaaŇčm…®usua norira nori v…®Ňčgeeghi. 
\p  
\v 11 Gumughun mee aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúManmagh…®usua Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi kamagh…®usue, Elaija ufhuaragh zeghtima, Got nom ee niam…®usua mb…®sevisir gumagh g…®n zaami?‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus mena azaaŇčs…®gh ikara, ‚ÄúGuisimbaaŇčra Elaija ufhuaragha zeghava bisia r…®k…®ri. Thoghousua fhom…®ra Got…®m mb…®gharani itiro os…®r kamagh iti, ‚ÄėGumasir Otar…®m mb…®zasi nitima mee ak…®ran aŇčga aseghemi?‚Äô  
\v 13 K…® gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, Elaija zegha g…®va. Mee fhom…®ra Got…®na akama os…®ra nori bisir kharsi aŇč ramuam…®usua mb…®kemisi mogh…®n, gumasi rako amisi mee non vhusvhusan m…®n gua nono othevir aŇčga amuigha g…®va.‚ÄĚ \f * \fr 9:13 \ft Uthughun khav…®n Iesus Elaija zaami bighaaŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, guisimbaaŇčra Jon, gumasi uruer gumagh am mb…®Ňčgeeghi. N…®…® ikaaŇčm…®usua, Metiu 17.12…®n gan. Jon…® ufhuaragha zava Iesus zaaousua aŇčm…®usua utuavia r…®k…®ri. \f* 
\s1 Iesus…® utuman maghat…®gh aphasasir otar aŇčga amuisima a nom indera 
\r (Metiu 17.14-23 koma Luk 9.37-45) 
\p  
\v 14 Mee za suren gumasir marsi mem mbatuivigha garima gumasi rako amisira av…®rara mee akuvasima Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi men phorugha nori v…®Ňčg…® nori vathosi.  
\v 15 Mee nori vatosima gumasi rako amisi Iesus…®n garav…®re ikha r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuigha uthughun aŇč ran…®…®Ňčm…®usua akh…®r…®s…®igha zui.  
\v 16 Iesus kamagh mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúGee thoghousua men phorugha gee nori vathosi?‚ÄĚ  
\v 17 Gumaghan mav gumasi rako amisira av…®ran thooŇčni ikhava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumagh, k…® nono otar nigha n…®…®m…®usua zee, utuman maghat…®gh aŇčga aphasasima, am mb…®Ňčge phat…®.  
\v 18 An aŇčga amuir…® uthughun, ana na ukurima a daaghira, phuvii aŇčna akamndooŇčnim mb…®sevi, aŇčna atari nori v…®tivima aŇčm mb…®k…®r…®vasi. K…® utuman maghat…®gha avharaghavharaghaousua n…®…®n suren gumasira azarasi mee aŇčga avharasi phat…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 19 Ana aŇčm mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúOio! K…® bara am…®ra, thighira itir gumasi rako amisi n…®gh…®n…®sia aghavagharisi phat…®. K…® fhom…®ra gen phorugha itima, gee daasughun bigha thav ikeeŇčg…®ti? K…® m…®ghas…®gh geno os…®mnd…®sira nitire? Otar nigh nam…®usua z…®…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 20 A mem mb…®kemisima mee otar Iesus…®usua ana nigha zee. Mauthughura utuman maghat…®gh Iesus…®n garav…®ra, magh…®ra otara amuima a in…®si. A unuagh…®naŇčgi ir…®gha uphoghuphogha phuvii aŇčna akamndooŇčnin…®m mb…®sevi. 
\p  
\v 21 Am mb…®sevima Iesus otarani inaghaves…®na azara, ‚ÄúA mana uthughun…® utuman maghat…®gh aŇčga aphasa?‚ÄĚ An aŇčm mb…®kemisima, inaghaves kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúA ir…®r…®vare itima an aŇčga aphasa.  
\v 22 An aŇč ramuightima ana aremighaousua uthusira av…®rara ana ukurima ana arivi rako r…®phar gueghiri. N…®…® ena akuruvaghamir gamgaaŇč ikh…®tima, n…®…® en…® ukuarukuvigh…®va ena akuragh…®ri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 23 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® thoghousua kamagh…®usue n…®…® gamgaaŇč ikh…®va nana akura? N…®…® n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar ikh…®tima bisir kharsi bar othuivhami.‚ÄĚ  
\v 24 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima otarani inaghaves uzuam…®ra kamagh d…®…®gham mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar ikhava, ano othevi. Kamagha amuisima, n…®…® nana akura!‚ÄĚ  
\v 25 Iesus garima gumasi rako amisi ak…®rsiigha mena aghan zesima a utuman maghat…®gha athogha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® kha utuman maghat…®gh gumasigha amuima mee ukuari oŇčandava mb…®Ňčger phat…®si thav. K…® n…®…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, n…®…® ak…®ran z…®…®, n…®…® nomthegh aven maaŇča thaghri!‚ÄĚ  
\v 26 Mauthughura utuman khav…® oraegha mb…®gh…®rav…®ra ana ikuskusava ak…®ran zesima otar gumaghan khuman m…®n gari. Kamagha amuisima gumasi rako amisira av…®rara kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAna aremi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 27 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus ana afhar…®n…® usuiragha ana ufhesi a r…®khavigha utu. 
\p  
\v 28 Gumughun Iesus r…®phenana aven gugha non suren gumasir phorugha mee norire ikhav ikha, mee kamagh aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúManmagha amuigha, ee utuman maghat…®ghan khav…® avharava avheeŇči?‚ÄĚ  
\v 29 Mem mb…®kemisima a kamagh mee ikara, ‚ÄúKamagha amuir…® unduur maghat…®si gee Got…®n phorughum mb…®k…®m…®va andagha avaraghti anda ak…®ran zaami. Nomthegha igharisi utuav thavi iti phat…®, utuav…®n…® uvav…®ra.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 30-31 Mee aŇčanan khava thaegha Galilin distrigh…®n otogha zui. Mee gua Iesus non suren gumasir surea amui. Bighan khuaŇčm…®usua Iesus mee itira aŇčan gumagha thav ikhaaŇčn a iph…®rph…®ri. Mee guava, a kamagh men phorugham mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúMee Gumasir Otar nigh…®va gumasira afhari rat…®gh…®va, gumughun mee aŇčm mb…®sueghti ana aremigh…®va, gumughun…® uthughun phunini ko mb…®kethav g…®vaghtima a nomthegh…® r…®kavighemi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 32 A mem mb…®kemisima mee am mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…® ikeeŇčsi phat…®gha, kamagha amuigha mee aŇčna azaaŇčs…®ghana atitiiŇči. 
\s1 Th…®…®Ňčre Ikh…®v 
\r (Metiu 18.1-5 koma Luk 9.46-48) 
\p  
\v 33 Mee Kaperneam…®n zegha r…®phenana aveni ikha Iesus mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúGee utuav…®n thaegham mb…®Ňčg…® nori vathosi?‚ÄĚ  
\v 34 Mee utuav…®n nori vathogha nori v…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúTh…®…®Ňčre ikh…®v?‚ÄĚ Kamagha amuisi mee in…®m…®re iti.  
\v 35 Gumughun Iesus apheraghav ikhava mb…®sevisir gumasir 12 p…®lan d…®…®gha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúTh…®…®Ňč ufhuaragh ikaaousua, a g…®ni ikh…®va gumasi bar meni iŇčaaran gumagh ikh…®ri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 36 Mauthughura Iesus otaran sovange nigha men thooŇčn ana rafhasi a utughavi itima, a nona agharaniiŇčn ana umuigha kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi,  
\v 37 ‚ÄúGumagha thav naŇčgi n…®gh…®n…®si mogh…®n kha otaran sovangen m…®n garir thav nigh ana akuraghami, a kamagh na nigha nana akuruvasi. N…®…® th…®…®Ňčra nana akuruvasi, n…®…® nara amui phat…®. N…®…® na amandasi gumagh iv…®ra aŇčga amui.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Th…®…®Ňč ena aphanaŇčga amui phat…®, a enav 
\r (Luk 9.49-50) 
\p  
\v 38 Jon kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumagh, ee garima gumaghan mav unduur maghat…®si n…®…®ni iz…®…®n anda vathosi. Ee ikaaŇči, a ena mav phat…®, ee aŇčn thevi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 39 Gumughun Iesus kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAŇčn th…®van thaghri. Gumagha thav nani iz…®…®n gamgaaŇč bisi ramuva, kha uthusir ana akaar maghat…®sir na ramuighem thughat…®s phat…®.  
\v 40 Th…®…®Ňč ena aphanaŇčga amui phat…® a enav.  
\v 41 K…® guisimbaaŇčra gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, gee Krais…®na andarsi. Krais a Got nom ee niam…®usua mb…®sevisir gumagh. Kamagha amuisima th…®…®Ňčra nani iz…®…®n r…®m…®n gee raniiŇčgemi, a guisimbaaŇčra non…® uvhues niaŇčga.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Othevir maghat…®si n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghara afharavasi 
\r (Metiu 18.6-9 koma Luk 17.1-2) 
\p  
\v 42 Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúOtaran kha thav n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar nani ik…®thi, n…®…® th…®…®Ňčra aŇčra amuightima ano oth…®vhan maghat…®gha thav…® ramuighemi. N…®…®m mb…®ŇčŇčue phat…®sir arivan maŇč…®va bar…® uvhuesan maghat…®gh nighemi. Mee ak…®mani ikh…®v n…®…®n…® ufh…®rara afhagh…®va oŇčaram mb…®k…®nightima n…®…® aremighemi. Kamagh indera.  
\v 43-44 Kamagha amuisi n…®…®na afharimuu n…®…® ramuightima n…®…® oth…®vhan maghat…®gha thav ramuightima, ana r…®tu. Kamagh indera, n…®…® afharimuun…® uvav…®re ikh…®v, a m…®ghas…®gha itiri ik…®rana aghuuŇč niaŇčgami. N…®…®na afharimuuni iv…®re ikh…®va n…®…® ramuightima n…®…®m mbuŇčŇčue phat…®sir arivan…® uŇčuun maŇčŇčaŇčga.  
\v 45-46 N…®…®n…® usua thav n…®…® ramuightima n…®…® oth…®vhan maghat…®gha thav ramuightima, ana r…®tu. Kamagh indera, n…®…® usuan…® uvav…®re ikh…®va, m…®ghas…®gha itiri ik…®rana aghuuŇč niaŇčgami. N…®…®n…® usuani iv…®re ik…®thi Got n…®…® nigh…®va mbuŇčŇčue phat…®sir arivan n…®…® ukunighemi.  
\v 47 N…®…®na ar…®magha thav n…®…® ramuightima n…®…® oth…®vhan maghat…®gha thav ramuightima ana sii. Kamagh indera, n…®…® ar…®maghan…® uvav…®re ikh…®va Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthughuna aven maŇčŇčaŇčga. N…®…®na ar…®maghaniiŇč iv…®re ik…®thi Got n…®…® nigh…®va mbuŇčŇčue phat…®sir arivan n…®…® ukunighemi.  
\v 48 AŇčanan khav aphisir…® uŇčusi mem mb…®kar…®si aphi tharsi gevi phat…®. Mem mb…®kar…®sir sir ariv iv…®ra mbuŇčŇčue phat…®. 
\p  
\v 49 Gumasi Got…®na aphuraphurir aghaera an…®…®Ňčm…®usua amaaghas…®ghan aghaegha ar…®gha arivan anda utuava anda nigha, Got…® an…®ndi. Amaaghas…®gh arivan…® utuir aghaegha amuima anda Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn indera. Os…®mnd…®si amaaghas…®ghan m…®na amui. Amaaghas…®gh mee utueghtima mee utuivigha aghavagharigh…®v os…®mnd…®si otuivtima mee Got…®n ar…®maghaniiŇčn inderaghami.  
\v 50 Amaaghas…®gh a indera, a nono ovheera thaeghti, n…®…® manmagh aŇč ramuightima a nomthegh ovheerighti? Os…®mnd…®si amaaghas…®ghan m…®na amui. Amaaghas…®gh gen navana aveni ikh…®tima gee nava am…®Ňčnd…®ghani ikh…®…®.‚ÄĚ 
\c 10  
\s1 Pharaghamuui noria tham…®rasi 
\r (Metiu 19.1-12 koma Luk 16.18) 
\p  
\v 1 Iesus…® uŇčuun khava thaegha guava, Judian distrigh…®n guava Jordan…® r…®m…®n muaaŇčmogh oto. Ana otosima, gumasi rako amisira av…®rara nomthegha zava, ana akuvasima, a m…®ghas…®gha amui mogh…®ra men surea amui. 
\p  
\v 2 A men surea amuima, FarisiiŇčn marsi zava aŇčn koruamua kamagh aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® eem mb…®k…®m, eno oth…®v manmagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi? Gumagh nona amuuŇč atham…®raghamiro oth…®vhan khav inderasi, o phat…®?‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 A mena azaaŇčs…®gh ikaragha kamagh mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúMoses oth…®vhan manav ramuam…®usua gem mb…®kemi?‚ÄĚ  
\v 4 A mem mb…®kemisima mee kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúMoses, gumagha thav amuuŇč atham…®raghaousua managhamuuŇčniiŇč noniiŇč tham…®raghamir…®m mb…®gharan ofh…®ghaaŇč os…®righa amigha amandaghaousua, an eem mb…®kemi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh mee ikara, ‚ÄúGen navia aghavaghari, kamagh amuisima Moses gem…®usua oth…®vhan khav os…®ri.  
\v 6 Bar fhom…®ra Got unuagh…®nan khav ko bisi bar andagha amuav…®ra gumasi rako amisigha amui.  
\v 7 Kamagha amuisima, gumagh noni inaghaves ko inaghamuuŇč thaegh…®va, a nona amuuŇčn phorugh aniiŇč noniiŇčn phorughami.  
\v 8 AniiŇč ner…®n ofh…®ghan…® uvav…®re ikaami. AniiŇč nom gumaghan phunini phat…®. AniiŇč ner…®n ofh…®ghan…® uvav…®re ikaami.  
\v 9 Kamagh amuisima Got bighan phuniniiŇčgu ufhuraghtima, gumagha thav aniia biighem thughat…®s phat…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 10 Gumughun mee nomthegha r…®phenana aven guava, Iesus…®n suren gumasi bighan khav…®usua aŇčna azaaghi.  
\v 11 A mee ikaragha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumagha thav nona amuuŇč thaegh igharisira amighani ikh…®va, a iv…®ra nona amuuŇčga as…®ghas…®gha pharaghamuui norir ok…®…®va nori nigha akuiro oth…®vha amui.  
\v 12 Amigha thav non mana thaegh igharisi gumaghani ikh…®va, a iv…®ra pharaghamuui norir ok…®…®va nori nigha akuiro oth…®vha amui.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus boorir akua 
\r (Metiu 19.13-15 koma Luk 18.15-17) 
\p  
\v 13 Gumasi rako amisi boorir sovseghe nigha Iesus…®usua zii. A nona afharimuun meni iph…® rar…®ghaousua mee zima, aŇčn suren gumasi meŇčga avhesava men thevi.  
\v 14 Mee meŇčga avhesima, Iesus men ganigha nava osemigha, a kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® th…®…®Ňčra Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthughuna aveni ikaaousua, boorir sovsegher kharsir m…®ni ikh…®…®. Kamagha amuisima boorir sovseghe thaeghtima, mee nam…®usua z…®…®. Men th…®va thaghri.  
\v 15 K…® guisimbaaŇčra gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, boorir sovseghe mee Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthughun ganan vhusvhusi. Gumagh a boorir sovsegher m…®n nomba amevi thav a inighinighemi. A Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthughuna aven maŇčŇčaŇčga. Gumagh nomba amevagham phat…®ghami a kha uthughuna aven maaŇč…®gham phat…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 16 A kamagh mem mb…®kemigha, boori uvhaghuvhagha mee nia mee umusi. Ana afhar…®n…® uvhaghuvhagha meni iph…®a ar…®ghava, inderagh…®v…®ra mee ramuam…®usua Got…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi. 
\s1 Bisira av…®rare itir gumagh 
\r (Metiu 19.16-30 koma Luk 18.18-30) 
\p  
\v 17 Iesus r…®khavigha zuima, gumaghan mav akh…®ghavt…®gha zava, Iesus…®m mb…®n…®man noni it…®v…®nia r…®ph…®righa kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumaghana aghuuŇč, k…® manmagh ramuigh…®va m…®ghas…®gha itiri ik…®rana aghuuŇč niiti?‚ÄĚ  
\v 18 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima Iesus ana ikaragha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® manmagh…®usua gumaghana aghuuŇčn naŇčga ar…®si? Gumaghana aghuuŇč thav iti phat…®. Got nomb…®ra aghuuŇč magh…®.  
\v 19 N…®…® Got Moses…® aniiŇčsiro oth…®v ikaaŇči, ‚ÄėN…®…® gumagham mb…®sueghti ana ar…®ma thaghri, n…®…® pharaghamuui norir okeero oth…®vha ramua thaghri, n…®…® igharisi gumaghan bisi ok…®ma thaghri, n…®…® bisir khorira amuan thaghri, n…®…® nomb…®…®gha bisi niam…®usua gumasir khorira amuan thaghri, n…®…® noni inaghaves ko inaghamuuŇčna apheeŇčni ikh…®va aniiŇčm mb…®zeva aragh.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ  
\v 20 Am mb…®kemisima ana na ikaragha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumagh, k…® fhom…®ra ir…®r…®vare ikhava othevir kharsigha amua za thighira ikha khari iti.‚ÄĚ  
\v 21 Mauthughura Iesus gumaghan khav…®n garava, aŇčn vhusvhusigha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® bighan…® uvav…®ra n…®…® thighira aŇč ramuaŇčgami. N…®…® itir bisi tharsi bar anda amandagh…®va aŇčg…®ro ov…®si nigh…®va, bisi phat…®si gumasi raniiŇčg…®va nan g…®n z…®…®. Gumughun n…®…® Got…®n…® uŇčuun bisir aghuuira niaŇčga.‚ÄĚ  
\v 22 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima gumaghan khava akaman khav…® oraegha, aŇčn khom mb…®s…®…®Ňči. A ikaaŇči, a guisimbaaŇčra bisira av…®rare itir gumagh. A kamagh…®n oraegha aŇčn nava osemisi a gu. 
\p  
\v 23 Gumughun Iesus…®n ar…®maghaniiŇč non suren gumasigha aruava, kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumasi bisir av…®rire iti tharsi, mee Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthughun maŇčam…®usua iŇčaaram mb…®themara ramuigh…®va aven maŇčŇčaŇčga!‚ÄĚ  
\v 24 AŇčn suren gumasi aŇčna akaar kharsiva oraegha, r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuisima, Iesus nomthegha kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúNan boori, gumagh Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthughuna aven maŇčam…®usua iŇčaaram mb…®themara ramuigh…®va aven maŇčŇčaŇčga.  
\v 25 Kamel thav, shaari isaer…® usuuŇčn thooŇčna aven maŇčam…®usua iŇčaarani ikh…®va ramuigh…®va aven maŇčŇčaŇčga. Gumasi bisir av…®rire iti tharsi, mee Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthughuna aven maŇčam…®usua iŇčaaram mb…®themara ramuigh…®va aven maŇčŇčaŇčga!‚ÄĚ  
\v 26 A mem mb…®Ňčgeema, mee guisimbaaŇčra r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuava n…®gh…®n…®sir av…®ragha amuava norira nori v…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúKamagh ramuightima, th…®…®Ňčra m…®ghas…®gha itiri ik…®rana aghuuŇčn khav niiti?‚ÄĚ  
\v 27 Mauthughura Iesus men gara kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumagh nona aghavagharan a m…®ghas…®gha itiri ik…®rana aghuuŇč nighem phat…®. Gumagh Got…®na aghavagharan…® uthugh…®va a m…®ghas…®gha itiri ik…®rana aghuuŇč niaŇčga. Got kha bisi bar andagha amuira aghavaghar iti.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 28 A mem mb…®kemisima Pita kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® gan, ee non bisi bar anda thaegha, n…®…®n g…®n zee.‚ÄĚ  
\v 29 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® guisimbaaŇčra gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, gumagh naŇčg…® n…®ghn…®gha nana akamana aghuuŇč ukunam…®usua, a no r…®phen, o nona aveeŇčnafhesi, o non…® umbuaramisi, o noni inaghaves ko inaghamuuŇč, o non boori, o nono ombaria thaegh…®va nan g…®n z…®…®.  
\v 30 Gumaghan khav thighira unuagh…®nan khav…®n Got guisimbaaŇčra bisi a ufhuaragha iti tharsi bar andagha afhiragh aŇč ran…®…®Ňčgami. A r…®phenira av…®rira ko aveeŇčnafhesi rako umbuaramisi ko inaghamuui koma boorira av…®rara, iv…®ra ombarira av…®rara aŇč ran…®…®Ňčgami. Mee Got…®na akamana aghuuŇčn g…®n zuima gumasir marsi zava mera afharavasi. Gumughun zaamir…® uthugh, Got a m…®ghas…®gha itiri ik…®rana aghuuŇčn an aŇč ran…®…®Ňčgami.  
\v 31 Thighira kha uthughun…® ufhuaragh…®v…®ra iti gumasi, mee g…®ni ikh…®tima, g…®ni iti gumasi, mee ufhuaragh ikaami.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus nono ovhevheeŇčn…® utugh…®m mb…®kemisi mogh…®n, a nomthegha aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi 
\r (Metiu 20.17-19 koma Luk 18.31-34) 
\p  
\v 32 Mee Jerusalem…®n guavanaŇčgava Iesus…® ufhuarasima, aŇčn suren gumasi aŇčn g…®n guava n…®gh…®n…®sira av…®rara amui, men phorugha zuir gumasi rako amisi atitiiŇči. Iesus nomthegha nom mb…®sevisir gumasir 12 p…®la nigha mem mb…®Ňč…®niiŇčn gughava, aŇčm mbatuivamir bisir gun mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 33 A kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee oraa. Ee Jerusalem…®n…® uŇčuuni ikh…®van guavanandi. Gumughun gumagha thav Gumasir Otar nigh…®va, Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi rako Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii ran…®…®Ňčva, mee os…®mnd…®sir aŇčra an…®…®Ňčva ana ar…®maaŇčgamira akaar r…®k…®rami. Gumughun mee ana nigh…®v igharisir kantrin gumasira afhari rat…®ghami.  
\v 34 Mee r…®mbovira akaar aŇčm mb…®k…®m…®va, aŇčgi iphar…®va, ana fhasarogh…®v, aŇčm mb…®sueghtima ana aremighemi. Ana aremighti, uthughun phunini ko mb…®kethav g…®vaghtima a nomthegh…® r…®kavighemi.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Jems ri Joni iz…®…®ni ikh…®v niam…®usua vhusvhusi 
\r (Metiu 20.20-28) 
\p  
\v 35 Sebedin otaraniiŇč, Jems ri Jon, Iesus…®usua zava kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumagh, aŇčga bighan mav…®n vhusvhusi. N…®…® aŇčgagha aŇč ramuam…®usua aŇčga n…®…®na azaaghi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 36 AniiŇč aŇčm mb…®kemisima, Iesus kamagh aniiŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúK…® manmagh aŇčgona akuruvaghti?‚ÄĚ  
\v 37 AniiŇč ana ikaragha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® bisigha ativasir gumaghani ikh…®va otogh…®va, aŇčga ramuighti, aŇčgana thav n…®…®n guv…®n aghara raperaghtima thav n…®…®ni ik…®na aghara raperagh…®ri.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 38 AniiŇč aŇčm mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAŇčgo azaaŇčs…®sir bighan khav, aŇčgo aŇčm mb…®n…®…®Ňč ikeeŇčsi phat…®gha, aŇčgo aŇčm…®usua nana azaaghi. AŇčgo ti k…® niaŇčgamin…®m mb…®zasi iv…®ra aŇčgo anda niaŇčgamira aghavaghar iti? O aŇčgo ti k…® thooŇčn maaŇčgamiro os…®mnd…®si iv…®ra andar thooŇčn maaŇčgamira aghavaghar iti?‚ÄĚ  
\v 39 Ana aniiŇčm mb…®kemisima, aniiŇč ana ikara, ‚ÄúAŇčre, aŇčga aghavaghar iti.‚ÄĚ 
\p Mauthughura Iesus kamagh aniiŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGuisimbaaŇčra, aŇčgo k…® niaŇčgamim mb…®zasi iv…®ra aŇčgo anda niaŇčgami. K…® thooŇčn maaŇčgamiro os…®mnd…®si tharsi aŇčgo iv…®rama andar thooŇčn maŇčŇčaŇčga.  
\v 40 AŇčgo nan guv…®n aghar ko ik…®na aghara raphighaousuava azaere, khara nan bigh…®n phat…®. AŇčanir kharsi Got…®n bisira. A kha aŇčanir raphighemir gumasi, a mee ikeeŇčga, mem…®usua aŇčanir kharsigha amui.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 41 Jems ri Jon bighan khav…®n Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčgeema, 10 p…®lan suren gumasiri igharis tharsi aŇčm mbaraegha, bighan khav…®usua Jems ri Jon…®Ňčga avhesi.  
\v 42 Mee avhesima, Iesus men d…®…®gha, mee akuvagha kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee ikaaŇči, igharisir kantrin ativasir tharsi gamgaaŇč ikhevigha phum meŇčga aghora meŇčga amuima, mee bar mena apheeŇčni iti. Men gumasira aphani nona akaava oraghaousua phuv…®ra mena afh…®ragh…®v…®rasi.  
\v 43 Othevir kharsi gen thooŇčni ikaan thughat…®s phat…®. Gumaghan manav gen thooŇčni ikh…®vani ikaaousua, a iŇčaaran gumaghan m…®ni ikh…®…®.  
\v 44 Gumaghan manav gen…® ufhuaragh maŇčam…®usua, a bar geni iŇčaaran gumaghan kh…®nan m…®ni ikh…®…®.  
\v 45 Gumasir Otar gumasi rako amisi aŇčm…®usua iŇčaraousua a zesi phat…®. Phat…®, a gumasi rako amisiv…®usua iŇčaraousua zee. A gumasi rako amisira av…®raraousua aremigh nom meŇčgu uvhuesigh mee niam…®usua zee.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus gumaghan ar…®maghan thughaniiŇčm mb…®zesi mav…®a amuisi a indera 
\r (Metiu 20.29-34 koma Luk 18.35-43) 
\p  
\v 46 Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha Jerikon guegha, gumasi rako amisira av…®rara men phorugha uŇčuun khava thaegha zui. Mauthughura ar…®maghaniiŇč mb…®zesi gumaghan mav, aŇčni iz…®…® Bartimeus Timeus…®n otar, a utuav…®m mb…®keeŇčn apheraghav ikhava bisiv…®usua azaaghi.  
\v 47 Ano orasima Nasaret…®n gumagh Iesus iv…®ra za zuima a d…®…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúIesus Devit…®n avav, nan…® ukuarukuvi!‚ÄĚ  
\v 48 Am mb…®Ňčgeema gumasi rako amisira av…®rara d…®man aŇčn th…®vagha in…®m…®re ikhaaousuava aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi. Mem mb…®Ňčgeema am mb…®gh…®rav…®ra d…®…®v…®re iti, ‚ÄúDevit…®n avav nan…® ukuarukuvi!‚ÄĚ  
\v 49 Mauthughura Iesus…® utugha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAŇčn d…®…®gha.‚ÄĚ A mem mb…®kemisima mee ar…®maghaniiŇč mb…®zesi gumaghan d…®…®gha kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúN…®…® gamgaeŇčg…®ri. Iesus n…®…®n deeghi. N…®…® r…®kavigh maaŇč…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 50 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima a nona ak…®rani iti shaar…® usuegha ana ukunigha uzuam…®ra r…®khavigha Iesus…®usua zee.  
\v 51 Mauthughura Iesus aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúK…® n…®…®m…®usua theegh…®na ramuam…®usua n…®…® vhusvhusi?‚ÄĚ An aŇčna azarasima ar…®maghaniiŇč mb…®zesi gumagh kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumagh, k…® ganam…®usua vhusvhusi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 52 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® maaŇč…®. N…®…® n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar Got…®ni itima, a n…®…®Ňčga amuisi n…®…® nom indera.‚ÄĚ A magh…®ra nomthegha gari. Mauthughura a Iesus…®n g…®n…® utuav…®n zui. 
\c 11  
\ms1 Iesusa aremigha nomthegha r…®kavi 
\mr (Sapta 11--16) 
\s1 Iesus ativasir gumaghan m…®n Jerusalem…®n zui 
\r (Metiu 21.1-11 ko Luk 19.28-40 koma Jon 12.12-19) 
\p  
\v 1 Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha Jerusalem…®na aghan gua Betfage ko Betanina aghan Oliv…®no oragh…®n oto. Mauthughura Iesus non suren gumaghan phunini amaŇčga,  
\v 2 kamagh aniiŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAŇčgo munagh itir…® uŇčuun maaŇč…®, gantima donkini ikaman mav, mee ana ikhesima, a iti. Gumagha thav…® uthugh thav…®n aŇčga apheraghava aruisi phat…®. AŇčgo an…® umbueeŇč afh…®righ…®va aŇčn…® usuiragh khagh z…®…®.  
\v 3 Thav aŇčgona azaaŇčm mb…®k…®maŇčga, ‚ÄėAŇčgo thoghousua donkia fh…®ri?‚Äô AŇčgo kamagh aŇčm mb…®k…®m, ‚ÄėIkh…®v iŇčaar aŇčni iti. AŇčni iŇčaar g…®vaghti a nomthegha ana amandaghti a zaami.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ  
\v 4 Ana aniiŇčm mb…®kemisima aniiŇč gua garima, donki mee r…®phenani it…®mana akamaniiŇčna ak…®ran…® utuav…®n ana ike. Mauthughura aniiŇč ana fh…®rima,  
\v 5 gumasir marsi utuivighav ikha aniiŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúAŇčgo thoghousua donkin…® umbueeŇč afh…®ri?‚ÄĚ  
\v 6 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus aniiŇčm mb…®kemisi mogh…®n aniiŇčm mena akam ikara. Mauthughura gumasi aniiŇčm mb…®nam…®naaŇč ath…®sima aniiŇč zui.  
\v 7 AniiŇč donki nigha Iesus…®usua zeghava nona ak…®rani itir shaaraniiŇč usuegha donkini iph…®a ath…®. AniiŇč shaaraniiŇč ath…®sima Iesus aŇčni iph…® aphera.  
\v 8 Mauthughura gumasi rako amisira av…®rara nona ak…®rani itir shaari usuava utuav…®na anda ughuari. Marsi uruaŇčn ther…®sosia r…®ghorigha anda ar…®si.  
\v 9 Ufhuaragha zui tharsi rako g…®n zui tharsi mee d…®…®va arava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúInighinigh…®ri! Got inderaghav…®ra Iesus…®a amuigha g…®va. Ee Got…®ni iz…®…® ufh…®ri! Gumaghan khav Ikh…®vani iz…®…® koma aghavagharan zii.  
\v 10 Ena avav Devit fhom…®ra eŇčga ativasi mogh…®n gumaghan khav thighira mamagh…®ra eŇčga ativami. Kamagha amuisi Got inderagh…®v…®ra Iesus…® ramutima a eŇčga ativami. Inighinigh…®ri! Got…®n…® uŇčuuni iti bisi bar aŇčni iz…®…® ufh…®ri!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 11 Gumughun Iesus Jerusalem…®na aven gugha guava Got…® r…®phenam mb…®rogh…®n gu. A gugha bisir garava andara asav…®usuisi. Am…®n ph…®raousuava amuima a non suren gumasir phorugha mee Betanin zee. 
\s1 Iesus baan fhigh…®n khan th…®va 
\r (Metiu 21.18-19) 
\p  
\v 12 Am…®r…®tusi Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha nomthegha Betania thaegha zuima, Iesus…®m mb…®ti aŇčna azi.  
\v 13 A isaghun garima fhigh…®n khan mav…®na afharire iti. Mauthughura ana aghangera maaŇč…® ikhaaŇčm…®usua ana aghae iti, o phat…®. Khara fhisir thee beer…® uthugh phat…®. Kamagha amuisima a guava ov…®gha thav…®n ganisi phat…®, afharir k…®nira aŇčni iti.  
\v 14 Mauthughura a kamagh khan khav…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúThav g…®n n…®…®no ov…®gha thava rameghem thughath…®gham phat…®ghami.‚ÄĚ An aŇčm mb…®kemisi, aŇčn suren gumasi oraghi. 
\s1 Iesus Got…® r…®phenam mb…®rogh…®n guava gumasi as…®si amandi tharsi mem mbatosi 
\r (Metiu 21.12-17 ko Luk 19.45-48 koma Jon 2.13-22) 
\p  
\v 15 Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha Jerusalem…®n otuivigha, Iesus Got…® r…®phenam mb…®rogh…®n gua gumasi as…®si amaŇčga andagh…® uvhuesi tharsi mem mbatosi. Ana aŇčg…®ro ov…®si nori ikarvasi gumasir akosi rako ukurasir buniiŇčmba amandi tharsir ambirembii, anda ufhava anda asiagh…®usue.  
\v 16 A bisi amaŇčga anda niagha arui tharsi v…®Ňčg…®va Got…® r…®phenam mb…®rogh…®na aven z…®…® maŇčan men th…®va.  
\v 17 A men surea amuava kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúMb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®r kharsi Got…®m mb…®gharano os…®rani iti, o phat…®? ‚ÄėNa r…®phenani iŇčaaram mb…®n…®…®Ňč kamagh…®n, kha unuagh…®nan gumasi rako amisi bar mee Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger r…®phen.‚Äô Gee okeer gumasi mondira aŇčanan m…®n aŇčga amui.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 18 Gumasi rako amisira av…®rara bar aŇčn surem mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®va oraegha r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui. Kamagha amuisima Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii rako Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi Iesus…®n atitiiŇčga, mee aŇčm mb…®sueghtima ana aremighaousua magh…®ra utuaviv…®usua urui.  
\v 19 Aro gevima Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha mee Jerusalem…®n…® uŇčuuni ikh…®va thaegha ak…®ran zii. 
\s1 Fhigh…®n kh…®m mb…®s…®…®Ňči 
\r (Metiu 21.20-22) 
\p  
\v 20 Am…®r…®tusi r…®maaŇčra Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha gua garima fhigh…®n khan bii iv…®ram mb…®s…®…®Ňči.  
\v 21 Pita n…®nd…®gha Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumagh, n…®…® gan, n…®…® booghuma as…®ghas…®ghaousuam mb…®kemisi fhigh…®n k…®, am mb…®s…®…®Ňči!‚ÄĚ  
\v 22 Iesus aŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®m ikaragha kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar Got…®ni ikh…®…®.  
\v 23 K…® guisimbaaŇčra gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi. Th…®…®Ňčra n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar Got…®ni ikh…®va oragh thav…®m mb…®k…®m, ‚ÄėGot n…®…® kha oragh…®n…® usuiragh ana ufhegh oŇčarao ukuni.‚Äô N…®…® khamagh…®m mb…®kemightima, a nomb…® ufhegh oŇčarao ukunighemi. A non navana aven n…®gh…®n…®ghan phunini phat…®gh…®va, n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar ik…®…®m mb…®k…®mtima kha bighaaŇč otoghomi.  
\v 24 Kamagha amuisima k…® gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, gee bigha thav niam…®usua n…®gh…®n…®ghana aghavaghar ik…®…®m mb…®k…®maŇčga, ‚ÄėGot anan eera aniiŇčgemi.‚Äô Kamagh…®n Got anan geera aniiŇčgemi. 
\p  
\v 25-26 N…®…® uthugh…®va Got…®n phorughum mb…®k…®m…®va os…®mnd…®gh th…®…®Ňčni iti, n…®…® aŇčno oth…®vhan maghat…®gh g…®na amandaghti, kamagh…®n n…®…®ni Inaghaves…®ni Ikh…®v, non…® uŇčuuni iti thav, a iv…®ra n…®…®no othevir maghat…®si g…®na amaaŇčga.‚ÄĚ \f * \fr 11:25-26 \ft IkeeŇčsi gumasir marsi kamagh n…®gh…®n…®si, mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®mano oth…®vhan mav iv…®ra ves…®n khav…®na aveni iti. Mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®man khav…®ra khara, ‚ÄúGee gumasi rako amisiri igharis tharsi, gee amuisiro othevir maghat…®si g…®na amaaŇčna agharkuvightima geni Inaghaves, kha non…® uŇčuuni itir Inaghaves, a iv…®ra geno othevir maghat…®si g…®na amandagham phat…®ghami.‚ÄĚ \f* 
\s1 Judarir gumasira aphani Iesus…®na azaaghi n…®…® manmagh…®ra iz…®…®n khav nii 
\r (Metiu 21.23-27 ko Luk 20.1-8) 
\p  
\v 27 Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha nomthegha gua Jerusalem…®n otogha Iesus Got…®n r…®phenam mb…®rogh…®na avena aruima, Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii rako Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi rako Judarir gumasira aphani aŇčm…®usua zee.  
\v 28 Mee zegha Iesus…®na azaaghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® manmagh…®ra kha iz…®…® nigha kha bisigha amui? Th…®…®Ňčra kha iz…®…®ni ikh…®van n…®…®Ňčga an…®…®Ňči?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 29 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus mee ikara, ‚ÄúK…® iv…®ra azaaŇčs…®ghan mav…®n gee ramuam…®usua gee inderagh…®v…®ra nani iŇčgar…®gha ramuightima, k…® gem mb…®k…®maŇčga, th…®…®Ňčra kha bisi ramuaŇčgamiri iz…®…®ni ikh…®van naŇčga an…®…®Ňči.  
\v 30 Jon…®n…® uruur khara Got…®n bigh…®n, o gumaghan bigh…®n? Nam mb…®k…®m!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 31 Mauthughura mee norira nori v…®kemigha kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúEe kamagh…®m mb…®k…®maŇčga, ‚ÄėAŇčn…® uruur Got…®n zee.‚Äô A nomthegh kamagh eem mb…®k…®maŇčga, ‚ÄėGee manmagha amuigha n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar Jon ramuani iph…®rph…®ri?‚Äô  
\v 32 Eem mb…®k…®maŇčga, ‚ÄėAŇčn…® uruur gumaghan zee.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ Kha akam iv…®ra thughat…®s phat…®. Gumasi rako amisira av…®rara mee ikaaŇči, Jon a guisimbaaŇčra Got…®na akam nigha zesi gumagh, kamagha amuisi mee kha gumasi rako amisir atitiiŇči.  
\v 33 Mauthughura mee Iesus…®na azaaŇčs…®gh ikaragha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe ikeeŇčs phat…®.‚ÄĚ Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra, k…® noni iz…®…® nisir…® utuav…®n, gun gem mb…®kemighem phat…®ghami.‚ÄĚ 
\c 12  
\s1 Uainir m…®gh…®n garir gumasir maghat…®sir aghunamana akam 
\r (Metiu 21.33-46 koma Luk 20.9-19) 
\p  
\v 1 Iesus aghunambara akaar Judarir gumasira aphanim mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGumaghan mav uainir m…®gh…® opharigha aŇčn r…®v…®na aghui. Uainiro ov…®si m…®gh…®m…®ghamiri ithaaŇčg…® ukuighava magh…®ra a r…®phenaŇčga amui. Mee kha r…®phenani iph…®ni ikh…®va uainir m…®gh…®n ganaŇčgami. Gumughun a uainir m…®gh nigha uainir m…®gh…®n ganaŇčgamir gumasir marsi meŇčga an…®…®Ňči. Mee g…®n…® uainiro ov…®siri imboori tharsi nomthegha ana ikaraghami. Gumughun a igharagha isaghun gu.  
\v 2 Gumughun…® uainiro ov…®si ukuaramir…® uthugho otosi, uainir m…®gh…®n guav iŇčaaran gumaghan mava amandasi a uainiro ov…®si tharsi niam…®usua uainir m…®gh…®n garir gumasiv…®usua gu.  
\v 3 Ana otosima, mee aŇčn…® usuiragha, aŇčm mb…®suegha ana amandasi ana afhar…®ra nomthee.  
\v 4 Gumughun guav iŇčaaran gumaghan igharisi thav amandasima, mee aŇčm mb…®sogha aŇčna aphana biigha amemerano othevir aŇčga amui.  
\v 5 Gumughun guav nomthegham mb…®kethava amandasima, mee aŇčm mb…®suesi ana aremi. Gumughun a iv…®ra igharis marsi sam…®ra amaaŇči. Marsi mee phura mem mb…®soghi, marsi mee mem mb…®suesi mee ar…®…®ghire.  
\v 6 Gumughun bar ambuunav iti ana ana amaaŇčm…®usua, aŇčno otaran khav…®ra, a bar aŇčn vhusvhusi. A bar men g…®n ana amaŇčgava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėMee nano otaran khav…®na akamam mbaraegh…®va inderagh aŇč ramuaŇčgami.‚Äô Mauthughura ana na amandasi a gu.  
\v 7 Thighira uainir m…®gh…®n garir gumasi kamagh nori v…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄėKha otar kha uainir m…®gh…®n guava amendaghti. Aria, ee nori nigh aŇčm mb…®sueghtima ana aremighemi. Gumughun…® uainir m…®gh…®n khav, ee norira aŇčn gueeŇč ameeŇčgemi.‚Äô  
\v 8 Mauthughura mee aŇčn…® usuiragha aŇčm mb…®suesima ana aremisi, mee ana nigha uainir m…®gh…®n ak…®ran ana ukuni. 
\p  
\v 9 Thighira uainir m…®gh…®n guav manmagh ramuti? A z…®va uainir m…®gh…®n garir gumasir kharsi v…®sueghtima mee ar…®m…®ghireghemi. Gumughun a uainir m…®gh nigh…®va igharis tharsi ran…®…®Ňčga. 
\p  
\v 10-11 Gee Got…®m mb…®gharano os…®ran khav…®n ganis, o phat…®? 
\q1 ‚ÄėAk…®man khav r…®phenaŇčga amuir gumasi aŇčgi iph…®rph…®righa aŇčm mbatuesima, 
\q2 Ikh…®v thighira aŇčga amuisi a rephenaŇčgi isaghuphusir ak…®maŇčgi ighesima 
\q1 gumasi rako amisi aŇčn ganigha r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 12 Thighira mee ikaaŇči aŇčna aghunamana akaman meŇčga asi, kamagha amuisima mee aŇčn…® usuiragh ana niam…®usua utuaviv…®usua urui. Mee aŇčn…® usuighaousua gumasi rako amisir atitiiŇčga, ana thaegha gue. 
\s1 Gumasi rako amisi aŇčg…®ro ov…®sir Sisar an…®…®Ňčgami, o phat…®ghami? 
\r (Metiu 22.15-22 koma Luk 20.20-26) 
\p  
\v 13 Gumughun Judarir gumasira aphani ko FarisiiŇčn marsi koma Herot…®n g…®na arui tharsi mee, mee amandasi, mee Iesus…®usua zee. Mee Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®ro oth…®vha thav…®n ganigh aŇčn…® usuiraghousua.  
\v 14 Mee zegha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumagh, ee ikaaŇči, n…®…® m…®ghas…®gha guisimbaaŇčram mb…®Ňčg…®va, mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®r…® uvarsira gumasi rako amisi bar meŇčga an…®ndi. Gumasi iz…®…®ri iti tharsi o gumasir kh…®ni, n…®…® akaman…® uvav…®ra mem mb…®Ňčg…®va guisimbaaŇčra Got…®n othevir men surea amui. Ee Got…®n oth…®vhan g…®n maŇč…®va, gavman…®na aŇčg…®ro ov…®si Sisar ran…®…®Ňčgami o phat…®ghami? Ee uvhuesami, o uvhuesam phat…®ghami?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 15 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus men khori ikeeŇčga kamagh mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúGee thoghousua nan khorigha amui? Ak…®mano ov…®gha thav nam…®usua ana nigh z…®…®ti k…® aŇčn ganaŇčga.‚ÄĚ  
\v 16 Am mb…®Ňčgeema mee ak…®mano ov…®gh aŇčm…®usua ana nigha zesi a mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúTh…®…®Ňčni iŇčeendaghani iz…®…® khara?‚ÄĚ A mem mb…®kemisima mee kamagh Iesus ikara, ‚ÄúSisar…®ni iŇčeendagh.‚ÄĚ  
\v 17 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra, gee Sisar…®n bisi Sisar ran…®…®Ňčva, Got…®n bisi nigh, Got ran…®…®Ňč.‚ÄĚ Mauthughura mee aŇčni iŇčgar…®ghan r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui. 
\s1 SadiusiiŇčn marsi, gumagha aremigh nom r…®kavamir bisi vagha Iesus…®na azaaghi 
\r (Metiu 22.23-33 koma Luk 20.27-40) 
\p  
\v 18-19 SadiusiiŇčn, mee kamagh n…®gh…®n…®si, gumagha aremigh nomthegh…® r…®kavighem thughat…®s phat…®. Kamagha amuigha mee Iesus…®na azaaŇčs…®ghaousua zee. Mee zegha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumagh, Moses fhom…®ra kamagh em…®usua os…®ri, gumagha aremigh nona amuuŇč thaegh…®va boori phat…®ghtima ana afhoghumasir mav…®n amuuŇčno os…®…®Ňčni ikh…®va aŇčm…®usua boorir niaŇčga.  
\v 20-21 Uthughun mav…®n 7 p…®la afhoghumasi iti. Avenafhes amuuŇčni ikha boorir phat…®gha aremisima, nom undooghan aŇčgi inesi thav aŇčni ikha boori phat…®ghava iv…®ra aremi. Gumughum mb…®kethav kamagh…®rama amui.  
\v 22 Gumughun 7 p…®la afhoghumasir kharsi bar mee aŇčni ikha, boori tharsi nisi phat…®gha ar…®…®ghire. Gumughun ambuuŇčn, amigh iv…®ra aremi.  
\v 23 Afhoghumasir 7 p…®la aŇčni ike. Kamagha amuisi a nomthegh…® r…®kavamir…® uthugh, a th…®…®Ňčna amuuŇčra?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 24 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh mee ikara, ‚ÄúGee Got…®m mb…®gharano os…®r ko Got…®n gamgaaŇč ikeeŇčsi phat…®, kamagh gee iphasa n…®ghn…®gham mb…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 25 Ar…®ghireghemi tharsi r…®kavamir…® uthughun, gumasi amuiri ikaami thughat…®s phat…®, iv…®ra mee amisi nigh gumasi rariighem phat…®ghami. Mee enselir m…®n Got…®n…® uŇčuuni ikaami. 
\p  
\v 26 Ar…®ghires tharsi nomthegh…® r…®kavamir bisiv…®usua, gee Moses…®m mb…®gharana aven sisi khan niaghagh gee aŇčn ganisi, o phat…®? Niaghaghan khav…®n, Got kamagh Moses…®m mb…®kemi, ‚ÄėK…® Abraham, ri Aisak koma Jekov…®n Got.‚Äô  
\v 27 Got gumasir niro ofh…®sir ar…®ghiri tharsi, men Got phat…®, a gumasir…® unduura aŇčam…®re iti tharsir Got. Gee bari iphasa n…®ghn…®gham mb…®Ňčgeeghi.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Got…®n…® ufhuaragha zuiro oth…®v 
\r (Metiu 22.34-40 koma Luk 10.25-28) 
\p  
\v 28 Iesus SadiusiiŇčn phorugha mee nori vatosima Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumaghan mav za mem mbarasi. Ano orasima Iesus ikarvaghana aghuuŇčn meŇčga aniiŇčsima, a Iesus…®na azaaghi, ‚ÄúGot…®n oth…®vhan manav…®ra marsi bar andagha afhiragha, ufhuaragha zui?‚ÄĚ  
\v 29 Am mb…®Ňčgeema Iesus ana ikara, ‚ÄúOth…®vhan bari ikh…®…®vara khara, ‚ÄėIsraeliiŇča, gee oragh. Eni Ikh…®v a en Got. A nomb…®ra eni Ikh…®v.  
\v 30 Gen non navira averi rako non…® unduu rako non n…®gh…®n…®si rako gamgaaŇčn iv…®ra aŇčn vhusvhusighiri.‚Äô  
\v 31 AŇčgi inesiro oth…®v khara, ‚ÄėN…®…® nomb…®n vhusvhuisi mogh…®ra gumasi rako amisi bar men vhusvhusighiri.‚Äô Nom oth…®vha thav kaniiŇčn m…®ni ikhevigha aniiŇčga afhirasi phat…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 32 Mauthughura kha gumagh kamagh Iesus ikara, ‚ÄúN…®…® guisimbaaŇčram mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, Got nomb…®ra, thav nom iti phat…®.  
\v 33 Ee non navira averi rako, non n…®gh…®n…®si rako non gamgaaŇčni Ikh…®van vhusvhusighiri. Mamagh…®ra n…®…® nomb…®n vhusvhuisi mogh…®ra gumasi rako amisi bar men vhusvhusighiri. Ee kha oth…®vhaniiŇč g…®n maaŇč…®tima, mee phurama aphuraphurir aghaer bisi rako arivan bar sisira aghaer bisira aphuraphuri tharsi andagha afhiraghami.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 34 Iesus orasima a inderaghav…®ram mb…®kemisi, Iesus aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGot kha bisigha ativamir…® uthugh n…®…® aŇčni isaghuni iti phat…®.‚ÄĚ Mauthughura thighira mee nomthegha azaaŇčs…®gha thav…®n nomthegh Iesus ramuan atitiiŇči. 
\s1 Iesus, Got nom ee niam…®usua mb…®sevisir gumaghaousua gumasi rako amisira azaaghi 
\r (Metiu 22.41-46 ko Metiu 23.1-36 ko Luk 11.37-54 koma Luk 20.41-47) 
\p  
\v 35 Iesus Got…® r…®phenam mb…®rogh…®n gumasi rako amisir surea amuava, mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúManmagha amuisi Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, Krais, Got nom ee niam…®usua mb…®sevisir gumagh, a Devit…®n avav?  
\v 36 Devit nomb…®, Got…®n…® Utum n…®ghn…®ghan khav…®n aŇčga aniiŇčsi, a kamagh…®m mb…®kemi, 
\q1 ‚ÄėGot kamagh nani Ikh…®vam mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, 
\q2 ‚ÄúN…®…® khagh nana agharan guv…®n rapheragh, 
\q1 mamagh…®ra ikh…®tima k…® n…®…®na aphanir gumasi r…®kambuuŇčtima 
\q2 mee n…®…®na apheeŇčni ikaami.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô 
\m  
\v 37 Devit nomb…® ‚ÄėIkh…®van‚Äô gumaghan khav…® ath…®. Manmagh amuigha gumaghan khav nomthegha Devit…®n avav?‚ÄĚ Am mb…®Ňčgeema gumasi rako amisira av…®rara aŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®v oraegha bari iphui. 
\p  
\v 38 Iesus gumasi rako amisir surea amua kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasiv…®usua ganigh…®ri. Mee shaarir…® uruaria sharigh rarutima gumasi rako amisi mee bisi amaŇčga andagh…® uvhuesira aŇčanani iz…®riri ikiir mee ran…®…®Ňčm…®usua, mee bar vhusvhusi.  
\v 39 Mee Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger r…®phenir ambirambir aghuuira niva, ishari ikiir…® uthugh mee aŇčaniri iz…®…®ri iti tharsi niam…®usua bar vhusvhusi.  
\v 40 Mee pha ar…®ghiresi amisir oz…®rir khoru amua men r…®phenir bisi nia, kamagh…®usue ee indera. Mee, gumasi meni iz…®…®ri ufhaaousua, kamagha amuigha mee Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger…®m mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®r…® uruarigha amui. Kamagha amuir gumasi, men…® uvhuesan maghat…®gh gumasi othevir maghat…®sigha amui tharsir…® uvhues bar aŇčga afhiraghami.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Mana aremisira amigh ak…®mano ov…®ghan phunaŇčg…®nira ithaaŇčga ath…® 
\r (Luk 21.1-4) 
\p  
\v 41 Iesus guava aŇčg…®ro ov…®si ar…®si ithaaŇčna aghan apheraghav ikhava gumasi rako amisir av…®rar garima mee nona aŇčg…®ro ov…®si nigha Got…®n r…®phenana aŇčg…®ro ov…®si ar…®si ithaaŇčn anda ar…®si. Gumasi rako amisi aŇčg…®ro ov…®sira av…®rare iti tharsi aŇčg…®ro ov…®sira av…®rara ar…®si.  
\v 42 Mauthughura mana aremisira amighano os…®…®Ňč bisi phat…®gha zava ak…®mano ov…®ghan phunaŇčg…®niiŇč ath…®, aniiŇč ak…®mano ov…®ghan…® urughan…® uvav…®ra aŇčn m…®n gu.  
\v 43 Mauthughura Iesus non suren gumasir d…®…®gha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® guisimbaaŇčra gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi mana aremisiro os…®…®Ňčna amighan khav bisi phat…®gha ak…®mano ov…®ghan sovan phunaŇčg…®ni aŇčg…®ro ov…®si ar…®siri ithaaŇčga ath…®si aŇčna ak…®mano ov…®ghan phunaŇčg…®ni gumasiri igharis tharsi ar…®sira aŇčg…®gha afhira.  
\v 44 Mee nona aŇčg…®ro ov…®sir av…®raghi ith…®r…®piiŇčga aŇčg…®ro ov…®sir…® uvhovhera an…®…®Ňči. Amighan khav nona ambirambiin maghat…®ghan m…®ra ak…®mano ov…®ghan ambuunani ath…®gha a nomthegha aghaegh…® uvhuesamira aŇčg…®ro ov…®si phat…®.‚ÄĚ 
\c 13  
\s1 Iesus kamagh…®usue, Got…® r…®phen g…®n maghatiighemi 
\r (Metiu 24.1-2 koma Luk 21.5-6) 
\p  
\v 1 Iesus Got…® r…®phenam mb…®rogha thaegha ak…®ran zima, aŇčn suren gumaghan mav am mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumagh! N…®…® gan, khara aŇčg…®r bar ikiira, mee andar Got…® r…®phenani iŇčarisima, aŇčn gangan bar indera! Got…® r…®phen ko r…®phenir sovseghe aŇčm mb…®rogh…®ni iti tharsi, anda bar r…®phenir r…®Ňčg…®rir aghuuira!‚ÄĚ  
\v 2 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagha ana ikara, ‚ÄúN…®…® r…®pheniri ikiir kharsir gari? Anda bar maghatiighemi. Gumughuna aŇčg…®r kharsi, gumasi bar anda uphueghtima anda barbar daaŇčgi ireghemi. Thav thav…®ni iph…®ni ikeghem phat…®ghami.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus kamagh…®usue, os…®mnd…®sira av…®rara g…®no otuivami 
\r (Metiu 24.3-14 koma Luk 21.7-19) 
\p  
\v 3 Iesus Oliv…®no oragh…®ni iph…®n, Got…® r…®phen khoman aŇčna aghuagha apheraghav itima, Pita ri Jems koma Jon ri Andru mee norire ikhava aŇčna azaaghi,  
\v 4 ‚ÄúEem mb…®k…®m…®va, r…®pheni maghatiighemir bighaaŇč, a mana uthughun otuivti? Oth…®vhan manav…® ufhuaragh otuivtima, ee ikeeŇčg…®m mb…®k…®maŇčga bisir kharsi otuivamir…® uthugha aghangera zee?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 5 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee noriv…®usua inderagh…®v…®ra gan, gumagha thav z…®…® gen khorir amuan thaghri.  
\v 6 Gumasira av…®rara nani iz…®…®n z…®…®, mb…®k…®maŇčga, ‚ÄėK…® Krais, Got nom ee niam…®usua mb…®sevisir gumagh.‚Äô Kha gumagh gumasi rako amisir av…®rar khori ramuaŇčga. 
\p  
\v 7 Uthughun khav…®n gee aghangera itir asaghuuri ikiir n…®n…®iva oragh…®va, isaghuni iti mb…®zorsiri ikiira akaava oraghami. Kha uthughun gee r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha ramuan thagh…®ri. Othevir kharsi otuivightima, unuagh…®nan khav g…®vamir…® uthugh thighar zaami.  
\v 8 Kantrin mav…®ni iti tharsi r…®kavigh igharisir kantriri iti tharsir phorughum mb…®soghomi. Kha uthughun ativasir gumaghan mav…®na andarsi r…®kavigh igharisir ativasi gumaghana andarsir phorughum mb…®soghomi. AŇčanir tharsi aghae bar phat…®ghtima, gumasi rako amisi v…®tiire ikaami. Mb…®k…®m…®k…®si iv…®ra igharisi uŇčuimbar otuivami. Kha bisi, amigh…® ufhuaragh…®v…®ra otaasa mb…®zagh nigh…®va gumughun ano otara otaami, os…®mnd…®sir kharsi iv…®ra kamagh…®ra otuivami os…®mnd…®sir kharsi ufhuaragh…®v…®ra otuivtima unuagh…®nan khav g…®vamir…® uthugh thighar…®. 
\p  
\v 9 Gee inderagh…®v…®ra norira noriv…®usua gan. Gen gumasi tharsi gee nigh…® uŇčuimbar garir gumasir ran…®…®Ňčga. Mee Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčger r…®phenir gem mb…®soghomi. Gee nani iz…®…®n…® utuivisi tharsi, gee gavman…®n gumasiri ikiir ar…®masi r…®fhaaŇčn…® uthugh…®va, k…® amuisi bisi, gee andar gun mem mb…®kemighemi.  
\v 10 Gumasi tharsi ufhuaragh maŇč…® Got…®na akamana aghuuŇčn gun gumasi rako amisi kha uŇčuimbari itir akaa uvhaghuvhagha andav v…®k…®m…®ri. Gumughun kha unuagh…®n g…®vami.  
\v 11 Gumasi tharsi mana uthughun gen…® usuiragh gee nigh os…®mnd…®siva oragha anda r…®k…®rir r…®phenan maŇč…®tima, gee ufhuaragh…®m mb…®k…®m…®usua n…®gh…®n…®sir av…®ri nia thaghri. N…®…® mb…®k…®m…®usua, Got n…®gh…®n…®sir n…®ra an…®…®Ňčti n…®…® mb…®ze v…®k…®maŇčga. Khara n…®…® nomb…®ram mb…®Ňčge phat…®, Got…®n…® Utum mb…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 12 Afhoghumasi norira nori nigh aphanir gumasir an…®…®Ňčtima mee mem mb…®soghti mee ar…®m…®ghireghemi. Inasi non boori iv…®ra kamagh…®ra andara amuaŇčga. Boori noni inasi rako inaghamuuira akaava athogh…®va ar…®maŇčgamiro othevir mee ramuighti, mee ar…®m…®ghireghemi.  
\v 13 Uthughun khav…®n gumasi rako amisi bar nani iz…®…®usua navan maghat…®ghan geni ikaami. Th…®…®Ňčra uthugha aghavagharigh maaŇč…® ana aremighemir…® uthugho otoghtima Got ik…®rana aghuuŇč g…®n aŇčra an…®…®Ňčgami.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus kamagh…®usue, bighan bar maghat…®ghara otoghomi 
\r (Metiu 24.15-28 koma Luk 21.20-24) 
\p  
\v 14 Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee gantima Got bari iph…®rph…®risi bigh aŇč r…®phenani ikaami. Khara a ikhaam phat…®ghamira aŇčan. A ik…®thi, Got no r…®phena thaeghemi. N…®…® th…®…®Ňčra os…®…®ran khav…®n ganigh, inderaghav…®ra n…®gh…®n…®gh…®va ana ikeeŇčg…®ri. Got bari iph…®rph…®risi bighan khav, uthughun khav…®n otoghtima Judian distrigh…®na aveni iti tharsi mee uzuam…®ra ar…® orasira anaeŇčg…®ri.  
\v 15 Thav r…®phenan ak…®rani ikegh…®va nomthegha aven maaŇč…® non bigha thav nia thagh…®ri.  
\v 16 Thav m…®gh…®ni ikh…®vani ikegh…®va nomthegh r…®phenan maaŇč…® nona ak…®ran sarir shaar nia thagh…®ri.  
\v 17 Naviri itira amisi rako boori otee aphiri inaghamuui mev…®si. Uthusir kharsi zaami, mee bar maghatiighemi!  
\v 18-19 Uthusir kharsi zaami, anda os…®mnd…®siri ikiir…® uthusi. Got unuagh…®n ko ovheea amuisi uthughun za thighira, kamagha amuisiro os…®mnd…®gha thav kamagha otosi phat…®. Uthugh thav nomthegh kamagh otoghom phat…®ghami. Kamagha amuisi gee Got…®n phorughum mb…®k…®mtima os…®mnd…®siri ikiir kharsi amogh…®n…® uthughun otuiva thagh…®ri.  
\v 20 Ikh…®v nomb…®usua mb…®sevisi gumasi rako amisi norighi n…®ghn…®gha, uthughun maghat…®ghan khav…®n…® uthusir marsia r…®ghorisi anda muaŇč othevi. A ti andar r…®ghoris phat…®si gumasi rako amisi bar ar…®ghireghaghi. 
\p  
\v 21 Zaamir…® uthugh, thav gem mb…®k…®maŇčga, ‚ÄėGee gan, Krais…®ra khara! A Got nom ee niam…®usua mb…®sevisir gumaghara,‚Äô o, ‚ÄėGee gan, Krais…®ra muna!‚Äô Ana akamam mbaraghan thaghri!  
\v 22 Gumasi tharsi z…®va gen khori ramu kamagh…®usuami, ‚ÄėK…®ra, Got gumasi rako amisi nom mee niam…®usua mb…®sevisi gumagh,‚Äô o ‚ÄėK…® Got…®na akam nigha ziir gumaghan mav.‚Äô Magh…®ra mee non gamgaaŇč kh…®vamir bisiri ikii rako r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuiro othevi ramuti anda otuivami. Mee kamagh vhusvhusi, mee gumasi rako amisir khorira amutima mee oŇčanighemi. Mee aghavaghar ikh…®va, iv…®ra Got nomb…®usua mb…®sevisi gumasi rako amisi, mee iv…®ra men khori ramuam…®usua.  
\v 23 K…® g…®no otuivamir bisi bar andar gun gem mb…®kemi. Kamagha amuisi gee inderaghav…®ra noriv…®usua gan…®ri.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus kamagh…®usue, Gumasir Otar g…®n zaami 
\r (Metiu 24.29-31 koma Luk 21.25-28) 
\p  
\v 24 Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúOs…®mnd…®siri ikiir kharsir…® uthugh g…®vaghtima, g…®n zaamir…® uthughun bisir kharsi otuivami. Aro g…®ng…®nighemi. Ik…®ni isiragham phat…®ghami.  
\v 25 Mb…®kovi ovheen asighireghemi. Ovheeni itir bisira aghavaghari, usuaghusuaghava, nona aŇčania tham…®raeghemi.  
\v 26 Uthughun khav…®n gumasi ganti Gumasir Otar aghavagharani ikh…®v ko aŇčarani ikh…®va sam…®ra guan thooŇčn zaami.  
\v 27 A non enseli amandaghti mee maaŇč…® ovhee ko unuagh…®nano othevi bar andar maŇč…®va Got…®m mb…®sevisi gumasi rako amisi mee akuvigh aŇčm…®usua zaami.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus kamagh…®usue, gee fhigh…®n khan gan ikeeŇčgemi 
\r (Metiu 24.32-35 koma Luk 21.29-33) 
\p  
\v 28 Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFhigh…®n khan aŇčguu nomthegh…®m mb…®kovtima gee ikeeŇčg…®m mb…®k…®maŇčga, amogh…®n…® uthugha aghangera zee. Gee fhigh…®n khan gan n…®gh…®n…®si niaŇčga.  
\v 29 Kamagh…®ra gee bisir kharsir ganti anda otuivtima gee ikeeŇčg…®m mb…®k…®maŇčga, Gumasir Otar a nom zaamir…® uthugha aghangera zee. A it…®mana akamaniiŇčn…® uthughav iti.  
\v 30 K…® guisimbaaŇčra gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi. Uthughun khav…®ni iti gumasi rako amisir kharsi ikh…®v…®re ik…®thima bisir kharsi bar otuivami.  
\v 31 Ovheen ko unuagh…®n g…®vaghami, nam mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…® g…®vagham phat…®ghami.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus kamagh…®usue, a nom zaamir…® uthugh thav a ikeeŇčsi phat…® 
\r (Metiu 24.36-44) 
\p  
\v 32 Iesus…®m mb…®Ňčg…® guava kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúThav ikeeŇčsi phat…®, uthughun manav…®ra k…® gem mb…®Ňčger bisir kharsi otuivti. Got…®n…® uŇčuuni itir enseli ko Got…®n Otari iv…®ra ikeeŇčsi phat…®. Afhes…®ni Ikh…®v nomb…®re ikaaŇči. 
\p  
\v 33 Gee uthughun khav…®n zaamir…® uthughi ikeeŇčsi phat…®. Gee inderagh…®v…®ra noriv…®usua gani ikh…®…®.  
\v 34 Kha uthughun gumaghan mav igharagha zui mogh…®n. A no r…®phena thaegha guava no r…®phen nigha noni iŇčaarir gumasir afhar…® ar…®ghava r…®phenani iŇčaaria r…®ghorava meŇčga an…®ndi. A it…®mana akamaniiŇčni itir gumagham mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, n…®…® inderagh…®v…®ra gan.  
\v 35 R…®phenan guav zaamir…® uthugh gee ana ikeeŇčsi phat…®, a boŇčgaara zaami, o r…®maaŇčnar…®ghan zaami, o utuari afhuti a zaami, o am…®ni itiraghti a zaami, o? Kamagha amuisima gee inderagh…®v…®ra gan…®ri.  
\v 36 Phat…®ghtima, a uzuam…®ra otogh gen ganti, gee rakuv…®re ikaami.  
\v 37 K…® gem mb…®Ňčger bisir kharsi, k…® gumasi rako amisi bar mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄėGee inderagh…®v…®ra gan…®ri!‚Äô ‚ÄĚ 
\c 14  
\s1 Gumasir arura aphani Iesus…®m mb…®sueghti ana aremighaousua mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®a r…®k…®ri 
\r (Metiu 26.1-5 ko Luk 22.1-2 koma Jon 11.45-53) 
\p  
\v 1 Iis phat…®sir…® uvisir…® uthuuri ishamaŇčga amuir…® uthugh koma Israeli Got nomthegha mee nisir…® uthughuni ikh…®van…® uthughun phuninira ikhav…®re iti. Kha uthughun Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii, koma Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi, momooŇčno oth…®vha thav…®n Iesus…®n…® usuiragh aŇčm mb…®sueghti ana aremighaousua utuaviv…®usua urui.  
\v 2 Mee kamagh nori v…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúEe ishaman…® uthughun aŇčn…® usuighem thughat…®s phat…®. Ee ramuightima ishamani iti gumasi rako amisi mb…®zorughani ikh…®va thav…®n ee ramuighemi.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Amighan mav…®m mbughuna aghuuŇč zuir…®m mburueŇč Iesus…®na aphanaŇč giŇče 
\r (Metiu 26.6-13 koma Jon 12.1-8) 
\p  
\v 3 Iesus Betanin…® uŇčuuni ikhava mamburan ar…®mar…®m itir gumagh Saimon r…®phenana aven aghaana akogh…®na aphava apheraghav iti. Ana aphava apheraghav itima, amighan mav…®m mbughuna aghuuŇč zuir…®m mburueŇčn mav nigha zii. Ana ak…®mana aghuuŇčna amuisi mb…®s…®vani iti. AŇčn…® uvhues bari iph…®ni iti. Amighan khav…®m mburueŇčn khav nigha Iesus…®usua zegha mburueŇčm mb…®s…®va bigha mburueŇčn Iesus…®na aphanaŇč giŇče.  
\v 4 Ma uthughuni iti tharsi mee navi siava kamagh nori v…®Ňčg…®v…®re iti, ‚ÄúTheghousua kha mburueŇčn mbughuna aghuuŇč zui thav amighan khavi iphasava aŇčga amui?  
\v 5 An ana amandagh…®va aŇčg…®ro ov…®sira av…®rara nighaghi. AŇčn…® uvhues ombaran…® uvav…®ran…® uvhues aŇčga afhira. Gumughun ana aŇčg…®ro ov…®si phat…®si tharsira akuruvaghami.‚ÄĚ Mauthughura mee phuv…®ra aŇčga avhesi.  
\v 6 Mem mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAna thaghi. Gee thoghousua os…®mnd…®ghan aŇčga an…®ndi? Ana thaghi! Ano oth…®vhana aghuuŇčn naŇčga amui.  
\v 7 Bisi phat…®si tharsi m…®ghas…®gh gen phorugh ikaami. Gee mana uthughun mena akuruvaghan n…®ghn…®gh z…®…®ti gee mena akuruvaghami. K…® m…®ghas…®gh gen phorugh ikhan thughat…®s phat…®.  
\v 8 K…® aremightima ana ramuaŇčgamir bighaaŇč, ana anaaŇčga amui. A ufhuaragh…®m mbughuna aghuuŇč zuir…®m mburueŇč nam mb…®kar…®gh aghevightima mee g…®n na umogh…® rar…®ghami.  
\v 9 K…® guisimbaaŇčra gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, mee unuagh…®nan khav…®na aŇčanan manav…®n Got…®na akamana aghuuŇč ukun…®va amighan khava amuisiro oth…®v iv…®ra aŇčm mb…®k…®m…®va anaaŇčgi n…®gh…®n…®gh…®v…®re ikaami.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Judas Iskariot Iesus nigh Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikiira afharimuura ar…®ghaousua akamana aghavaghara r…®k…®ri 
\r (Metiu 26.14-16 koma Luk 22.3-6) 
\p  
\v 10 Judas Iskariot a Iesus…®m mb…®sevisir gumasir 12 p…®lan gumaghan mav. A Iesus nigh…®va Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikiira afharimuura ar…®ghaousua mem…®usua gu.  
\v 11 Mauthughura mee aŇčna akaman khav…® oraegha bar phuvure inighinighava, aŇčg…®ro ov…®si aŇčra n…®…®m…®usua akamana aghavaghara r…®k…®ri. Thighira aŇčn…® usuiragh mera an…®…®Ňčm…®usua utuaviv…®usua urui. 
\s1 Iesus non suren gumasir phorughava aphi 
\r (Metiu 26.17-25 ko Luk 22.7-14 ko Luk 22.21-23 koma Jon 13.21-30) 
\p  
\v 12 Iis phat…®sir…® uvisir…® uthuuri ishamaŇčga amuir…® uthusir…® ufhuaragha zuir…® uthugho otosima Judarir gumasi mee oth…®vhan khav iti. Mee ufhuaragha Israelir Got nomthegha mee nisir…® uthugh aŇčgi n…®gh…®n…®gh…®va sivsiv…®ni ikamam mb…®suegh ana nigh…®v Got ran…®…®Ňčva aŇčm mb…®nambagh…®v ana nigh maaŇč…®va anara amaŇčga. Thighira Iesus…®n suren gumasi aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúEe aŇčanan manav…®n maaŇč…®, n…®…® Israeli Got nomthegha mee nisir…® uthughuni ishama ramuam…®usua, ee bisia r…®k…®r ti?‚ÄĚ  
\v 13 Mem mb…®kemisima a non suren gumaghan phunini amaŇčga kamagha aniiŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAŇčgo uŇčuuni ikh…®van maŇč…®tima gumagha thav…® r…®m…®m mb…®naŇčg…® uphugh z…®…® aŇčgom mbatoghti, aŇčgo aŇčn g…®n maaŇč…®.  
\v 14 Ana aven zui r…®phen aŇčgo aŇčn maŇč…®va aŇčn guav…®m mb…®k…®m…®ri, ‚ÄėFh…®gh…®n gumagh kamagha azaaghi, ‚ÄúK…® non suren gumasir phorugh Israeli Got nomthegha mee nisir…® uthughi n…®ghn…®gh ishamaŇčga amuira aŇčan mana?‚ÄĚ ‚Äô  
\v 15 AŇčgo aŇčm mb…®k…®mti a iph…®n r…®phenana aveni itira aŇčanani ikh…®vana aŇčgon kh…®vaghami. AŇčanan khav bisi bar ikha em…®usuav…®ra gari. Uthughun khav…®n gee aŇčanan khav ee noriv…®usua bisi bar andar r…®k…®righiri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 16 Mauthughura aŇčn suren gumaghaniiŇč mee thaegha uŇčuuni ikh…®vana aven guava garima bisi am mb…®kemisi mogh…®ra gusi, aniiŇč magh…®ra Israeli Got nomthegha mee nisir…® uthughusua aghae rako bisia r…®k…®ri. 
\p  
\v 17 Ma uŇčguarthughura Iesus nom mb…®sevisir gumasir 12 p…®lar phorugha guava otuivi.  
\v 18 Mee aŇčna aghan akogh…®n apiighav ikha aphava, Iesus kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® guisimbaaŇčra gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, gena thav na nigh…®va nana aphanaŇčga amuir gumasi tharsira afharimuu rat…®ghami, a iv…®ra nan phorugha ikhava aphi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 19 Mee aŇčna akamam mbaraegha, navi bar osemi. Mee bar…® uvhaghuvhagha aŇčna azaaŇčs…®gha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…®ghee, k…®ra ti?‚ÄĚ  
\v 20 Mem mb…®kemisima a mee ikaragha kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee 12 p…®la gena thav…®ra. Ma gumagh nan phorugh uvighan…® utumani ithaaŇčn…® uvav…®ra raghumi thav.  
\v 21 Gumasir Otar, Got…®m mb…®ghar…®m mb…®kemisir mogh…®ra, ana aremighemi. Gumagh, Gumasir Otar nigha aphanir gumasira afhar…® ath…®si khav! A bar maghatiighemi! InaghamuuŇč aŇčm mbatesi phat…®ghav khasi, a inderaghaghi!‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesus uvisir…® uthuu rako uainiro ov…®siri imbooriri iŇčgaa non suren gumasigha an…®…®Ňči 
\r (Metiu 26.26-30 ko Luk 22.15-20 koma 1 Korin 11.23-25) 
\p  
\v 22 Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha apha ikhava, a uvighan…® utuman mav nigha Got…®m mb…®nambagha ana biigha, ana nigha non suren gumasigha an…®…®Ňčga, kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúKhara nan neer…®nofh…®gh. Gee ana nigh ana ram…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 23 Mauthughura a uainiro ov…®siri imboori aphiri ithaaŇč nigha Got…®m mb…®nambagha meŇčga aniiŇčsi, mee uvhaghuvhagha norir guri.  
\v 24 Mee uainiro ov…®siri imboori aphima a kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúKhara nan Ňčaan. K…® gumasi rako amisi bar mena akuruvaghaousua ana asigh…®usuami. K…® kamagh ramuighti Got kha akama r…®Ňčg…®rana aghavaghar ikeghemi.  
\v 25 K…® guisimbaaŇčra gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, K…® nomthegh uainiro ov…®siri imboori tharsi rameghem phat…®ghami, kamagh…®re ikh…®…® maaŇč…® Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthugho otoghomi. Kha uthughun, k…® uainiro ov…®siri imbooriri iŇčgaa ramaŇčga.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 26 Mauthughura mee Got…®ni iz…®…® ufhir…®m mb…®tighan mav…®a amuigha r…®khavigha Oliv…®no oragh…®n zee. 
\s1 Iesus kamagh…®usue, Pita g…®n…®m mb…®k…®maŇčga, a Iesusi ikeeŇčsi phat…® 
\r (Metiu 26.31-35 ko Luk 22.31-34 koma Jon 13.36-38) 
\p  
\v 27 Iesus kamagh non suren gumasi v…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGot…®m mb…®gharano os…®r kamagh iti, ‚ÄėK…® sivsiviir garir gumagh aŇčm mb…®sueghtima sivsivii atamatam…®ra areghemi.‚Äô Kamagha amuisi gee bar, nani itir n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar g…®vaghtima, gee na thaegh…®va areghemi.  
\v 28 K…® gem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, k…® aremigh nomthegh…® r…®kavigh gen…® ufhuaragh Galilin distrigh…®n maŇčŇčaŇčga.‚ÄĚ  
\v 29 A mem mb…®kemisima Pita kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúMee bar n…®…® thaeghtima k…®ra phat…®ghami.‚ÄĚ  
\v 30 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® guisimbaaŇčra n…®…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, thighira r…®maaŇčn khav…®n n…®…® nomb…® uthughun phunini ko mb…®kethav…®n n…®…®m mb…®k…®maŇčga, ‚ÄėK…® ana ikeeŇčsi phat…®.‚Äô Magh…®ra utuar g…®na afhuvan buaaŇčniiŇč ramuaŇčga.‚ÄĚ  
\v 31 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima Pita akamana aghavaghara amua kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúK…® n…®…®n phorugha aremighaousuava ar…®maŇčga, k…® kamagh…®m mb…®kemighem phat…®ghami. Bar phat…®ghami!‚ÄĚ Mauthughura suren gumasi bar kamagh…®ra aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi. 
\s1 Iesus Getsemanin m…®gh…®n Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčgeeghi 
\r (Metiu 26.36-46 koma Luk 22.39-46) 
\p  
\v 32 Iesus non suren gumasir phorugha olivir ther m…®gh…®n zee. Ma m…®gh…®ni iz…®…® Getsemani. Mee aŇčn zegha, Iesus kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee khagh raphigh…®v ik…®thi k…® Got…®n phorughum mb…®k…®maŇčga.‚ÄĚ  
\v 33 Mauthughura a Pita, ri Jems koma Jon mee nigha gu. Thighira atitiiŇč phuv…®ra aŇčna anandima, a bar osemigha,  
\v 34 kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúNan navana avee, os…®mnd…®gh ana itheragha gueghiri. K…® aremighaousuava amui. Gee khaghi ikh…®va, inderagh…®v…®ra gan.‚ÄĚ  
\v 35 Mauthughura a muaŇč s…®vagha gugha, non khoma mogh…®ra unuagh…®naŇčgi ir…®gha kamagh Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, utuav…®ni igharis thav ikh…®tima n…®…® uthughun maghat…®ghan khav nam mbath…®gh…®n ana nii.  
\v 36 A kamagh Got…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGiifheve, nani inaghaves, bigha thav bar n…®…®no osemisi phat…®. Kamagh amuisi mb…®zagh…®n khav, n…®…® nam mbath…®gh…®n ana nii. N…®…® nan vhusvhusan g…®n maŇča thagh…®ri. N…®…® non vhusvhusan m…®n, n…®…® ramu.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 37 Mauthughura a nomthegha non suren gumaghan phunini ko mb…®kethav…®na aghan zegha garima mee akui. Mee akuima a kamagh Pita mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúSaimon, n…®…® akuire? N…®…® thange nan phorugh ikegh gan…®va uthughuno oth…®vhaaŇčni ikeghem phat…®ghtire?  
\v 38 Gee inderagh…®v…®ra gan…®va, Got…®n phorughum mb…®k…®mti os…®mnd…®gha thav gee ramuightima gee ireghem phat…®ghami. K…® ikaaŇči, gen navira averi vhusvhusi, mb…®kar…®sia aghavagharisi phat…®. Kamagha amuisi pharphari geŇčga amui.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 39 Mauthughura a nomthegha gugha ufhuaragha Got…®n phorugham mb…®kemisi mogh…®ra nomthegha aŇčn phorugham mb…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 40 Gumughun a nomthegha non suren gumasiv…®usua za gari, mee akuav…®re iti. Pharphari phuv…®ra meŇčga amui. Mauthughura a meŇčga aghurasi, mee aŇčm mb…®k…®maŇčgamira akaagha asa. 
\p  
\v 41 Mauthughura a uthughum mb…®kethav…®n gugha Got…®n phorugham mb…®kemigha nomthegha za mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee avughusuava akuav…®re itire? Oth…®vhan khava thaghi! Uthugho oto. Gee gan, Gumasir Otar mee ana nigh…®va othevir maghat…®sigha amuir gumasira afharira ar…®ghaousua zii.  
\v 42 Gee r…®kavigh…®va! Ee maŇčŇčaŇčga! Gee gan. Na nigh aphanir gumasir ran…®…®Ňčgamir thav…®ra, a muna zii!‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Judas Iesus nigha aŇčna aphanir gumasira afhar…® ath…® 
\r (Metiu 26.47-56 ko Luk 22.47-53 koma Jon 18.3-12) 
\p  
\v 43 Iesus Pita, ri Jems ko Jon…®m mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima, Judas, aŇčm mb…®sevisir gumasir 12 p…®lan mav oto. Av…®rani ikh…®v aŇčn phorughum mb…®soghomir…®m mb…®zorsir akosi rako ifhani nigha Iesus…®usua zii. Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii rako Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi rako Judarir gumasira aphani, mee mee amaeŇčsi, mee zii.  
\v 44 Iesus nigh mena fharira r…®ghaousua amuir gumagh…® ufhuaragha kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúK…® oth…®vhan khav…®n gen kh…®vaghami. K…® iŇčŇč…®samir gumagh, a Iesus…®ra. Gee an…® usuiragh, inderagh…®v…®ra aŇčn gan…®va, ana nigh maaŇč…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 45 Mauthughura Judas Iesus…®usua zav…®re ikha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúFh…®gh…®n gumagh!‚ÄĚ Judas aŇčni iŇčŇč…®si.  
\v 46 Magh…®ra gumasi zava Iesus agharir aŇčga ariigha, mb…®gh…®rav…®ra aŇčn…® usuira. 
\p  
\v 47 Mauthughura Iesus…®na aghani iti gumaghan mav nom mb…®zorughana akos asigha, Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasira aphananiri iŇčaaran gumaghan…® ukuara r…®tusi aŇčn…® ukuar r…®tughir…®.  
\v 48 Magh…®ra Iesus kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® okeer gumagh phat…®. Gee thoghousua nan…® usuighaousua mb…®zorsira akosi rako ifhani niia zii?  
\v 49 K…® m…®ghas…®gha gen phorugha ikha, Got…®n r…®phenam mb…®rogh…®na aven surea amui. Gee nan…® usuighani iph…®rph…®ri. Got…®m mb…®gharano os…®r…®m mb…®kemisi mogh…®ra gee kamagh naŇčga amui.‚ÄĚ  
\v 50 Mauthughura Iesus…®n suren gumasi bar ana thaeghava are. 
\s1 Gumaghani ikaman mav ara gu 
\p  
\v 51 Gumaghani ikaman mav bigha thav arusi phat…®, am mb…®sasin…® ughura ak…®rani iti thav ikegha Iesus…®n g…®n zui. Mauthughura Iesus…®na aphani aŇčn…® usuirasima,  
\v 52 a nona ak…®rani itir…®m mb…®sasin…® ughuran khava thaegha imuŇčgamara ara gu. 
\s1 Judariro os…®mnd…®siva oraghava anda r…®k…®rir gumasi Iesus…®n phorugham mb…®Ňčgeeghi 
\r (Metiu 26.57-68 ko Luk 22.54-55 ko Luk 22.63-71 ko Jon 18.13-14 koma Jon 18.19-24) 
\p  
\v 53 Iesus…®na aphani ana nigha Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasira aphaniv…®usua gu. Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii, rako Judarir gumasira aphani, rako Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi, mee bar za nori akuvaghav iti.  
\v 54 Mauthughura Pita thighiiŇčn muaŇčn aŇčga ath…®gha Iesus…®n g…®n guava bar gua Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasira aphanan r…®phenan r…®v…®nana aven gughava a ganganir gumasir phorugha apheraghav ikha arivan fheeghi. 
\p  
\v 55 Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii rako Judariro os…®mnd…®siva oragha anda r…®k…®rir gumasi bar Iesus…®m mb…®sueghti ana aremighaousua akaman mena akuruvaghaousua uruiava, avheeŇči.  
\v 56 Gumasira av…®rara khorigha amuir…®m mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…®r Iesus…®a amuisi, mem mb…®Ňčg…®m…®Ňčg…® uvhorsira zui phat…®.  
\v 57 Marsi r…®khavigha khorigha amuira akaman khav…®n aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi,  
\v 58 ‚ÄúEe orasima, a kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėGumasi iŇčarisi Got…® r…®phenan khav k…® ana r…®ph…®righ…®va, uthughun phunini ko mb…®kethav…®ra igharis thav…®ni iŇčarighemi. K…® iŇčarighemi thav gumasi aŇčni iŇčarighem phat…®ghami.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ  
\v 59 Mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®r kharsi iv…®ra guisimbaaŇčra uvhorsira zui phat…®. 
\p  
\v 60 Mauthughura Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasira aphan r…®khavigha men thooŇčn…® utugha Iesus…®na azaaghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® akama thav ikarvaghani iph…®rph…®risire? Mee n…®…®Ňčga asira akaman khav, a guisimbaaŇčra, o?‚ÄĚ  
\v 61 Mauthughura Iesus in…®m…®re ikha mem mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®ma thav ikarasi phat…®. 
\p Mauthughura Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasira aphan nomthegha aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® Krais, Got nom ee niam…®usua mb…®sevisir gumagh? Gumasi rako amisi kha Got…®ni iz…®…® ufhi, n…®…® ano Otarara me?‚ÄĚ  
\v 62 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima Iesus kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® aŇčno Otarara. Gumughun n…®…® ganti, Gumasir Otar kha gamgaaŇč iti Got…®n guv…®n aghara apheragh…®va ovheen…® ughura sam zaami.‚ÄĚ  
\v 63 Mauthughura Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasira aphan non shaara biighava azaaghi, ‚ÄúEe theghousua nomthegh gumasi tharsir phorugh d…®…®gh ti mee z…®va akaar aŇčga as…® ti? Marik…®…®!  
\v 64 Gee nori aŇčm mbarasi, am mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®r maghat…®sir Got…®ni iz…®…®ra afharavasi. Gee manmagh n…®gh…®n…®si?‚ÄĚ Mauthughura mee barbar akaman aŇčga asa, kamagh…®usue ana aremighemi. 
\p  
\v 65 Mauthughura marsi aŇčgi iphari. Mee aŇčna ar…®maghaniiŇč avaragha, mee nona afharir aŇčm mb…®sogha kamagh aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…®m mb…®k…®m. Th…®…®Ňčra n…®…®m mb…®sosi?‚ÄĚ Mauthughura ganganir gumasi ana nighava aŇčm mb…®soghav…®re iti. 
\s1 Pita kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúK…® Iesusi ikeeŇčsi phat…®‚ÄĚ 
\r (Metiu 26.69-75 ko Luk 22.56-62 ko Jon 18.15-18 koma Jon 18.25-27) 
\p  
\v 66 Uthughun khav…®ra Pita r…®phena r…®v…®nam mb…®Ňč…®niiŇčni itima, Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasira aphanani iŇčaarana amighan mav zii.  
\v 67 A zava Pitan garima ana arivan fheema, a r…®k…®rav aŇčn gara, kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® gumaghan khav n…®…® iv…®ra Iesus…®n phorugha ike. A NasaretiiŇčn gumagh mav.‚ÄĚ  
\v 68 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima a nomb…®n guaragha kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúK…® n…®…®m mb…®Ňčger bighan mav ikeeŇčsi phat…®.‚ÄĚ Mauthughura r…®v…®nani it…®mani ikh…®vana akamaniiŇčno otogh…®va ak…®ran maŇčam…®usuava amuima magh…®ra utuar afhui.  
\v 69 Gumughuni iŇčaarana amighan khav khagh aŇčn garav…®ra utuivighav itir gumasi rako amisi nomthegha mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúMuna mena mav…®ra.‚ÄĚ  
\v 70 A mem mb…®kemisima a nomthegha nomb…®n guaragha muaŇč g…®n, aŇčna aghan…® utuivighav itir gumasi Pita mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® Galilin distrigh…®n gumagh, kamagha amuisima guisimbaaŇčra n…®…® mena mav…®ra.‚ÄĚ  
\v 71 Magh…®ra Pita mb…®gh…®rav…®ram mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúK…® guisimbaaŇčram mb…®Ňčgeeghi. K…® khorira amuightima Got naŇčga as…®ghasiighemi.‚ÄĚ A kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúK…® gem mb…®Ňčger gumaghan khav ikeeŇčsi phat…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 72 A kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re itima utuar nomthegha afhui. Magh…®ra Pita Iesus aŇčm mb…®kemisi mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®maŇčgi n…®nd…®…®, ‚ÄúN…®…® ufhuaragh…® uthughun phunini ko mb…®kethav…®m mb…®k…®maŇčga, ‚ÄėK…® Iesusi ikeeŇčsi phat…®.‚Äô Magh…®ra utuar g…®n…® uthughun phuninin afhuighemi.‚ÄĚ Pita anaaŇčgi n…®gh…®n…®ghava ara gua bar phuv…®ra azii. 
\c 15  
\s1 Mee Iesus nigha Pailat…®usua gu 
\r (Metiu 27.1-2 ko Metiu 27.11-14 ko Luk 23.1-5 koma Jon 18.28-38) 
\p  
\v 1 Am…®r…®tusi r…®maaŇčra, Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii rako Judarir gumasira aphani, ko Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi, rako Judariro os…®mnd…®siva oragha anda r…®k…®rir gumasiri igharis tharsi iv…®ra, mee n…®ghn…®ghan mav…® oto. Mee Iesus…®na afhari ikegha ana akua guava Pailat…® an…®…®Ňči.  
\v 2 Mee Pailat…® aniiŇčsima, Pailat aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúN…®…® Judarigha ativasir gumagh, o?‚ÄĚ An aŇčna azarasima Iesus ana ikaragha kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAŇčre, n…®…® inderagh…®v…®ram mb…®Ňčgeeghi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 An aŇčm mb…®kemisima Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii bisira av…®rara aŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®va akaar aŇčga asi.  
\v 4 Mauthughura Pailat nomthegha aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúN…®…®m mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®r kharsi ikaravaghami, o phat…®? N…®…® orasi, mee bisira av…®rara n…®…®m mb…®Ňčg…®va andar n…®…®Ňčga asi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 An aŇčna azarasima Iesus bar aŇčm mb…®Ňčger phat…®si, Pailat r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui. 
\s1 Pailat khani ighuuvan Iesusa guusua mb…®Ňčgeeghi 
\r (Metiu 27.15-26 ko Luk 23.13-25 koma Jon 18.38‚Äď19.16) 
\p  
\v 6 Pailata amuiro oth…®v kamagh…®n, ombari bar ishamani ikh…®van khav…®n…® uthugh, mee Pailat…®m mb…®k…®mtima a r…®v…®nan k…®rth…®ghani itir gumagha thav, men vhusvhusan ana thaeghti, a maŇčŇčaŇčga.  
\v 7 Gumaghan mav, aŇčni iz…®…® Barabas, a gavman…®n gumasir phorugham mb…®sosi tharsi men phorugha r…®v…®nan k…®rth…®ghani iti. Mee bighan khav…®usua r…®v…®nan k…®rth…®ghani iti. Mee gavman…®n phorugha nori v…®sogha gumaghan mava aremi.  
\v 8 Thighira gumasi rako amisi Pailat itira aŇčanan guavanambogha r…®v…®nan k…®rth…®ghani itir gumagha thav mee vhusvhuisi thava tham…®raghaousua Pailat…®na azaaghi. Khara Pailat m…®ghas…®gha oth…®vhan khav…®a amui.  
\v 9 Mee aŇčna azarasima, Pailat mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúK…® Judarigha ativasir gumagha thaegh…®va gem…®usua ana amaaŇčm…®usua, gee vhusvhuisi o?‚ÄĚ  
\v 10 Pailat ikaaŇči, ‚ÄúGot…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii Iesusa amuir bisivagha navi osemigha, ana nigha nana afhar…® ath…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 11 Mauthughura Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii v…®kemisi gumasi rako amisir navi r…®kavisima mee Pailat…®m mb…®kemightima a Iesus…®n th…®vagh…®va, Barabasa thaeghtima a mem…®usua zaami.  
\v 12 Mem mb…®kemisima Pailat azaaghi, ‚ÄúGee Judarigha ativasir gumagh ar…®si thav, k…® manmagh…®ra aŇč ramuti?‚ÄĚ  
\v 13 A mem mb…®kemisima gumasi rako amisi mb…®gh…®rav…®ra d…®…® kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúAna nigh khani ighuuvan ana gura!‚ÄĚ  
\v 14 Mauthughura Pailat mena azaaghi, ‚ÄúManmagh…®usua? Ano oth…®vhan maghat…®ghan manav…®a amui?‚ÄĚ A mem mb…®kemisima mee bar…®m mb…®gh…®rav…®ra d…®…® mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúKhani ighuuvan ana gura!‚ÄĚ  
\v 15 A mee ramuightima men navi inderaghaousua, Pailat Barabasa thaghi. Am mb…®zorsir gumasi mb…®kemisi mee umbuer Iesusa afhasoroegha, Pailat khani ighuuvan ana guusua meŇčga an…®…®Ňči. 
\s1 Mb…®zorsir gumasi Iesus r…®phovi 
\r (Metiu 27.27-31 koma Jon 19.2-3) 
\p  
\v 16 Mb…®zorsir gumasi Iesus nigha gavman…®n r…®phenani ikh…®vam mb…®rogh…®na aven gueghira mb…®zorsir gumasi bar men d…®…®sima mee za nori akuvaghav iti.  
\v 17 Mee uph…®gh…® rutusir shaaran agh…®van…® uruaran mav…®n aŇčn sharagha r…®khon…®n…® amaeŇčna r…®k…®righa aŇčna aphanan shara.  
\v 18 Mee magh…®ra aŇčn d…®…®va aŇčm mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúJudarigha ativasir gumagh, n…®ra ativasir thav!‚ÄĚ  
\v 19 Mauthughura mee aghor…®n aŇčna aphanam mb…®sogha, iv…®ra aŇčgi ipharav…®re iti. Mee khoru amua noni itevira akuriri iph…®ni ira, mee guisimbaaŇčra aŇčni iz…®…® ufhi mogh…®ra amui.  
\v 20 Mee othevir kharsir aŇčga amua aŇč r…®phovigha g…®vagha, a ma sarisir shaari usuegha, aŇčn shaaran aŇčn shara. Mauthughura mee ana nigha khani ighuuvan aŇčga afhughafhughaousua aŇčna akua zui. 
