\p  
\v 21 Sairinin gumaghan mav Saimon, a Aleksander ko Rufus…®n inaghaves, a uŇčuuni igharisi thav…®ni ikegha Jerusalem…®na aven zui. Magh…®ra mb…®zorsir gumasi Iesusa guumir khani ighuuve isaghuphughaousua aŇčn…® usuirasi, an aŇčgi isaghuph…®. 
\p  
\v 22 Mee guava aŇčanan mav…®ni iz…®…® Golgota, mee aŇčno otuivi. AŇčanan khav…®ni iz…®…®m mb…®n…®…®Ňč kamagh…®n, Aphanir Agharir AŇčan.  
\v 23 Mauthughura mee uainiro ov…®siri imboori ko mb…®zasia gevi r…®m…®n phorugha ighav…®suegha Iesus…® an…®ndima ana na thaghi.  
\v 24-25 Aro anaŇčga 9_oklogh nisima mee Iesus nigha khani ighuuvan ana guragha aŇčga afhu. Mauthughura mb…®zorsir gumasi aŇčn shaari isiragha norigha aniiŇčga satu ikararaaghi. Thav…® ufhuaragho otogh…®va, shaara thav niaŇčga.  
\v 26 Mauthughura mee aŇčn gun…®m mb…®Ňčgera akaman khavo os…®ri, ‚ÄúA Judarigha ativasir gumagh.‚ÄĚ Mee akaman kuaŇčm…®usua aŇčm mb…®sueghtima ana aremighemi.  
\v 27-28 Mee, ok…®…®va mb…®zorsigha amuisi gumaghan phunini, mee aniiŇč nigha Iesus…®na aghani iv…®ra aniia agura. Mee mav nigha Iesus…®na agharan guv…®n itir khani ighuuvan aŇčga afhugha, mav nigha agharani ik…®n itir khani ighuuvan aŇčga afhu. \f * \fr 15:27-28 \ft IkhaaŇčmarir gumasir marsi mee kamagh n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®usue kha akam iv…®ra khagh iti. Kha akam a kamagh…®n, ‚ÄúMamagha amuigha akaman mav Got…®m mb…®gharana aveni iti a bar guisimbaaŇčra otoghomi. Ma akam kamagh…®n, ‚ÄėGumasi rako amisi gumaghan maghat…®ghan mav…®n m…®n aŇčn gari.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ \f* 
\p  
\v 29 Mauthughura za zui tharsi mee r…®mbovir…®m mb…®zeer aŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®va nona aphani ukuaukuaghava kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúOre! N…®…®, Got…®n r…®phena r…®ph…®righ aron phunini ko mb…®kethav…®n nomthegh aŇčni iŇčaraousua mb…®kemisi gumagh.  
\v 30 N…®…® thighira n…®…® nomb…®ra nomb…®na akuragh, khani ighuuva thaegh…®va zighir…®!‚ÄĚ  
\v 31 Got…®na aphuraphurava aghae rako bisir aŇčga an…®ndir gumasiri ikii rako Judariro othevi ikeeŇčsi gumasi iv…®ra kamagh…®ra aŇč r…®phova nori v…®Ňčgeeghi. Mee kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúA igharis tharsira akuruvasi a nomb…®ra nomb…®na akuruvaghani iŇčgura!  
\v 32 Kha gumagh, a kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄėK…® Got nom gumasi rako amisi niam…®usua mb…®sevisi gumagh. K…® Israeligha ativasir gumagh.‚Äô Khara guisimbaaŇčrana akam n…®…® khani ighuuva thaegh…®va zighir…®tima, ee n…®…®n ganigh n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar n…®…®ni ikaami.‚ÄĚ Okeer gumaghan phunini aŇčna aghan guraghav ikha, iv…®ram mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®r maghat…®sira av…®rara phuv…®ra aŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®v…®re iti. 
\s1 Iesus…®n ovhevheeŇč 
\r (Metiu 27.45-56 ko Luk 23.44-49 koma Jon 19.28-30) 
\p  
\v 33 Aro za phesakhaman thooŇčni itima g…®ng…®n…® unuagh…®nani itir…® uŇčuimba bar anda avaragha, guava 3_oklogh…®n…® uŇčguarthughura utu.  
\v 34 Aro gua 3_oklogh nisima Iesus it…®…®Ňčni ikh…®van…®m mb…®gh…®rav…®ra kamagh deeghi, ‚ÄúEloi, Eloi, lama sabaktani?‚ÄĚ Akaman khav…®m mb…®n…®…®Ňč kamagh…®n, ‚ÄúNan Got, nan Got n…®…® thoghousua na thaghi?‚ÄĚ  
