\v 36 Magh…®ra gumaghan mav akh…®ghavt…®gha gua r…®m…®n…® usuisi bigh nigha uainiro ov…®siri imboorira afhaaŇčnd…®gha rugha ana nigha aghor…®n mav…® ath…®gha, Iesus ramam…®usua ana amandi. A kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúGee thaegh, ee ganaŇčga, Elaija ti z…®va aŇčna akuraghami, o phat…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 37 Mauthughura Iesus…®m mb…®gh…®rav…®ra d…®…®gha utumu usue. 
\p  
\v 38 Magh…®ra Got…®n r…®phenan guraghavi iti mb…®sasini ikh…®v iph…®ni ikegha thooŇčra bigha gueghira uv…®no otogha araran phunini ir…®.  
\v 39 100 p…®lam mb…®zorsir gumasir garir gumaghana aphanan mav, a Iesus…®na aghan…® uthughav ikha orasi, am mb…®gh…®rav…®ra d…®…®gha, manmagh…®ra aremisiro oth…®vhan ganigha kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúBar guisimbaaŇčra, kha gumagh a Got…®n Otarara!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 40 Uthughun khav…®na amisir marsi muaŇč isaghun…® utuivighav ikha gari. Men thooŇčn Makdalan…®n…® uŇčuuna amigh Maria, ko Salome, ko Josev ri Jems…®ni inaghamuuŇč Maria. Kha Jems a Josev…®n…® undoogh.  
\v 41 Amisir kharsi Galilin distrigh…®ni ikegha Iesus…®na akuruvagha aŇčn phorughava arui. Amisir av…®rar marsi iv…®ra Iesus…®n phorugha Jerusalem…®na anambogha iv…®re iti. 
\s1 Mee Iesus…®n khum nigha ak…®man thooŇčga ath…® 
\r (Metiu 27.57-61 ko Luk 23.50-55 koma Jon 19.38-42) 
\p  
\v 42-43 Thighira aron avhughususan…® uthughusua bisiar r…®k…®rir…® uthugh. Am…®n ph…®rtima avhughususan…® uthugho otuivami. Kamagha amuisima aro gevima, Arimatean gumagh Josev, Judariro os…®mnd…®siva oragha anda r…®k…®rir gumaghana aghuuŇč mee bar ikeeŇčsi mav. A nomb…® iv…®ra Got kha bisigha ativamir…® uthughusua gari. Ana atitii phat…®gha Iesus…®n khum niam…®usua gua Pailat…®na azaaghi.  
\v 44 An aŇčna azarasima Pailat oraghi, Iesusa aremigha g…®vasima, a r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui. A 100 p…®lam mb…®zorsir gumasir garir gumaghana aphanan mav…®usua akama amandasima a zesima an aŇčna azaaghi, ‚ÄúIesus guisimbaaŇčra aremisire?‚ÄĚ  
\v 45 An aŇčm mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®mam mbaraegha a ikaaŇči, Iesus guisimbaaŇčra aremi. Mauthughura a Iesus…®n khum niam…®usua Josev…®m mb…®namba.  
\v 46-47 Mauthughura Josev…®m mb…®sasin…® ughurana aghuuŇčn mav aŇčgu uvhuesigha zava Iesus…®n khuma daeŇčga zeghir…®. Ana na uphomigha g…®vagha ana nigha guava ak…®man thooŇč mee r…®tusi thav…®n gugha ana ath…®. Ma uthughun Makdalan…®n…® uŇčuuna amigh Maria, ko Josev…®ni inaghamuuŇč Maria, aniiŇč garima, Josev Iesus…®n khum nigha ak…®man thooŇčna avena ana ath…®gha, ak…®mani ikh…®van mav…® uphoghuphuegha zava aŇčna akamania r…®kuugha. 
\c 16  
\s1 Iesus nomthegha r…®kavi 
\r (Metiu 28.1-8 ko Luk 24.1-12 koma Jon 20.1-10) 
\p  
\v 1 Avhughususan…® uthugh g…®vasima, Makdalan…®n…® uŇčuuna amigh Maria, ko Jems…®n inaghamuuŇč Maria, ko Salome mee maaŇč…® Iesus…®n khum agh…®vousua mb…®ghuriir aghui zuir…®m mb…®ruer marsigh…® uvhuesi.  
\v 2-3 7 p…®lar…® uthusir…® ufhuaragha zuir…® uthughun aro anandima, r…®maaŇčra mee gua Iesus…®n khum ath…®si ak…®man thooŇčna aghan norira nori v…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúTh…®…®Ňčra ena akuragh ak…®man thooŇčna akamania r…®kuusi ak…®m…® uphuegh ti?‚ÄĚ \f * \fr 16:2-3 \ft 7 p…®lar…® uthusir…® ufhuaragha zuir…® uthugh a Sande. \f* 
\v 4 Mee gua garima ak…®mani ikh…®van khav, mee ana uphoghuphuegha gu.  
\v 5 Mee ak…®man thooŇčna akamaniiŇčna aven gua garima gumaghani ikaman mav shaaran…® ughuran…® uruaran mava arugha agharan guv…®n amandaghava apheraghav iti. Mee aŇčn ganigha bar r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amui. 
\p  
\v 6 Gumaghan khav kamagh…®m mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee atitiiŇčn thagh…®ri. K…® ikaaŇči. Gee NasaretiiŇčn gumagh, Iesus…®usua gari. A khani ighuuvana aremigha nomthegha r…®kavi! A khagh iti phat…®. Gee khagh a ir…®ghavi ikesira aŇčanan gan.  
\v 7 Thighira gee maaŇč…®, Pita ko aŇčn suren gumasiri igharis tharsi v…®k…®m, ‚ÄėA gen…® ufhuaragh Galilin distrigh…®n maŇčŇčaŇčga. Am mb…®kemisi mogh…®n gee munagh aŇčmba othuivhami.‚Äô ‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 8 Mauthughura mee r…®Ňčgavan maghat…®gha amuigha guava ak…®ran guegha phuv…®ra are. Mee atitiiŇči, kamagha amuigha mee tharsi v…®kemisi phat…®. 
\s1 Makdalan…®n…® uŇčuuna amigh Maria Iesus…®n gani 
\r (Metiu 28.9-10 koma Jon 20.11-18) 
\p  
\v 9 Iesus 7 p…®la uthusir…® ufhuaragha zuir…® uthughun r…®maaŇčra nomthegha r…®khavigha Makdalan…®n…® uŇčuuna amigh Maria, ufhuaragha nomb…®n aŇčn kh…®va. Amighan khav, Iesus…® ufhuaragha unduur maghat…®sir 7 p…®la iti tharsi vatoghi.\f * \fr 16:9 \ft IkeeŇčsi gumasira av…®rara Sapta 16, ves 9…®ni ikegha gua 20in…® uthusir akaa v…®Ňčg…® kamagh…®usue, ‚ÄúMak nomb…® ana os…®risi phat…®, gumaghan mav g…®n ana os…®ri.‚ÄĚ \f* 
\v 10 Gumughun gumasi rako amisi Iesus…®n phorugha aruava ikesi tharsi, mee aŇčm…®usua bar osemigha phuv…®ra azia itima, Maria gugha Iesus…®n gun mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi.  
\v 11 A mem mb…®kemisima, mee oraghi, Iesus nomthegha r…®khavigha nomb…® nigha Makdalan…®n…® uŇčuuna amigh Marian kh…®vasi an aŇčn gani. Mee kamagh oraegha n…®ghn…®ghana aghavagharana amighan khav…®na akaar iti phat…®. 
\s1 Suren gumaghan phunini utuav…®n Iesus…®n gani 
\r (Luk 24.13-35) 
\p  
\v 12 Uthughun khav…®n g…®n Iesus…®n suren gumaghan phunini uŇčuuni ikh…®van ak…®ran zuima Iesus igharaghava otogha aniiŇčm mbato.  
\v 13 Mauthughura aniiŇč nomthegha za bighan khav…®n gun marsi v…®kemisi, mee iv…®ra n…®ghn…®ghana aghavagharan aniiŇčna akaar iti phat…®. 
\s1 Iesus mee ramuaŇčgamiri iŇčaaran gun non suren gumasi v…®Ňčgeeghi 
\r (Metiu 28.16-20 ko Luk 24.36-49 koma Jon 20.19-23) 
\p  
\v 14 G…®n…® 11 p…®lan suren gumasi aphima Iesus nomb…® nigha men kh…®va. A ikaaŇči, mee n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar phat…®gha, mee navana aghavaghar iti. A nomthegha r…®kavisir bighaaŇč, marsi aŇčn ganigha mem mb…®Ňčgeema, mee n…®ghn…®ghana aghavagharam mb…®Ňčg…®Ňčg…®man khav…®ni iti phat…®. Bisir kharsiv…®usua Iesus mem mb…®Ňčg…® meŇčga avhesi.  
\v 15 A kamagh mem mb…®Ňčgeeghi, ‚ÄúGee maaŇč…® unuagh…®nan khav bar aŇč raruva unuagh…®nan khav…®ni iti gumasi rako amisi bar kha akamana aghuuŇčn mem mb…®k…®m.  
\v 16 Gee mem mb…®k…®mti th…®…®Ňčra n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar nani ikh…®va, urueghtima, Got aŇčna akuraghti, a m…®ghas…®gh Got…®n phorugh ikaami. Th…®…®Ňčra n…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar nani iti phat…®, a Got os…®mnd…®siva oragh anda r…®k…®ramir…® uthughuna aveni ikh…®va uvhuesan maghat…®gh niaŇčga.  
\v 17-18 N…®ghn…®ghana aghavaghar nani iti tharsi, gamgaaŇčn bisir kharsi iv…®ra men kh…®vami. Mee nani iz…®…®n…® unduur maghat…®si vatogh…®va, mee uŇčuimbar akaa ikeeŇčsi phat…®si tharsi v…®k…®m…®va, ukurusi nona afharir andar…® usuighemi. Mee ar…®ghirira aŇčguar r…®m…® thava rameghti a thange men navigha as…®ghasiighem phat…®ghami. Mee nona afhari nigh ar…®mar…®r gumasir ar…®ghtima mena ar…®mar…® g…®vaghami.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Got Iesus nigha non…® uŇčuun guavanambo 
\r (Luk 24.50-53 koma Iesus…®m Mb…®sevisir Gumasi 1.9-11) 
\p  
\v 19 Uthughun khav…®ni Ikh…®v Iesus, bisir kharsir mem mb…®kemigha g…®vasima Got ana nigha non…® uŇčuun guavanambo. Ana nambogha, a Got…®na agharan guv…®n amandagha apheraghav iti.  
\v 20 Gumughun suren gumasi unuagh…®nan khav…®na aŇčani bar andar guava akam…® ukuri. Ikh…®v men phorugha iŇčaarava non gamgaaŇčn meŇčga aniiŇčsi mee aŇčn gamgaaŇčn bisigha amui. Kamagha amuisima gumasi rako amisi ikaaŇči, akaman khav bar guisimbaaŇčra.